\id EZK Pohnpeian Bible
\h ESEKIEL
\toc1 ESEKIEL
\toc2 ESEKIEL
\toc3 Ese.
\mt1 ESEKIEL
\is1 Oaralap en Pwuhk wet
\ip Soukohp Esekiel iang kalipilipalahng nan Papilonia oh momourki erein ahnsou ehu mwohn oh mwurin ohlahn Serusalem limwahn pahr 586 mwohn Krais. Eh doadoahk oarepene soangen mehn Suhs riau: eri, mehn Suhs me kalipilipalahr ko me mihmi nan Papilonia, oh me kin mihmi Serusalem kan. \bk Pwuken Esekiel \bk* kak pwalpeseng wiahda pali weneu: 1) Malipilip ong Esekiel pwe en wiahla soukohp. 2) Audaudkihda kehkehlik kan ong aramas akan duwen ohlahn oh mwomwlahn Serusalem me pahn kohdo. 3) Kasalehda sapwellimen Kaun-o mahsen en kaweid ong wehi kei me wiakauwe oh kaweidsuwedihala sapwellime aramas akan. 4) Duwen kapohl oh kakehlepen mehn Israel kan mwurin ohlahn Serusalem, oh duwen inoun paiamwahu me pahn kohdo. 5) Kokohp me uhwong Kok. 6) Esekiel koasoiahda duwen onohnsapahl en Tehnpas Sarawio oh wehin Israel.
\ip Esekiel, ohl emen me eh pwoson inenen kehlail oh nan kapehd wehwe. Kamarainpen nan kapehde tohtohie sansanlda ni mwomwen kaudiahl, oh peuspen sapwellimen Kaun-o mahsen tohto reh kin wiawi ni karasaras dehde oh lingan. Esekiel inenen kin kehlailki anahn en onohnsapahl en nan kapehd en aramas oh ngene, oh pwukoahn emenemen aramas ong ni dipe kan; e ahpw pil lohkihda eh koapworopworki onohnsapahl en mouren wehi. Nin duwen samworo men oh soukohp, e kin ngoangki mehlel kamwahupen Tehnpas Sarawio, oh anahnepen mour sarawi.
\iot Audepe ni Oaralap
\io1 Malipilip ong Esekiel 1.1—3.27
\io1 Mahsen duwen mwomwlahn Serusalem 4.1—24.27
\io1 Sapwellimen Koht kadeik ong wehi kan 25.1—32.32
\io1 Sapwellimen Koht inou ong sapwellime aramas akan 33.1—37.28
\io1 Kokohp me uhwong Kok 38.1—39.29
\io1 Kaudiahl ehu en Tehnpas Sarawi oh wehi ong ni ahnsou kohkohdo 40.1—48.35
\c 1
\s1 Mwoalen Koht
\p 
\v 1 Ni kalimaun rahn ni kapahieun sounpwong en kesilihsek en pahr,\f a \fr 1:1 \fk KESILIHSEK EN PAHR: \ft E sohte nohn sansal mehnia pahr met.\f* ngehi, samworo Esekiel, nein Pusi, mihmi rehn riei mehn Suhs ako me kalipilipalahr nan Papilonia limwahn Pillap Separ. Pahnlahng ahpw ritpeseng, ngehi eri kilangada Koht nan kaudiahl ehu. \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Kaud. 19.11.\x*
\p 
\v 2 (Met iei ni kalimaun sounpar sang ni ahnsou me Nanmwarki Sehoiakin kalipilipalahng Papilonia.\x - \xo 1:2 \xt 2 Nan. 24.10-16; 2 Kron. 36.9-10.\x*
\v 3 Wasao limwahn Pillap Separ, I ahpw rongada mahsen en KAUN-O eh peidohng ie, oh I ahpw pehmada sapwellime manaman.
\p 
\v 4 Ngehi eri sarada oh kilangada lapalahn elipip ehu me kohkohdo sang paliepeng, oh lapalahn pelien depwek pali. Sang nan pelien depwek pali wet lioal ahpw kin piripirsang, oh marain lingaling ehu me kapilpene. Wasa me lioal kin pirasang ieo, mie mehkot me inenen lingaling duwehte prons.
\v 5 Nan werengen elipipo mwohmw kei ahpw wie sansaldo, likamwete menmour pahmen. Re mwomwen aramas,\x - \xo 1:5 \xt Kaud. 4.6.\x*
\v 6 ahpw emenemen menmour ko mas pahieu oh pehnpihr pahieu.
\v 7 Nehrail ko me inen, ahpw patehnehrail ko duwehte kumwut en kouwol. Menmour ko ahpw kin wie lingalingdo duwehte lingan en prons.
\v 8 Eri, mas pahieu oh pehnpihr pahieu me emenemen ahneki, pil mie pehn aramas rehn emenemen menmour pwukat me uhsang pahn ehuehu ar pehnpihr kan.
\v 9 Emenemen menmour ko ngapkipeseng pehnpihr riau, oh imwin pehrail kan doakpene, me kahrehda mwomwarail wia keimw pahieu. Eri, ni ar kin mwekid, re kin wiahkinteieu mwekidwei, sohte mwahn kin sohpeiseli.
\p 
\v 10 Mesen emenemen menmour pwukat me pahieu ahpw wekpeseng: mesen aramas me mi mwowe, a mesen laion me mi ni palimaun, mesen kouwol palimeing, oh mesen ikel me mi likinpaiki.\x - \xo 1:10 \xt Esek. 10.14; Kaud. 4.7.\x*
\v 11 Emenemen menmour pwukat ahpw kapapeseng eh pehnpihr riau pwe imwin ar pehnpihr kan en doakpene, oh riau ar pehnpihr ko pwoalepene paliwararail.
\v 12 Menmour pwukat sohpeipeseng ni keimw pahieu en sampah, kahrehda re kin pwonte mwekidwei wasa me re men kohla ie, oh sohte kin pirekek ni arail kin mwekidwei.
\p 
\v 13 Eri, likamwete mehnser ehu me wie lullul oh mwekimwekid poatopoat nanpwungen menmour ko. Mehnsero kin lullul oh lioal kin piripirsang loale.\x - \xo 1:13 \xt Kaud. 4.5.\x*
\v 14 Pein menmour ko ahpw kin mwekidwei oh kin pwurodo, rasehng mwekid en lioal.
\p 
\v 15 Ni ei uduhdiahl menmour pahmeno, I kilangada mehn kadahr pahieu me leldiong pohn pwehl; ehuehu mehn kadahr mihte limwahn emenemen menmour ko.\x - \xo 1:15 \xt Esek. 10.9-13.\x*
\v 16 Ehuehu mehn kadahr ko inenen melengileng duwehte kisin takai kesempwal, oh koaros duwepenehte. Ehuehu mehn kadahr ko pil mie ehu mehn kadahr tohrohr loale me pangapang,
\v 17 me kahrehda mehn kadahr ko koaros kak tangewei ong ni keimw pahieu en sampah.
\v 18 Oh kilin mehn kadahr ko pwoaren mas tohr me wia.\x - \xo 1:18 \xt Kaud. 4.8.\x*
\v 19 Ni ahnsou koaros me menmour ko kin mwekid, mehn kadahr ko pil kin iang mwekid, oh ma menmour ko kin pihrda, mehn kadahr ko pil kin iang.
\v 20 Menmour ko kin kohla wasa koaros me re mwahuki, oh mehn kadahr ko pil kin iangete, pwehki re kin mihmi pahn manaman en menmour ko.
\v 21 Ahnsou koaros me menmour ko pahn kin mwekid, de uhdi, de pihrda, mehn kadahr ko pil kin wia soahngohte.
\p 
\v 22 Pohnangin moangen menmour ko mie mehkot me likamwete pwalang ehu me wiawihkihda kilahs kamahl.\x - \xo 1:22 \xt Kaud. 4.6.\x*
\v 23 Pahn pwalango emenemen menmour ko kapapeseng pehnpihr riau kadangalahng me mi limwah, oh riau pehnpihr pwoalepene paliwere.
\v 24 I ahpw rongada ngilen arail pehnpihr ko ni ar kin pihr. Ngihlo rasehng ngirisek en madau, ngilen karis laud ni eh kin mwekid, oh rasehng kapitien Koht, Wasa Lapalahpie. Ni ar kin uhdi sohla pihr, re kin kihpene pehrail kan,\x - \xo 1:24 \xt Kaud. 1.4-15; 19.6.\x*
\v 25 ahpw ngihlo kin peipeido sangete pohnangin pwalango pohnangin moangarail kan.
\p 
\v 26 Pohnangin pwalango mie mehkot me likamwete mwoahl ehu me wiawihkihda takai kesempwal sapair, oh mehmen me mwomwen aramas ketiket powe.\x - \xo 1:26 \xt Esek. 10.1; Kaud. 4.2-3.\x*
\v 27 Eri, mwohmw wet wie lingalingdo duwehte lingaling en prons nan werengen kisiniei. Marain lingaling ehu ahpw kapilpene wasa koaros.\x - \xo 1:27 \xt Esek. 8.2.\x*
\v 28 Marain lingan me rasehng lingan en ahia me kin pwarada nin depwek en keteu kan. Ih duwen met mwomwen marain lingaling me kin kasalehda me KAUN-O kin ketiket wasao.
\c 2
\s1 Koht ketin Malipe Esekiel pwe en Wiahla Soukohp
\p 
\v 1 Ni ei kilangada irair wet, I ahpw poaridiong nanpwel. Oh rongada ngihl ehu me mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas,\f b \fr 2:1 \fk NEIN ARAMAS: \ft Nan Kadehde Kapw lepin mahsen pwukat wia mwar ehu en Sises Krais, ahpw wasaht mouren lepin mahsen pwukat weksang. wasaht e kasalehda duwen soukohp Esekiel eh wia aramaste, kaidehn Koht. Eri, ih wehwehn lepin mahsen pwukat nan pwuhk wet.\f* uhda. I men lokaiaiong uhk.”
\p 
\v 2 Nindokon ngihlo eh mahmahsen, ngenen Koht kipeiehdi oh kasihnenihiehda. I ahpw pil rongorong ngihlo eh mahsanih,
\v 3 “Kowe, nein aramas, I kadarowohng uhk rehn aramas en Israel kan, me kahngohdilahr oh pelianiedahr. Re kahngohdilahr duwehte samarail en mahs ako.
\v 4 Re keptakailahr oh sohte kin waunekin ie. I kadaruhkewei pwe ke en padahkihong irail dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, mahsanihong irail.
\v 5 Mehnda ma aramas kahngohdi pwuko pahn rong uhk de soh, a re en ese me soukohp men miher nanpwungarail.
\p 
\v 6 “Ahpw kowe, nein aramas, ke sohte pahn masak irail de masak mehkot me re pahn nda. Re pahn uhwonguhk oh kailongkin uhk; ke pahn rasehng me ke mihmi nanpwungen skorpion kan. Ahpw ke dehpa masak aramas kahngohdi pwuko, de masak mehkot me re pahn ndawei.
\v 7 Ke pahn ndaiong irail mehkoaros me I padahkihong uhk, mehnda ma re men rong uhk de soh. Tamataman me irail aramas kahngohdi kei.
\p 
\v 8 “Eri, kowe, nein aramas, rong kanahieng dahme I pahn mahsanih. Ke dehr kahngohdi duwehte irail. Sarapeseng oh kangala dahme I pahn kihong uhk.”
\v 9 I ahpw kilangada peh ehu, me kapadohng ie pelien doaropwe ieu me limilimpene.\x - \xo 2:9 \xt Kaud. 5.1.\x*
\v 10 E ahpw welikpeseng pelien doaropweo, ngehi eri kilangada me pelien doaropweo nting pali koaros. Eri, audepen doaropweo iei mahsen en nsensuwed kei, oh pil mahsen en mwahiei oh kapahtou.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Koht eri ketin mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, kangala pelien doaropwe wet; ke ahpw kohwei oh lokaiaiong mehn Israel kan.”\x - \xo 3:1 \xt Kaud. 10.9-10.\x*
\p 
\v 2 Ngehi eri sarapeseng, e ahpw ketikihong ie pelien doaropweo pwe I en tungoalehla.
\v 3 Ih eri mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, kangala pelien doaropwe wet me I kihwei; kadirehkihla kapehdomwen.” Ngehi eri tungoalehla, oh kehnda duwen eh mem duwehte sukehn loangalap.
\p 
\v 4 Koht eri mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, kohwei rehn mehn Israel kan, oh padahkihong irail mehkoaros me I pahn mahsanihwei.
\v 5 I sohte kadaruhkewei nan ehu wehi me kin lokaiahki lokaiahn liki, pwe rehn mehn Israel kante.
\v 6 Ma I kadaruhkewei nan wehi kan me ar lokaia uhdahn apwal ong uhk ke en dehdehki, re uhdahn pahn rong uhk.
\v 7 Ahpw sohte emen mehn Israel kan pahn men rong; re pil sohte mwahn men rong ie. Irail koaruhsie keptakailahr oh kahngohdilahr.
\v 8 A met, I pahn wiahiong uhk pwe ke en keptaki oh kahngohdiong irail kowahlap, duwehte me irail kin wiahiong ie.
\v 9 I pahn kakehleiukada pwe ke en pil kekeluwak, rasehng takai kesempwal daimon; ke dehpa masak aramas kahngohdi pwuko.”
\p 
\v 10 Koht pil ketin mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, tehk mwahu oh tamataman mehkoaros me I padahkihong uhk.
\v 11 Ke ahpw kohwei rehn riomw pwilidak en sapwomw kan me kalipilipalahr oh padahkihong irail dahme I mahsanihong irail, mehnda ma re men rong de soh.”
\p 
\v 12 Ngenen Koht eri ketin pwekiehda, I ahpw rongada ngihl ehu me duwehte ngirisek en rerrer en sahpw, me mahsanih, “Kapinga roson en KAUN-O nanleng wasa ileilehie!”
\v 13 I ahpw pil rongada ngilen pehnpihr en menmour ko ar mwekimwekid nan wehwe, oh pil ngilen mehn kadahr ko, rasehng ngirisek en rerrer en sahpw.
\v 14 Manaman en KAUN-O ahpw kadireiehla, nindokon ngenen Koht eh ketin pwekiehda, I ahpw nsensuwedla oh lingeringerda.
\v 15 Ngehi eri patohla Tel Apip limwahn Pillap Separ, wasa me mehn Suhs me kalipilipala ko kin koukousoan ie, oh I mihmihki wasao erein rahn isuh oh wie pwunopwundoki audepen kaudiahl kapwuriamwei wet.
\p 
\v 16 Mwurin rahn isuhwo, KAUN-O ahpw ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 17 “Kowe, nein aramas, I pahn wiahkinuhkala silepen wehin Israel. Ke ahpw padahkihong irail kehkehlik kan me I pahn wiahiong uhk.
\v 18 Ma I pahn mahsanih me emen pahn mehkihla dipe, ke ahpw sohte kaweidki pwe en wekidala eh mour suwed pwe en kak momour, e uhdahn pahn mehla nan dipe kan, a I pahn kapwukoahnkin uhk eh mehla.
\v 19 A ma ke kalikedihsang emen nan eh mour suwed, e ahpw sohte men tokedihsang wiewia dihp, e pahn mehla nan dipe, a omw mour pahn poadoandoarla.
\p 
\v 20 “Ma aramas me uhdahn mwahu men tapihada wia me suwed, I ahpw pahn kihong nan irair keper ehu, aramaso pahn mehla ma ke sohte kaweidki en tokedihsang eh suwed. E pahn mehla pwehki dipe kan, oh I sohte pahn tamanda eh wiewia mwahu kan me e wiadahr. A I pahn kapwukoahnkin uhk eh mehla.
\v 21 Ma ke kaweidki aramas mwahu men en dehr wiahda dihp, a e ahpw rong uhk oh sohte wiahda dihp, e pahn mourla, oh omw mour pil pahn poadoandoarla.”
\s1 Esekiel Sohla Kak Lokaia
\r (Esekiel 33.1-9)
\p 
\v 22 Ngehi eri pehmada manaman en limmen KAUN-O rehi oh patohwan rongada kapitie me mahsanihong ie, “Uhda oh kohwei nan wahwo. I pahn mahseniong uhk wasao.”
\p 
\v 23 Ngehi eri patohla nan wahwo oh kilangada lingaling en KAUN-O wasao, duwehte me I kilangadahr limwahn Pillap Separ. I ahpw poaridi nanpwel,
\v 24 a ngenen Koht ahpw kasihnenihiehda. KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie, “Kohkohwei ni imwomwo, oh mihmihte loale sohte pedoisang.
\v 25 Eri, kowe, nein aramas, ke pahn selikihdi sellap kei oh ke sohla pahn kak kohla wasa me mie aramas.
\v 26 I pahn katengehdi lowomwen pwe ke en dehr kaweid aramas kahngohdi pwukat.
\v 27 Eri, ni ei pahn pwurehng mahseniong uhk oh sapwadada lowomwen, ke ahpw pahn patohwanong irail dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahmahsanih. Ekei irail pahn rong uhk, a ekei pahn pohnsehseiuk, pwe irail wialahr wehi kahngohdi ehu.”
\c 4
\s1 Esekiel Mwomwehda duwen Serusalem eh pahn Lohdi
\p 
\v 1 Koht ketin mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, ale ehu takai pweht, kihdiong mwohmw, oh elehda lain powe pwehn wia kelel en kahnimw en Serusalem.
\v 2 Eri, pwe en uhd mwomwehda duwen imwintihti eh pahn kalowehdi kahnimwo, ke pahn wiahda warawar, doadoahk en koasoakehda pwehl kan, impwal kan, oh wiahda lepin tuhke mehn kauwehla ewen kehl kan.
\v 3 Ale ehu pan mete oh kauwada duwehte kehl ehu nanpwungen kowe oh kahnimwo. Eri, ke ahpw sohpeiong kahnimwo. Mwekid en kalowehdi kahnimwo tepier oh kowe me mahmahweniong. Met pahn wia kilel ehu ong wehin Israel.
\p 
\v 4-5 “Mwuhr ke pahn wendi keingihngla palimeingomw, I ahpw pahn kihdiong pohmw dihp me wehin Israel wiadahr. Ke pahn mihmi wasao wie lokolok erein rahn 390 pwehki diparailo. I kileledionguhkehr me rahn ehu pahn wehwehki ehu sounpar me arail lokoloko pahn reireiki.
\v 6 Ni omw pahn kanekehla met, ke pahn wekidekla palimaunomw oh uhd ale kalokepen dipen Suda erein rahn pahisek—rahn ehu pahn wehwehki sounpar ehu ong ni kalokepen diparailo.
\p 
\v 7 “Mesomw en pahn uhlahngete Serusalem mwasamwasahn kahpwal me wiewiawihong, rok kumwut ong kahnimwo oh wiahiong kokohp me pahn uhwong.
\v 8 I pahn pireiukpene pwe ke en sohte kak mwekidseli lao kahpwalo pahn imwisekla.
\p 
\v 9 “Ke pahn ale ekei wahn wihd, parli, pihn, pihs, millet, oh spelt. Ke ahpw doaloairailpene oh wiahkihda pilawa. Ihme ke pahn kangkang erein rahn 390 me ke pahn wonohnki ni palimeingomwo.
\v 10 Ke pahn mweimweiong en kang ouns waluh en pilawa nan rahn ehu, oh e pahn nekila mandahsang rahno.
\v 11 Pil nimomw pihl pahn itaitete, kepte riau nan rahn ehu.
\v 12 Ke pahn saunkihda kisiniei pwisehn aramas me madekenglahr, umwunda pilawa pohn mwoalus ko, oh kang wasa me aramas kak kilang uhk ie.”
\p 
\v 13 KAUN-O ahpw mahsanih, “Met iei duwen mehn Israel ar pahn kang mwenge me Kosonnedo keinapwih,\f c \fr 4:13 \fk MWENGE ME KOSONNEDO KEINAPWIH: \ft Kosonned en Moses kin keinapwih soangen mwenge kei me kin wia mehkot samin ong kaudok (tehk Lip. 11).\f* ni ei pahn kamwarakirailpeseng nan wehin liki kan.
\p 
\v 14 I ahpw sapeng, patohwan, “Soh, Maing KAUN, Wasa Lapalahpie! I sohte mwahn kasaminehla pein ngehi. Sang ni ei tikitik I soh mwahn tungoalehda uduk en mahn emen me mehkihla soumwahu de me mahn lawalo kan kemehla. I sohte mwahn tungoalehda mahn emen me aramas kin wiahki me samin.”
\p 
\v 15 Koht eri mahsanih, “Eri, me mwahu. I pahn mweidohng uhk ke en saunkihda kisinieio pwisehn kou, oh ke kak umwunda konomw pilawa pohn mwoalus ko.”
\p 
\v 16 E ahpw ketin usehla mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, I pahn ketikihsang pilawa nan Serusalem. Aramas akan wasao pahn pahtoula oh pwunod ni ar pahn kin teneki uwen mwenge me re pahn kang oh pihl me re pahn nim.
\v 17 E pahn sohla kanarail mwenge oh nimarail pihl; re pahn pahtoula, tihtihla oh mehla pwehki diparail kan.”
\c 5
\s1 Esekiel Sehkasang Pitenmoange kan
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, ale ehu kedlahs keng oh sehkasang omw alis kan oh pitenmoangomw koaros. Kowe eri tenekihda pohn mehn tenek oh nehkpeseng ni mwutumwut siluh.
\v 2 Ke pahn isikala kesiluhn mwutumwuto nan kahnimwo ni ahnsou me mwekid en mahwen me ke wiewiao pahn imwisekla. Pil ale ehu mwutumwuto oh pelehkipene noumw kedlahso nindokon omw pahn alialuseli likin kahnimwo. Mwutumwut me luhweo ke pahn kamwerepeseng nan kisinieng, I ahpw pahn pwakiheki nei kedlahset.
\v 3 Ke pahn nekidala ekis pitenmoang oh kidimpene nan pwungipen omw likou kan.
\v 4 Mwuhr ke pahn ale ekei oh keselahng nan kisiniei, oh mweidohng en mwasikala. Eri, sang wasao kisiniei pahn kohda oh isikala wehin Israel pwon.”
\p 
\v 5 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie ahpw mahsanih, “Kilang Serusalem. I kihdiong nanwerengen sampah, wehi teikan ahpw kapilpene.
\v 6 Ahpw Serusalem kahngohdiong ei koasoandi kan oh kasalehda me e suwed sang wehi teikan, sapeik sang wehi teikan me kapilpene. Serusalem soikala ei koasoandi kan oh sohte men kapwaiada ei kosonned akan.
\v 7 Eri met, rong kowe Serusalem, rong dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih. Pwehki omw sohte peikiong ei kosonned kan oh sohte kapwaiada ei koasoandi kan, ke wiadahr me suwed sang wehi teikan me kapiluhkpene. Ke idawehnlahr tiahk en wehi teikan.
\v 8 Eri, ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanihong uhk me kowe iei ei imwintihti. I pahn kadeikuhkada wasa me wehi koaros kak kilang.
\v 9 Pwehki mehkoaros me ke wiadahr me I kin kalahdeki, I pahn kaloke Serusalem laudsang ei kalokeier mahs oh sohte ehu kalokolok en mwuhr pahn duwe met.
\v 10 Pwehki met, sahm oh ihn kan nan Serusalem pahn kangala neirail seri kan, oh seri kan pahn kangala samarail oh inarail kan. I pahn kalokei kumwail oh kamwarakpeseng wasa koaros irail kan me momourte.\x - \xo 5:10 \xt Koul Ked. 4.10.\x*
\p 
\v 11 “Iei me kahrehda ngehi Koht ieias—met iei mahsen en KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie—pwehki amwail kasaminehkihla Tehnpasei Sarawio me suwed, oh tiahk saut kan me kumwail wiadahr, I pahn kauweikumwailla ni sohte kupwur mahk.
\v 12 Silikis ehun aramas akan pahn mehkihla soumwahu oh duhpek nan kahnimwo; a silikis ehu pahn mehkihla kedlahs likin kahnimwo; oh I pahn kamarakpeseng luhwe kan nan kisinieng oh pwakihkin irail kedlahs.
\p 
\v 13 “Ke pahn kehn engin ei engieng lao I nsenamwahula. Ni mepwukat eh pahn pweida, ke pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahsenionguhkehr, pwehki ei engiengkidahr omw soaloalopwoat.
\v 14 Aramas koaros sang nan wehi kan me kapiluhkpene pahn keid wasaht oh kouruhrkin uhk oh sohte pahn men keidohng mpomw.
\p 
\v 15 “Ni ei kin engiengda pahmw oh kalokeiuk, wehi koaros me kapiluhkpene pahn kin masepwehkada. Re pahn kin mwamwahlkinuhkala oh kouruhrkin uhk.
\v 16 I pahn ketikihsang konomw kisin mwenge oh mweidala pwe ke en duhpekla. Ke pahn kehn medek en duhpek rasehng arep keng me pekederdohng kamwomwuhkala.
\v 17 I pahn kadarodo lehk oh mahn lawalo pwe en kemehla noumw seri kan, iangahki soumwahu, kamaramas, oh mahwen pwe en kemeiukala. Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen.”\x - \xo 5:17 \xt Kaud. 6.8.\x*
\c 6
\s1 KAUN-O ketin Keriahla Dikedik en Eni kan
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, kilengwohng pohn nahna kan en Israel oh kihiong irail ei mahsen.
\v 3 Padahkihong nahna kan en Israel en rong mahsen en KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie—en rong dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong nahna kan, dohl kan, wahu loal kan, oh wahu tikitik kan; I pahn kadarodo kedlahs pwoat pwehn kamwomwala wasa kan me aramas kin kaudokohng dikedik en eni kan ie.
\v 4 Pei sarawi kan pahn mweredi oh pei sarawien warpwohmwahu kan pahn ohla. Aramas koaros wasao pahn kamakamala mwohn mesen ar dikedik en eni kan.
\v 5 I pahn kamwarakpeseng paliweren mehn Israel kan me melahr; I pahn kamwarakpeseng tihrail kan kapilkipene pei sarawi kan.
\v 6 Kahnimw koaros en Israel pahn kamwomwmwomwla, pwe arail pei sarawi koaros oh dikedik en eni koaros pahn mwerpeseng, arail pei sarawien warpwohmwahu kan pahn ohla, oh mekoaros me re wiadahr pahn sohrala.
\v 7 Aramas pahn kamakamala wasa koaros, oh irail kan me pahn pitla pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 8 “I pahn mweidohng ekei en pitsang kamalahn aramaso oh mwarahkpeseng nan wehi kan,
\v 9 wasa re pahn kalipilipala ie. Re ahpw pahn tamaniehda wasao oh esehla me I kaloke irail oh kasaroweiraildi pwehki arail nan kapehd soaloalopwoat kan eh soikiehla oh mwohnkihla dikedik en eni kan sang ie. Oh re pahn kauwong pein irail ar lingeringer pwehki suwed oh tiahk sapwung kan me re wiadahr.
\v 10 Re pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, oh ei kehkehlik kan kaidehn mehkot mwahl.”
\p 
\v 11 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Welik pehmw kan! Tomtomki nehmw kan! Sengiseng en pahtou pwehki soahng suwed, oh kasaut kan me mehn Israel wiadahr. Re pahn mehkihla mahwen de lehk lapalap de soumwahu.
\v 12 Irail kan me mihmi wasa doh pahn soumwahuda oh mehla; irail kan me mi wasa keren pahn mehkihla mahwen; irail kan me pahn pitsang mehla pahn uhd mehkihla duhpek. Re pahn kehn engin ei engieng koaros.
\v 13 Paliweren me melahr akan pahn mwarahkpeseng nanpwungen dikedik en eni kan oh kapilpene pei sarawi kan, re pahn mwarahkpeseng pohn dohl ile koaros, pohn kumwen nahna koaros, pahn tuhke losolos koaros oh pahn tuhke ohk laud koaros, wasa koaros me re kin wia ie ar meirong isihs ong ar dikedik en eni kan. Eri, aramas koaros ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.
\v 14 Ei, I pahn kapahwei limei oh kamwomwala arail wehi. I pahn wiahkihla sapwtehn sang ni palieir en sapwtehno lellahng kahnimw Ripla ni paliepeng, I sohte pahn mahkohng wasa kis me mehn Israel kan kin kousoan ie. Eri, koaros ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.”
\c 7
\s1 Imwilahn Israel Kerendohr
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, iet me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihiong wehin Israel: Met iei imwilahn wehio pwon!
\p 
\v 3 “Israel, imwilahn omw ahnsou leledohr. Ke pahn kehn ei engieng pwehki ei pahn kadeikada omw wiewia kan. I pahn dupukohng uhk omw tiahk saut kan.
\v 4 I sohte pahn poakeiukala de kasalehda ei kupwur mahk. I pahn kalokehkin uhk tiahk saut kan me ke wiadahr, pwe ke en esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.”
\p 
\v 5 Ih met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: “Ehu kahpwal pahn leledo mwurin ehu pahn lelohng uhk.
\v 6 E nekier. Met e imwiseklahr. Ke nekier.
\v 7 Imwilahn ahnsou leledohr ong noumw aramas akan me kin kousoan nan wehio. Ahnsowo kerendohr me solahr sarawi pahn wiawi ni wasahn kaudok pohn nahna kan, ahpw ihte pingiping me pahn wiawi.
\p 
\v 8 “Kereniongehr ke pahn kehn engin ei engieng. I pahn kadeikada ahmw wiewia kan, oh dupukohng uhk omw tiahk saut kan.
\v 9 I sohte pahn poakeiukala de kasalehda ei kupwur mahk. I pahn kalokehkin uhk tiahk saut kan me ke wiadahr, pwe ke en esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O, oh iei ngehi me kalokalokeiuk.’
\p 
\v 10 Rahnen apwal laud samwodohr. Kamaramas uklahr. Aklapalap daulihalahr mehkoaros.
\v 11 Kamaramas kin kahrehda uklahn me suwed. Sohte mehkot me arail pahn luhwehdi, sohte arail dipwsou kesempwal, arail dipwisou lingan, de arail lingan pahn luhwehdi.
\p 
\v 12 Ahnsowo leledohr. Rahno kerendohr me solahr pahn katepen netinet, pwehki sapwellimen KAUN-O kalokolok pahn lelohng aramas koaros.
\v 13 Sohte sounnet men pahn mour werei pwe en kak kapwurehda dahme e luhskihla, pwehki sapwellimen KAUN-O engieng pahn lelohng aramas koaros. Irail kan me suwed sohte kak mourla.
\v 14 Sowi pepeukehr, oh aramas koaros onopadahr. Ahpw sohte emen pahn kohla mahwen, pwe sapwellimen Koht engieng pahn lelohng aramas koaros.
\s1 Kalokepen Dipen Israel
\p 
\v 15 Pei wiewiawi pohn ahl akan, oh soumwahu oh duhpek nan ihmw kan. Mehmen me mihmiseli nansapw pahn mehla nan mahwen, oh mehmen me mihmi nan kahnimwo pahn mehkihla soumwahu oh duhpek.
\v 16 Ekei pahn sopolahng nin dohl kan rasehng mwuroi me masepwehkada tangasang nan wahu kan. Irail koaros pahn weiweirengki diparail kan.
\v 17 Pehn aramas koaros pahn luwetala, oh pwukiarail kan pahn rerrer.
\v 18 Re pahn pwuhriong nan likoun nsensuwed oh paliwararail pwon pahn rerrer. Pitenmoangarail kan pahn seiseisang, oh re pahn sarohdi.
\v 19 Re pahn kesehla neirail kohl oh silper kan pohn ahl akan duwehte kihd, pwehki kohl de silper sohte kak doareirailla ni ahnsou me KAUN-O pahn ketikidohng pohrail sapwellime engieng. Pwehki ar sohte kak doadoahngki pwehn kaitarala arail anahn de audehkihda nan kapehdirail kan. Kohl oh silper kahrehiong irail nan dihp.
\v 20 Mahs re kin pohnmwahsohki arail elin kapwat lingan akan, ahpw re kin doadoahngki elin kapwat pwukat ong ni wiepen dikedik en eni saut kan. Iei kahrepe wet me KAUN-O ketin kupwurehkihda re en sautikihla ar reken kepwe kan.”
\p 
\v 21 KAUN-O ketin mahsanih, “I pahn mweidohng mehn liki kan en pirapahsang ar diwpisou kan, oh me kin kauwehla kosonned kan pahn adihasang ar kepwe kan oh kasaminehla.
\v 22 I sohte pahn lidere ahnsou me dipwisou kesempwal kan en Tehnpasei Sarawio pahn saminla, ni ahnsou me sounpirap akan pahn pedolong loale oh kasaminehla.
\p 
\v 23 “Mehkoaros pingidahr—sahpwo direkilahr kamaramas oh kahnimwo direkilahr pei eikek.
\v 24 I pahn ketikihdo wehi kan me keieu suwed wasaht oh mweidohng re en adihasang imwamwail kan. Noumwail ohl keieu kehlail kan pahn nan kapehd tikitikla ni ahnsou me I pahn mweidohng wehi kan en kasaminehla wasa kan me kumwail kin kaudok ie.
\v 25 Seukoapworopwor ehu kohkohdo. Kumwail pahn rapahki popohl, ahpw kumwail sohte mwahn pahn diar.
\v 26 Ehu kahpwal pahn kohdo mwurin ehu, oh rohng kansensuwed kan ukla. Kumwail pahn peki rehn soukohp kan re en kohpada dahme pahn wiawi. Sohla mehkot me samworo kan pahn padahkihong aramas akan, oh sohla kaweid me mah kan kak wiahda.
\v 27 Nanmwarkio pahn mwahmwahiei, sapwellime pwutak pahn sohla eh koapworopwor, oh aramas akan pahn rerrerki ar masepwehk. I pahn kalokehkin kumwail amwail wiewia kan, oh pahn kadeingkumwailda nin duwen amwail kadeikadahr meteikan. Met pahn kasalehiong kumwail me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.”
\c 8
\s1 Dikedik en Eni kan nan Serusalem
\p 
\v 1 Ni kelimaun rahnen keweneun sounpwong en keweneun sounpar en ahnsou me se kalipilipala, me kaunda pwihn kalipilipala ko sang Suda ahpw iang ie mwomwohd nan imweio. Manaman en KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ahpw mwadangete tiada pohi.
\v 2 I ahpw sarada oh kilangada mwomwen aramas emen. Sang nan lukope kohdi mwomwen kisiniei, oh sang nan lukope kohda melengileng duwehte prons mwakelekel.\x - \xo 8:2 \xt Esek. 1.27.\x*
\v 3 Likamwete mwomwen lime me e kapahla oh kolada pitenmoangei ko. Eri, nan kaudiahl wet ngenen Koht ahpw pwekiehda nan wehwe oh ketikinielahng nan Serusalem. E ketikiniehla ni wenihmwen masloalen ewen kelen paliepeng en Tehnpas Sarawio, wasa me dikedik en eni men mihmi ie me inenen kahngiangih mehlel kupwur en Koht.
\p 
\v 4 I ahpw kilangada wasao marain lingaling me kasalehda me Koht en Israel ketiket wasao, duwehte me I kilangehr ni ahnsou me I patopato limwahn Pillap Separ.\x - \xo 8:4 \xt Esek. 1.28.\x*
\v 5 Koht ahpw mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, kilenglahng paliepeng.” I ahpw kilengla, oh wasao limwahn pei sarawio ni wenihmwen ewen kehlo I kilangada dikedik en enio me kahngiangih kupwur en Koht.
\p 
\v 6 Koht eri mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, ke kilang dahme wiewiawi? Kilang soahng saut kan me mehn Israel wiewia wasaht, re kadokadohwaniehla sang ei wasa sarawio. Ke pil pahn kilang ekei soahng kanamenek me laudsang met.”
\p 
\v 7 E ahpw ketikiniehla ni maslikin kehlo oh kasalehiong ie pwoahr ehu me mi ni kehlo.
\v 8 E ahpw mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, kauwehla dihden.” Ngehi eri kauwehla oh diarada wenihmw ehu.
\v 9 E ahpw mahsanihong ie, “Pedolong oh kilang soahng suwed oh saut kan me re wiewia wasao.”
\v 10 Ngehi eri pedolong oh kilang. Ni dihd ko inenen diren mahlen en sineik oh soangen mahn samin\f d \fr 8:10 \fk MAHN SAMIN: \ft Kosonned en Moses kin keinapwih aramas en kang soangen mahn ekei me samin ong kaudok (tehk 4.13; Lip. 11).)\f* teikan, oh pil soahng teikan me mehn Israel kan kin wie pwongipwongih.
\v 11 Kaunen mehn Israel isiakan me mihmi wasao, me iangahki Saasanaia nein Sapan. Emenemen irail kolokol mehn isik warpwohmwahu, oh warpwohmwahu ko wie edied.
\v 12 Koht ahpw keinemwe rehi, “Kowe, nein aramas, ke kilang dahme kaunen mehn Israel wiewia ni rir? Re wiewia ar kaudok nan pere ehu me diren dikedik en eni. Re kin akupwungki ndinda me: ‘KAUN-O sohte mwahn mahsanih kitail! E keselahr sahpwet.’”
\p 
\v 13 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie, “Ke pahn pil kilang mehkan me saut sang met.”
\v 14 Ih eri ketikiniehla ni ewen kelen paliepeng en Tehnpas Sarawio oh kasalehiong ie lih akan me wie sengisengki mehlahn koht Dammus.\f e \fr 8:14 \fk DAMMUS: \ft Koht emen me aramas akan kin lemehiong me e kin mehla ni ahnsou me wahnsahpw akan kin mehla oh pil pwurehng mourda nan sounpar me pahn wadedo mwuri. Lih akan kin mwahieiki eh mehla.\f*
\p 
\v 15 E ahpw keinemwe, “Kowe, nein aramas, ke kilang men? Ke pahn pil kilang mehkan me saut sang met.”
\v 16 Ih eri ketikiniehla masloalen kelen Tehnpas Sarawio. Limwahn wenihmwen mwoahlo, nanpwungen pei sarawio oh palangko, mweinele ohl riehk limmen me mihmi wasao. Re sohpeisang mwoahlo oh poaridiong palimese, wie kaukaudokiong dakadahn ketipin.
\p 
\v 17 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, ke kilang men? Mehn Suda pwukat sohte itarki ar wiewia me saut kan me ke kilangehr wasaht oh kamaramas me parpesengier nan sahpwo. Soh, re uhdahn pahn kohdo oh wia wasaht nan Tehnpas Sarawiet oh kalaudehkihla ei engieng. Kilang mwomwen ar lahlahwei ie ni soangen mwohmw me keieu kansensuwed!\f f \fr 8:17 \fk MWOHMW ME KEIEU KANSENSUWED: \ft Met soangen mwohmw ehu me duwehte mwomwen kaudok en me rotorot akan ni ar kin kihong rahntuhke ni tumwarail kan.\f*
\v 18 Re pahn kehn engin ei engieng. I sohte pahn kupwur mahkohng irail de kasalehda ei kupwurkalahngan. Re pahn weriwerki ar kapakap ong ie ni uwen ar kak, ahpw I sohte pahn karonge irail.”
\c 9
\s1 Serusalem Ale Lokolok
\p 
\v 1 Ngehi eri rongada Koht eh kapitie laudida, mahsanih, “Kohdo wasaht, kumwail kan me pahn kaloke kahnimwo. Kumwail wahdo noumwail tehtehn pei kan.”
\v 2 Ohl wenemen ahpw mwadangete pedolong sang maslikin ewen kehl ni paliepeng en Tehnpas Sarawio, emenemen irail weuwa nah tehtehn pei. Ohl emen ahpw iang irail me mi nan likou linen, e weuwa mehkot me e pahn ntingki. Irail koaros ahpw kohdo oh kesihnenda limwahn pei sarawi pronso.
\p 
\v 3 Marain lingaling en Koht en Israel ahpw kohdahsang pohn menmour ko\f g \fr 9:3 \fk MENMOUR KO: \ft Tehk 1.5-12.\f* wasa me e mihmi ie, oh mwekidlahng ni wenihmwen Tehnpas Sarawio. KAUN-O ahpw malipe ohl me mi nan likou lineno, mahsanih,
\p 
\v 4 “Kohwei nan kahnimw en Serusalem pwon oh kihdiong kilel ehu ni temwen aramas koaros me pahtoulahr oh milahr nan apwal pwehki soahng saut akan me wiewiawi nan kahnimwet.”\x - \xo 9:4 \xt Kaud. 7.3; 9.4; 14.1.\x*
\p 
\v 5 I ahpw rongada Koht eh mahsanihong ohl teiko, “Kumwail idawehnewei nan kahnimwo oh kemehla aramas akan. Kumwail kemehla koaros; kaleke kumwail mahkohng emen.
\v 6 Kumwail kemehla ohl mah kan, mwahnakapw akan, peinakapw akan, ihn kan, oh seri kan. Ahpw kumwail dehpa sair mehmen me kilel mi nan temwe. Kumwail tepida wasaht nan Tehnpasei Sarawiet.” Irail eri tepida kemehla kaun ako me kesikesihnen nan Tehnpas Sarawio.
\p 
\v 7 Koht ahpw mahsanihong irail, “Kumwail kasaminehla Tehnpas Sarawio. Kumwail audehkihla paliweren me melahr akan nan kehlo. Nna, kumwail tepida doadoahk!” Irail eri tepida kemehla aramas nan kahnimwo.
\p 
\v 8 Nindokon kamaramas eh wiewiawi, I kelekelehpw mwo, I ahpw poarikihdi meseiet nanpwel oh weriwerki, “Maing KAUN, Wasa Lapalahpie, ia duwe, komwi uhdahn engieng pahn Serusalem me kahrehda omwi pahn kemehla aramas koaros me luhwehdi nan Israel?”
\p 
\v 9 Koht ahpw sapeng, mahsanih, “Mehn Israel oh Suda wiadahr dihp kan me inenen suwed. Re kemelahr aramas wasa koaros nan sahpwo oh kadirehkilahr Serusalem dihp. Re nda me ngehi, KAUN-O, keselahr sapwarailo oh dene I sohte mahsanih irail.
\v 10 Ahpw I sohte pahn poakeirailla; I pahn dupukohng irail dahme re wiahiong meteikan.”
\p 
\v 11 Eri, ohl me mi nan likou lineno ahpw pwurodo oh pakairkihong KAUN-O, “I kapwaiadahr sapwellimomwi koasoandi.”
\c 10
\s1 Lingan en KAUN-O Sohrasang nan Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 1 I kilengla pohn moangen menmour ko\f h \fr 10:1 \fk MENMOUR kO: \ft Tehk 1.5-12.\f* oh kilangada mehkot me mwomwen mwoahl ehu me wiawihkihda kisin takai kesempwal me adaneki sapair. \x - \xo 10:1 \xt Esek. 1.26; Kaud. 4.2.\x*
\p 
\v 2 Koht ahpw mahsanihong ohl me mi nan likou lineno, “Kohwei nanpwungen mehn kadahr ko me mi pahn menmour ko oh audehkihda nan pehmwen mwoalus okohk. Kowe eri kamwerepeseng mwoalus ko nan kahniwmo pwon.”\x - \xo 10:2 \xt Kaud. 8.5.\x*
\p Ngehi eri mwasamwasahn ohlo eh kohkohla.
\v 3 Menmour ko wie kesikesihnen ni palieier en Tehnpas Sarawio ni ahnsou me ohlo pedolongala, oh pelien depwek pali ahpw kadirehla masloalen kehlo.
\v 4 Marain lingaling en KAUN-O ahpw mwekididahsang pohn menmour ko oh mwekidlahng ni wenihmwen Tehnpas Sarawio. Pelien depweko ahpw kadirehla nan Tehnpas Sarawio, oh nan kehlo ahpw wie lingalingki maraino.
\v 5 Ngilen menmour ko ahpw peipeilahng maslikin kehlo. E mwomwen kapitien Koht Wasa Lapalap.
\p 
\v 6 Ni ahnsou me KAUN-O ketin ruwese ohl me mi nan likou lineno en ale ekei mwoalus sang nanpwungen mehn kadahr ko me mi pahn menmour ko, ohlo ahpw pedolongala oh kesihnenda limwahn ehu mehn kadahr ko.
\v 7 Emen menmour ko ahpw kapahla peho nan kisinieio me mi nanpwungarail, pwekada mwoalus ko, oh kihdiong nan pehn ohl me mi nan likou lineno. Ohlo eri ale mwoalus ko oh kohkohla.
\p 
\v 8 I ahpw kilangada me emenemen menmour ko mie mehkot me mwomwen pehn aramas mi pahn ehuehu ar pehnpihr kan.
\v 9-10 I pil kilangada me mehn kadahr pahieu, koaros duwepenehte, ehuehu mi limwahn emenemen menmour ko. Mehn kadahr ko me lingaling duwehte kisin takai kesempwal, oh ehuehu mehn kadahr ko pil mie ehu mehn kadahr me pangapang loale.\x - \xo 10:9-10 \xt Esek. 1.15-21.\x*
\v 11 Ni ahnsou me menmour ko kin mwekid, re kak kohla wasa koaros ahpw sohte pirekekseli. Irail koaros kin wiakinteieu mwekidla wasa me re men kohla ie, re sohte kin pirekek.
\v 12 Paliwararail, tihnsewerail, pehrail, ar pehnpihr kan, oh mehn kadahr kan kidikidkihla pwoaren mas.\x - \xo 10:12 \xt Kaud. 4.8.\x*
\v 13 Mehn kadahr pwukat duwehte me I kilangehr nan kaudiahl keieuo.
\p 
\v 14 Emenemen menmour ko mas pahieu. Me keieuo mesen kouwol, me keriauo mesen aramas, me kesiluhwo mesen laion, oh me kapahieuo mesen ikel.\x - \xo 10:14 \xt Esek. 1.10; Kaud. 4.7.\x*
\v 15 (Menmourkohte me I kilangehr limwahn Pillap Separ.) Ni ahnsou me menmour ko kohda nan wehwe
\v 16 oh mwekid, mehn kadahr ko pil iang irail. Ni ahnsou me re kin kapapeseng ar pehnpihr kan pwe re en pihr, mehn kadahr ko pil kin iang irail.
\v 17 Ni ahnsou me menmour ko kin uhdi, mehn kadahr ko pil kin uhdi; oh ni ahnsou me menmour ko kin pihr, mehn kadahr ko pil kin iang irail, pwehki re mihmi pahn manaman en menmour ko.
\p 
\v 18 Eri, marain lingaling en KAUN-O ahpw mwekidsang ni wehnimwen Tehnpas Sarawio oh mwekidlahng wasa kis pohnangin menmour ko.
\v 19 Re kapapeseng ar pehnpihr kan oh pihrdahsang pohn sampah nindokon ei kilikilang, oh mehn kadahr ko pil iang irail. Re ahpw uhdi limwahn ewen kelen palimesehn Tehnpas Sarawio, oh marain lingalingo mi pohnangirail.
\v 20 I kadehdehda me iei irail menmourkohte me I kilangehr me mi pahn Koht en Israel ni Pillap Separ.
\p 
\v 21 Emenemen irail mas pahieu, pehnpihr pahieu, oh mwomwen pehn aramas mi pahn ehuehu ar pehnpihr ko.
\v 22 Masarail ko duwehte mas ko me I kilangehr limwahn Pillap Separ. Emenemen menmour ko kin mwekidlahte sohte pirekekseli.
\c 11
\s1 Serusalem Pakadeikada
\p 
\v 1 Ngenen Koht ahpw pwekiehda oh ketikinielahng ni ewen kelen palimesehn Tehnpas Sarawio. I ahpw kilangada wasao limwahn kehlo ohl riehk limmen, me iangahki Saasanaia nein Asur oh Pelataia nein Penaia, kaun riemen en wehio.
\p 
\v 2 Koht eri mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, ohl pwukat kin wiewia koasoandi suwed oh kihda kaweid suwed nan kahnimwet.
\v 3 Re kin nda, ‘Kereniongehr kitail pahn pwurehng kauwada ihmw kan. Kahnimwo duwehte einpwoat ehu, oh kitail duwehte uduk me mi loale, ahpw einpwoato pil doarehsang kitail kisiniei.’
\v 4 Eri met, kerieirailla, kowe, nein aramas.”
\p 
\v 5 Ngenen KAUN-O ahpw ti pohi, oh KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong ie I en patohwanohng aramas akan mahsen wet: “Kumwail mehn Israel kan, I ese dahme kumwail ndinda oh koasoakoasoane.
\v 6 Kumwail kemelahr aramas tohto nan kahnimwet me kahrehda ahl akan direkilahr paliweren aramas mehla.
\p 
\v 7 “Eri, iet me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong kumwail. Me pwung amwail nda me kahnimw wet iei einpwoat ehu, ahpw ia uduken? Iei paliweren irail kan me kumwail kemelahr! Kumwail sohte pahn mihmi wasaht—I pahn kesei kumwail sang nan kahnimwo!
\v 8 Kumwail kin masak kedlahs? I pahn ketikihdo aramas me pahn wisik kedlahs pwe re en mahweniong kumwail.
\v 9 I pahn weikumwailsang nan kahnimwo oh pangkumwaillahng mehn liki kan. I koasoanedier kumwail en kamakamala,
\v 10 oh kumwail pahn kamala nan mahwen nan pein sapwamwailo. Eri, aramas koaros ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.
\v 11 Kahnimw wet sohte pahn doareikumwailla duwehte einpwoat eh kin doare uduk me mi loale. I pahn kalokei kumwail wasa koaros me kumwail mihmi ie nan wehin Israel.
\v 12 Kumwail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, oh ni amwail kolokol kosonned kan en wehi kan me karanih kumwail, kumwail kauwelahr ei Kosonned kan oh sapeikiong ei Mahsen kan.”
\p 
\v 13 Nindokon ei wiewia ei kokohp, Pelataia ahpw pwupwudi mehla. I ahpw poarikihdi meseiet nanpwel oh weriwerki, patohwan, “Soh, maing KAUN, Wasa Lapalahpie! Ia duwe, komwi pahn kemehla aramas koaros me luhwehdi nan Israel?”
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Inou ong me Kalipilipala ko
\p 
\v 14 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie,
\v 15 “Kowe, nein aramas, aramas akan me koukousoan nan Serusalem wie koasoakoasoia duwen kowe oh iengomw mehn Israel kan me kalipilipala. Re ndinda, ‘Me kalipilipala ko me nohn doh oh sohte kak kaudokiong KAUN-O. E ketikihongehr kitail en sapwenikihla sahpwo.’
\p 
\v 16 “Eri, ndahng iengomw me kalipilipala ko dahme I mahmahsanih. Iei ngehi me kadarirailla pwe re en kousoanla nan wehi doh oh pil kamwarakiraillahng nan wehi teikan. Ahpw, erein ekis ahnsou I pahn ieiang irail nan sahpw me re kousoanlahr ie.
\p 
\v 17 “Eri, ndahng irail dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih. I pahn kapwureiraildo sang nan sahpw akan me I kamwarakiraillahng ie, oh kapwuredohng irail wehin Israel.
\v 18 Ni ar pahn pwurodo, re pahn kesehla ar wiewia samin, oh dikedik en eni saut kan me re pahn diar.
\v 19 I pahn ketikihong irail mohngiong kapw oh lamalam kapw. I pahn ketikihsang ar mohngiong keptakai kan oh ketikihong irail mohngiong peik.\x - \xo 11:19 \xt Esek. 36.26-28.\x*
\v 20 Eri, re ahpw pahn kapwaiada ei kosonned kan oh peikiong ni loalopwoat ei mahsen koaros. Re pahn wiahla nei aramas oh I pahn wiahla ar Koht.
\v 21 Ahpw I pahn kaloke irail kan me kin poakohng wiewia samin, oh dikedik en eni saut kan. I pahn kalokehkin irail dahme re wiadahr.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Lingan Sohrasang Serusalem
\p 
\v 22 Menmour ko ahpw tepida pihrda, oh mehn kadahr ko iang irail. Marain lingaling en Koht en Israel mi pohnangirail.\x - \xo 11:22 \xt Esek. 43.2-5.\x*
\v 23 Marain lingalingo ahpw mwekidsang nan kahnimwo oh mwekidlahng nin nahno ni palimese.
\v 24 Nan kaudiahlo ngenen Koht ahpw pwekiehda oh kapwureiedohng wasa me I kalipilipala ie nan Papilonia. Kaudiahlo eri sohrala,
\v 25 ngehi eri ndahng me kalipilipala ko mehkoaros me KAUN-O ketin kasalehiong ie.
\c 12
\s1 Soukohpo nin duwen Aramas me Sopohsang nan Apwal
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, ke wie koukousoan nanpwungen aramas kahngohdi kei. Mie pwoaren masarail, ahpw sohte mehkot re kilang; mie salengarail, ahpw sohte mehkot re rong, pwehki ar kahngohdi.\x - \xo 12:2 \xt Ais. 6.9-10; Ser.5.21; Mk. 8.18.\x*
\p 
\v 3 “Eri met, nein aramas, wahda omw koruk nin duwen aramas emen me kin sopohsang nan apwal kin wia oh mweselda mwohn eh pahn wasa pwong. Aramas koaros en kilang omw pahn mweselda oh kolahng nan ehu wasa. Mweinele aramas kahngohdi pwuko pahn tehkuhkada.
\v 4 Ni eh pahn rarahnte, ke pahn kihpene omw koruk en kalipilipala, pwe re en kak kilang uhk, oh re en kilang omw pahn mweselda nin soutik rasehng ma ke kalipilipala.
\v 5 Nindokon ar pahn kilikilang, wiahda ehu pwoahr ni dihd en imwomwo oh duwaleisang nan ihmwo wa omw koruk en.
\v 6 Re en kilang omw pahn kidahng omw koruk en pohn pwopwomw oh kohkohla nan roto perepere mesomwen, pwe ke en dehr kilang wasa me ke kohkohla ie. Dahme ke pahn wia iei kehkehlik ehu ong mehn Israel kan.”
\p 
\v 7 Ngehi eri kapwaiada dahme KAUN-O mahsanihong ie I en wia. Ni rahno I wiahda ei koruk ehu nin duwen aramas me kin sopohsang nan apwal, oh nin soutiko ni eh wie rotorotpene I ahpw wiahkihda pwoahr ehu pehi kat ni dihdo oh pwediei ie. Nindokon aramas koaros ar kilikilang, I ahpw kidahng koruko pohn pwopwei oh kohkohla.
\p 
\v 8 Mandahn rahno KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong ie,
\v 9 “Kowe, nein aramas, pwehki mehn Israel kahngohdi pwuko ar idihdek rehmw dahme ke wiewia,
\v 10 ndahng irail dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong irail. Mahsen wet iei ong soupeidio me kakaun nan Serusalem oh ong aramas koaros me koukousoan wasao.
\v 11 Ndahng irail me dahme ke wiahier iei kilel ehu en dahme pahn wiawihong irail—re pahn wiahla aramas me tangatangasang nan apwal oh wiahla aramas selidi kei.
\v 12 Soupeidi me kakaunirailo pahn wahda eh koruk nan rot oh pwediei nan pwoahr ehu me re pahn wiahda ni kehlo. E pahn perehla mese oh sohte kilang wasa me e kohkolahng ie.
\v 13 Ahpw I pahn pahkpeseng ei uhk oh lidipihediong loale. I ahpw pahn ketikilahng nan kahnimw Papilon, wasa e pahn mehla ie sohte kilang wasao.\x - \xo 12:13 \xt 2 Nan. 25.7; Ser. 52.11.\x*
\v 14 I pahn kamwarakpeseng wasa koaros tohn tehnpese koaros, iangahki sapwellime sounkaweid oh silepe kan, oh aramas akan pahn rapahkin irail pwe re en kemeirailla.
\p 
\v 15 “Ni ei pahn kamwarakirailpeseng nanpwungen wehi teikan oh nan wehin liki kan, re ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.
\v 16 I pahn mweidohng pwe me malaulau rehrail en pitsang mahwen oh lehk lapalapo, oh soumwahu kan, pwe re en esehla wasao nanpwungen wehi ko duwen kasaut en ar wiewia kan oh esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.”
\s1 Kilel en Sokohp me wie Rerrer
\p 
\v 17 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 18 “Kowe, nein aramas, rerrer ni omw pahn mwenge, oh rerrerki omw masapwehk ni omw pahn nimpil.
\v 19 Ndahng wehio pwon me met iei mahsen sang rehn KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ong mehn Serusalem me wie koukousoante nan sapwarailo: Re pahn rerrer ni ar pahn mwenge oh rerrerki ar masepwehk ni ar pahn nimpil. Sapwarailo pahn tehnla, pwehki koaros me koukousoan wasao ar sehse kosonned.
\v 20 Kahnimw kan me diren aramas met pahn mwomwla, oh sahpwo pahn wiahla sapwtehn. Eri, re ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.”
\s1 Lepin Kahs Ndand oh Mahsen me Kansensuwed
\p 
\v 21 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 22 “Kowe, nein aramas, dahme mehn Israel kan kin ndindahki lepin kahs wet: ‘Rahn akan imwiseklahr, oh kokohp kan sohte pweida’?
\v 23 Eri, ndahng irail dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, pahn mahsaniheki duwen met. I pahn katokihedi lepin kahso. Solahr me pahn pwurehng wia kahso nan wehin Israel. Ahpw ke pahn ndahng irail met: Ahnsowo leledohr, oh kokohp kan pahn pweidahr!
\p 
\v 24 “Solahr kaudiahl likamw de kokohp likamw pahn wiawi rehn mehn Israel kan.
\v 25 Ngehi, KAUN-O, pahn mahseniong irail, oh dahme I pahn mahsanih pahn pweida. Solahr pahn pwapwand. Kumwail kin kahngohdi erein amwail momour, I pahn kapwaiadahr dahme I kahkehlingkihong kumwail me I pahn wia. Ngehi me mahmahsen.” Met iei mahsen en KAUN-O
\p 
\v 26 KAUN-O ketin mahsaniong ie,
\v 27 “Kowe, nein aramas, mehn Israel kan lemeleme me omw kaudiahl oh kokohp kan saikinte pahn leledo.
\v 28 Eri, ndahng irail me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Solahr pahn pwapwand. Dahme I mahsanih pahn pweida. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen!”
\c 13
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Ohl Soukohp Likamw akan
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla soukohp en Israel kan me kin pein wiahda ar kokohp kan. Ndaiong irail en rong mahsen en KAUN-O.”
\p 
\v 3 Iet me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie mahsanih: “Meid suwediong soukohp pweipwei pwukat! Re kin pein wiahda audepen nan kapehdirail oh kin kinehda ar kaudiahl akan.
\v 4 Kumwail mehn Israel kan, sohte katepen amwail soukohp kan; re rasehng kidi en wel kan me kin koukousoan nan mohn ihmw kan.
\v 5 Re sohte kin sinsile wasa me rengkdier ni kehl kan, de re sohte kin onehda kehl kan; ihme kahrehda Israel sohte pahn kak doarehla pein ih ni ahnsou me rahnen KAUN-O pahn leledo.
\v 6 Ar kaudiahl akan sohte mehlel, oh ar kokohp akan me likamw. Re kin nda me re kin kohpada ei mahsen, ahpw kaidehn ngehi me kadarirailwei. Re ahpw kin kose me ar lokaia kan pahn pweida!
\v 7 I kin mahsanihong irail: Kaudiahl ko me kumwail kilikilang sohte mehlel, oh kokohp kan me kumwail wiahda me likamw. Kumwail kin nda me ei mahsen me kumwail koasoakoasoia, ahpw I sohte mwahn mahseniong kumwail!”
\p 
\v 8 Eri, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ahpw mahsanihong irail, “Amwail koasoi kan sohte mehlel, oh amwail kaudiahl kan me likamw. I uhdahn uhwong kumwail.
\v 9 I nektehn kaloke kumwail soukohp kan me kin wia kaudiahl me sohte mehlel oh kin wia keseu ong ni ahnsou kohkohdo kan me pahn kaweidsuwdihala aramas akan. Kumwail sohte pahn iang mi wasao ni ahnsou me nei aramas akan pahn pokonpene pwe re en wie lamalam; adamwail kan sohte pahn iang mi nan wadawad en tohn Israel; kumwail sohte pahn pwuralahng nan uhdakamwailo. Eri, kumwail ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie.
\p 
\v 10 “Soukohp kan kaweidsuwedihalahr nei aramas akan ni ar ndinda me mehkoaros me mwahu. Ahpw mehkoaros sohte mwahu! Nei aramas akan kauwadahr kelen takai luwet ehu, oh mwuhr soukohp kan ahpw kohdo oh litoapwieki litoapw pwetepwet.\x - \xo 13:10 \xt Ser. 6.14; 8.11.\x*
\v 11 Ndaiong soukohp kan me arail kehlo pahn pwupwudi. I pahn kadarodo ehu keteu laud. Keteu aihs takai pahn mweredi powe, oh kisinieng kehlail pahn ipirala.
\v 12 Kehlo pahn ohla, oh aramas koaros pahn idek rehmw ia kahrepen litoapw pwetepweto.”
\v 13 Eri, iet me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih: “Nan ei engieng I pahn kadarodo ehu kisinieng kehlail, keteu laud, oh keteu aihs takai pwehn kauwehla kehlo.
\v 14 I koasoanedier I en kauwehla kehlo me re litoapwieki litopw pwetepwet; I en kamwerehdi, oh kapwarehda takai kan me wia poahsoane. E pahn rengkidi oh kemehla kumwail koaros. Eri, aramas koaros ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 15 “Kehlo iangahki irail kan me litoapwieki litoapw pwetepwet pahn kehn engin ei engieng. Eri, I ahpw pahn mahsanihong uhk me kehlo sohralahr iangahki irail kan me litoapwieki litoapw pwetepwet—
\v 16 soukohp pwuko me kohpadahng Serusalem me dene mehkoaros me mwahu, ni mehkoaros eh sohte mwahu!” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Lih Soukohp Likamw akan
\p 
\v 17 KAUN-O ketin mahsanih, “Eri, kowe, nein aramas, kilang lih akan me mihmi nanpwungen noumw aramas akan, me kin kasawih ahnsou kohkohdo kan. Kerieirailla,
\v 18 oh ndaiong irail dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong irail:
\p “Meid suwediong kumwail lih akan! Kumwail kin wiahda kisin ngkoal en silasil mehn kohieng ni pehn aramas koaros oh koaduhpwel sarawi mehn kodahng pohn moangarail kan, pwe re en kak ahneki manaman pohn mour en aramas teikan. Kumwail men ahnekihla manaman en kihong mour oh mehla ong nei aramas akan, oh doadoahngki pwehn wia kamwahupamwail.
\v 19 Kumwail kihsang wauwi mwohn mesen nei aramas akan pwe kumwail en alehki kisin oaroahr en parli kis oh kisin sansar en pilawa kei. Kumwail kemehla aramas akan me sohte konehng en mehla, oh kumwail kolokol mour en aramas akan me sohte konehng en momour. Kumwail ahpw ndaiong nei aramas akan koasoi likamw, re ahpw kamehlele kumwail.”
\p 
\v 20 Eri, iet dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih: “I kalahdeki kisin ngkoal kan me kumwail kin doadoahngki pwe kumwail en ahneki manaman ong mour oh mehla. I pahn dapengasang pehmwail kan oh kasaledekihala aramas akan me milahr pahn amwail manaman.
\v 21 I pahn tehrasang amwail koaduhpwel kan oh mweidohng nei aramas akan en pitsang pahn amwail manaman met oh kohkolahte. Kumwail eri pahn esehla me ngehi KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 22 “Amwail likamw akan katoutouwihalahr nan kapehd en aramas mwahu kan, irail kan me I sohte men kaloke. Kumwail kerempwahla aramas suwed kan pwe re en dehr pwilikihdi ar suwed oh doarehla ar mour.
\v 23 Eri met, amwail kaudiahl me sohte mehlel kan oh keseu ong ahnsou kohkohdo kan mehn kaweidsuwedih aramas akan imwiseklahr. I pahn kapitala nei aramas akan sang pahn amwail manaman, pwe kumwail en esehla me ngehi KAUN-O.”
\c 14
\s1 Koht ketin Keriahla Dikedik en Eni kan
\p 
\v 1 Ekei kaunen mehn Israel ko ahpw patohdo rehi pwe re en ale kaweid duwen kupwur en KAUN-O.
\v 2 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie,
\v 3 “Kowe, nein aramas, ohl pwukat pangalahr mohngiongirail kan ong dikedik en eni kan oh mweidalahr pwe dikedik en eni kan en kahrehiong irail nan dihp. Ke lemeleme me I pahn kak kasalehiong irail ei pasapeng?
\p 
\v 4 “Eri, lokaiaiong irail oh padahkihong irail dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong irail: Mehn Israel men me pangalahr eh mohngiong ong dekedik en eni kan oh kahrehiong ih nan dihp, e ahpw pahn kohdo pwehn ale kaweid rehn soukohp men, pahn ale pasapeng sang rehi—pasapeng me konehng nah dikedik en eni ngeder kan!
\v 5 Dikedik en eni pwuko koaros kahredahr mehn Israel kan ar sohpeisang ie, ahpw sang nan ei pasapeng I koapworopworki me I pahn kapwureiraildohng nan ar loalopwoat.
\p 
\v 6 “Eri met, ndaiong mehn Israel kan dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Kumwail pwurodo oh kesehla noumwail dikedik en eni saut kan.
\p 
\v 7 “Ni ahnsou me emen mehn Israel kan de emen mehn liki kan me koukousoan rehn mehn Israel kan pahn sohpeisang ie oh pwongih dikedik en eni kan, oh mwuhr e ahpw kohla pwehn ale kaweid rehn soukohp men, ngehi, KAUN-O, me pahn kihong ei pasapeng!
\v 8 I pahn uhwong. I pahn wiahkihla ih mehn karasepe ehu. I pahn katohrehsang ih nanpwungen nei aramas akan, pwe kumwail en esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 9 “Ma soukohp men pahn wiahda kokohp likamw, met pwehki ngehi, KAUN-O, me kupwurehda en wiahda kokohp likamw. I pahn katohrehsang rehn mehn Israel kan.
\v 10 Soukohpo oh mehmeno me ale kaweid sang reh pahn ale soangen kalokolok teieu.
\v 11 I pahn wia met pwehn kolokol mehn Israel kan pwe re dehr sohpeisang ie oh kasaminehkihla pein irail diparail kan. Iei irail nei aramas, oh ngehi me ar Koht.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\s1 Noha, Danel, oh Sohp
\p 
\v 12 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 13 “Kowe, nein aramas, ma wehi ehu pahn wiahda dihp oh soaloalopwoatohng ie, I pahn kapahla limei oh kamwomwala eh wahnsahpw akan. I pahn kadarodo lehk lapalap oh kemehla aramas oh mahn akan.
\v 14 Mehnda ma ohl silimeno, Noha, Danel,\f i \fr 14:14 \fk DANEL: \ft De Daniel (tehk 28.3), ohl ndand men, me aramas akan pil wehwehki duwen eh mour poadidi.\f* oh Sohp, iang koukousoan wasao, ar lelepek pahn doarehlahte pein ar mour.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\p 
\v 15 “De I pahn kadarodo mahn lawalo pwehn kemehla aramas akan me kahredahr sahpwo eh keperlahr oh solahr me kak seiloak kotehla sahpwo,
\v 16 oh pil mehnda ma ohl silimeno koukousoan wasao—nin duwen ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, Koht ieias emen—re sohte pahn pil kak doarehla pein nair seri kan. Re pahn doarehlahte pein irail, oh sahpwo pahn wiahla sapwtehn ehu.
\p 
\v 17 “De I pahn kadarodo mahwen pohn sahpwo oh kadarodo tehtehn mahwen kehlail pwehn koakoahsang aramas akan oh mahn akan,
\v 18 oh pil mehnda ma ohl silimeno koukousoan wasao—nin duwen ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, Koht ieias emen—re sohte pahn pil kak doarehla pein nair seri kan, ahpw arail mour kelehpw.
\p 
\v 19 “Ma I pahn kadarodo soumwahu lusulus pohn sahpwo oh kihsang mour en me ngeder nan ei engieng, kemehla aramas oh mahn akan,
\v 20 mehnda ma Noha, Danel, oh Sohp koukousoan wasao—I kahukihla nin duwen ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, Koht ieias emen—re sohte pahn kak en doarehla pein nair seri kan. Arail lelepek pahn doarehla pein ar mour kelehpw.”
\p 
\v 21 Iei met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: “I pahn kadarodo ei kalokolok keieu suwed pahieu pohn Serusalem— mahwen, lehk lapalap, mahn lawalo, oh soumwahu—pwehn kemehla aramas oh mahn koaros.\x - \xo 14:21 \xt Kaud. 6.8.\x*
\v 22 Ma mehmen pahn pitla oh doarehla nah seri, tehk mwomwarail ni ar pahn pwarodo rehmwail. Tehk mwomwen ar suwed, oh kumwail en esehla me kalokolok me I pahn ketikidohng pohn Serusalem me pwung;
\v 23 kumwail eri pahn esehla me mie kahrepe mwahu ehu me kahredahr ei wiahda soahng pwukat koaros.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\c 15
\s1 Karasaras en Tuhkehn Wain
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, ia duwen tuhkehn wain pwoat eh pahn kapahrekiong apwoat tuhke? Ia katepen rahntuhkehn wain pwoat eh pahn kapahrekiong tuhke kan nanwel?
\v 3 Ke kak doadoahngki pwe ke en wiahkihda mehkot? Ke pil kak wiahkihda kisin tuhke mehn mehkot en tenekida ie?
\v 4 Pwe e mwahuongete en wia mehn saunda kisiniei. Oh ni ahnsou me imwin rah kan kin luluda oh nanwerengen tuhkeo kin mwasikala, mie mehkot e kak wiahda?
\v 5 Sohte katepen tuhkeo mehnda ma e saikinte mwasikala. Eri, ni eh mwasikalahr, e ahpw sohla katepe douluhl.”
\p 
\v 6 Eri, iet me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie ketin mahmahsanih: “Nin duwen tuhkehn wain pwoat eh kin wisiksang nanwel oh isihsla, iei duwen ei pahn ale aramas akan me koukousoan nan Serusalem
\v 7 oh kalokei irail. Re pitsangehr ehu kisiniei, ahpw met kisiniei pahn kamwasikeirailla. Ni ei pahn kaloke irail, kumwail pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\v 8 Re soaloalopwoatohng ie, ihme kahrehda ei pahn wiahkihla sahpwo sapwtehn ehu.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\c 16
\s1 Serusalem Kahnimw Soaloalopwoato
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ahpw pwurehng mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, padokehng Serusalem soahng saut kan me e wiadahr.
\v 3 Padahkihong Serusalem dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong:
\p “Ke ipwidi nan wehin Kenan. Omw pahpa mehn Amor, oh omw nohno mehn Id.\f j \fr 16:3 \fk AMOR...ID: \ft Mehn Israel kan kin wiahki aramas pwukat, aramas dipan oh kin kaudok ong dikedik en eni.\f*
\v 4 Ni ahnsou me ke ipwidi, sohte emen me lupukasang selin omw pwuhs de duhpuhkada de iriskin uhk soahl de kidimkinuhkpene likou.
\v 5 Sohte me poakeiukala oh wiahiong uhk soahng pwukat. Ni ahnsou me ke ipwidio, sohte emen me poakohng uhk. Ke lekdekla nansapw.
\p 
\v 6 “I ahpw keid wasao oh mahsanihada omw wie weriwer nan pein ntahmw. Nta kidimala paliweromw, ahpw I sohte mweidohng ke en mehla.
\v 7 I kakairuhkada duwehte kisin tuhke kehlail kis. Ke ahpw kehlailla oh reireila oh wiahla peinakapw emen. Omw dihdi kan inenen kaselel, oh pitenmoangomw kan reirei, ahpw ke kilisou.
\p 
\v 8 “Ni ei pwurehng keid wasao, I ahpw tehkada me e lelehr ahnsoun omw ale omw mwohnlimpoak. I ahpw kidimkihla ei likou puhp paliweromw oh inoukihda me I pahn poakohng uhk. Ei, I wiadahr inoun pwopwoud nanpwungata, oh ke wialahr ei pwoud.” Iei met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie ketin mahsanih.
\p 
\v 9 “Ngehi eri ale pihl oh widensang nta rehmw. I keiehki lehn olip pohn kilimw.
\v 10 I ahpw kapwuhrehng uhk nan likou reirei deiad oh ketikihong uhk suht kilin kou kaselel, koaduhpwel linen, oh likou puhp silik ehu.
\v 11 I kapwatahkinuhkada kisin takai kesempwal—liwou oh mwaramwar.
\v 12 I ketikihong uhk ehu rihng en ni tumwomw oh tiati oh nihn kaselel ehu pwe ke en kidahng pohn moangomw.
\v 13 Ke ahneki mehn kapwat kohl oh silper, oh ke kin likawih likou linen oh silik ahnsou koaros. Ke kin kang pilawa sang ni pilawa me keieu mwahu, oh kin kang sukehn loangalap oh lehn olip. Omw kaselel me inenen kamahl, ke ahpw wiahla lih nanmwarki men.
\v 14 Ke ndandkihla nan wehi koaros omw kaselel, pwehki ngehi me wiahda omw kaselelen.” Iei met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih.
\p 
\v 15 “Ke ahpw engimwahukihla omw kaselel oh ndand, kowe eri kin wia nsenen pwopwoud ong ohl koaros me kohdo rehmw.
\v 16 Ke doadoahngki ekei omw likou kaselel kan pwe ke en kapwatahkihda omw wasahn kaudok kan, ke duwehla lihen netiki paliwere men me kin wia nsenen pwopwoud ong ohl koaros.
\v 17 Ke ale kisin takai kohl oh silper kan me I ketikihong uhk, wiahkihda sansal en ohl, oh wiahda dipen kamwahl ong irail.
\v 18 Ke ale likou deiad kan me I ketikihong uhk oh kidahng pohn sansal ko, ke ahpw meirongkihong sansal ko lehn olip oh warpwohmwahu me I ketikihong uhk.
\v 19 I ketikihong uhk mwenge—pilawa keieu kaselel, lehn olip, oh sukehn loangalap—ahpw ke wiahkihla mehn meirong ong dikedik en eni kan pwe ke en kenkenla pahrail.” Iei met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih.
\p 
\v 20 “Ke ale pwutak oh serepein kan me ke wiahiong ie oh wiahkihla mehn meirong ong dikedik en eni kan. Ia duwe, e sohte itar omw soaloalopwoatohng ie,
\v 21 a ke pil ale nei seri kan oh meirongkihong dikedik en eni kan?
\v 22 Erein omw mihmi nan mour saut en wiewia lihen netiki paliwere men, ke sohte mwahn tamanda pak ehu duwen omw tikitik— ni ahnsou me ke kilisouwo, wie weriwer nan ntahmw.”
\s1 En Serusalem eh Mour en Netiki Paliwere
\p 
\v 23 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie ketin mahsanih, “Meid suwediong uhk! Meid suwed! Ke wiadahr me suwed pwuko, oh mwuhr
\v 24 ke ahpw kauwada ni keilen ahl koaros wasahn kaudok ong dikedik en eni kan oh wasahn wia tiahk en netiki paliweromw.
\v 25 Ke ruwahdekiseli omw lingan nan pwelmatak. Ke mweidala paliweromw ong koaros me kohdo rehmw, oh omw tiahk en netiki paliweromw wie lalaudla rahn koaros.
\v 26 Ke mweidohng mehn mpomw, mehn Isip ineng suwed kan, re en wiahda nsenen pwoupwoud ong uhk, ke ahpw wiewia omw tiahk en netiki paliweromw pwe ke en kahngiangihkin ie.
\p 
\v 27 “Eri, met I ketikidahr limei pwe I en kalokeiuk oh adihasang pai kan me I ketikihong uhk. I panguhkalahr rehn mehn Pilisdia kan, me kin kailongkin uhk oh sautiki omw wiewia suwed kan.
\p 
\v 28 “Pwehki omw sohte itarki meteikan me kahredahr omw pil pwakipwakih mehn Asiria kan. Ke wia neirail lihen netiki paliwere, ahpw re pil sohte kin kansenamwahwihiuk.
\v 29 Ke pil wia lihen netiki paliweromw ong mehn Papilonia kan, wehi me towe kan kin netiki dipwisou, ahpw re pil sohte kansenamwahwihiuk.”
\p 
\v 30 Iet me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: “Ke wiadahr mepwukat koaros duwehte lihen netiki paliwere men me sehse namenek.
\v 31 Ke kauwadahr wasahn kaudok ong dikedik en eni kan pohn ahl koaros oh wasahn wia tiahk en netiki paliweromw. Ahpw ke sohte raparapahki mwohni duwen me lihen netiki paliwararail kan kin wiewia.
\v 32 Ke duwehte lih emen me sohte kin poakohng eh pwoud ahpw kin wiahda dipen kamwahl ong mehn liki kan.
\v 33 Lihen netiki paliwere men kin ale pweinen paliwere, ahpw, kowe, ke kin mwarkihla omw dipwisou kan ong omw kerir kan oh pwainohng irail pwe re en kohdo sang wasa koaros oh wendi rehmw.
\v 34 Ehu soangen omw wia tiahk en netiki paliweromw. Sohte emen me idingkin uhk ke en wia tiahk wet. Ke sohte ale pweinomw; kowe me kin pwain irail! Ei, ke weksang lihen netiki paliwere men.”
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Kadeik ong Serusalem
\p 
\v 35 Eri met, kowe Serusalem, lih tiahk suwed! Rong dahme KAUN-O mahmahsanih.
\p 
\v 36 Iet me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih: “Ke kapwuhrasang omw likou kan, oh wiahda duwehte lihen netiki paliwere men, ke pangalahng paliweromw rehn omw kerir oh ong noumw dikedik en eni saut kan, oh ke kemehla noumw seri kan wiahkihla mehn meirong ong dikedik en eni kan.
\v 37 Pwehki met me kahrehda ei pahn ketikipene omw kerir en mahs ako—me ke kin mwahuki ko oh me ke kin kailongki ko. I pahn ketikiniraildo oh kapilkinuhkpene, I ahpw pahn kapwuhrasang omw likou oh mweidohng re en kilang uhk nan omw kilisou.
\v 38 I pahn kadeikada omw dipen kamwahl oh kamaramas, oh nan ei engieng kowahlap I pahn kalokehkin uhk mehla.
\v 39 I pahn panguhkala pahn ar manaman, oh re pahn kamwerehdi wasa kan me ke kin wiewia ie omw tiahk en netiki paliweromw oh wiewia kaudok ong dikedik en eni kan. Re pahn kihsang omw likou kan oh omw kapwat akan oh keseiukala nan omw kilisou.
\p 
\v 40 “Re pahn pangepangenki ehu pokonen, en katehkin uhk takai, oh pelehkinuhkpene neirail kedlahs kan.
\v 41 Re pahn isikala imwomw kan oh mweidohng pokon en lih akan en kilang omw lokolok. I pahn katokihedi omw tiahk en netiki paliweromw oh katokihedi omw kin mwarehng omw kerir kan.
\v 42 Ei engieng ahpw pahn tokedi, oh I pahn meleileidi. I solahr pahn pwurehng engieng de luwak.
\v 43 Ke manokelahr duwen ei apwalihiuk ni omw tikitik, ke ahpw kahngiangihkiniedahr omw wiewia kan. Iei kahrepen ei kupwuredahr pwe ke en ale dupuken omw wiewia kan koaros. Dahme ke kapatahkihong tiahk en nenek ong omw tiahk saut teikan?” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\s1 Serepein men kin Tang Mwurin eh Nohno
\p 
\v 44 KAUN-O mahsanih, “Aramas akan pahn kin doadoahngki lepin kahs wet duwen kowe, Serusalem: ‘Daumwur ieu neitik.’
\v 45 Kowe uhdahn nein omw nohno. E sautikihla eh pwoud oh nah seri kan. Ke uhdahn duwehte riomw serepein kan, me kailongkihla ar pwoud kan oh nair seri kan. Kowe oh riomw serepein kahnimw kan nohnohki lihen Id men oh pahpahki ohl en Amor men.\f k \fr 16:45 \fk ID...AMOR: \ft Tehk 16.3.\f*
\p 
\v 46 “Iei Sameria, ni paliepeng, me wia riomw serepein laud, iangahki eh kisin kahnimw kan. Sodom, ni palieir, ianghki eh kisin kahnimw kan me wia riomw serepein tikitik.
\v 47 Ke itarki omw idawehn ar wiewia kan oh alasang ar wiewia saut kan? Soh, kisin ahnsou kis omw wiewia kan suwedsang arail kan ni mehkoaros me ke wiadahr.”
\p 
\v 48 KAUN-O ahpw mahsanih, “I kahukihla nin duwen ngehi Koht ieiaso, riomw serepein Sodom oh eh kisin kahnimw kan sohte mwahn wiahda soahng suwed kan me kowe oh omw kisin kahnimw kan wiadahr.
\v 49 Ih oh nah serepein kan pohnmwahsohki eh tohto kanarail kisin mwenge, oh mie popohl oh meleilei rehrail, ahpw re sohte kin apwalih me semwehmwe kan oh me milahr nan apwal akan.
\v 50 Re me aklapalap oh keptakai oh kin wiewia mehkan me I kin kalahdeki, ihme I kamwomwkinirailla, nin duwen me kumwail ese.
\p 
\v 51 “Dipen Sameria sohte lel elep en dihp me ke wiadahr. Omw wiewia kan suwedsang mehlel me e wiadahr. Omw tiahk suwed kahredahr likamwete sohte dipen riomw serepein kan.
\v 52 Oh met ke pahn ale kanamenekpomw. Dipomw kan me nohn suwedsang dipen riomw serepein ko me kahrehda likamwete sohte diparail. Eri, met ke en sarohdi oh toutoukihla omw namenek, pwehki omw kahredahr riomw serepein ko ar mwomwen sohte diparail.”
\s1 Sodom oh Sameria pahn Onohnda Sapahl
\p 
\v 53 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong Serusalem, “I pahn pwurehng kapaiairailda—Sodom oh eh kisin kahnimw kan oh Sameria oh eh kisin kahnimw kan. Ei, I pahn pil pwurehng kapaiaiukada.
\v 54 Ke pahn namenengkihda pein kowe, oh omw namenek pahn kasalehiong riomw serepein kan me re mwahusang uhk.
\v 55 Re pahn pwurehng paiamwahula, oh kowe oh omw kisin kousapw akan pahn pil pwurehng onohnda sapahl.
\v 56 Ke soh kepitki Sodom ni rahn pwuko me ke kin aklapalap,
\v 57 mwohn dipomw kan eh saikinte sansalada? Eri, met ke duwelahr ih—wialahr mehn kepit rehn mehn Edom kan, mehn Pilisdia kan, oh mehn mpomw teikan me kin kailongkin uhk.
\v 58 Ke uhdahn pahn lokolongki tiahk suwed oh saut kan me ke wiadahr.” KAUN-O me mahmahsen.
\s1 Inou me Poatopoat
\p 
\v 59 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie ketin mahsanih, “I pahn wiahiong uhk dahme konehng uhk, pwehki omw pohnsehsehla omw inou kan oh kauwehla inou lapo.
\v 60 Ahpw ngehi I pahn wauneki inou me I wiahiong uhk ni omw tikitik, oh I pil pahn wiahiong uhk ehu inou me pahn poatopoat kohkohlahte.
\v 61 Ke pahn tamanda duwen omw mwekid kan, oh namenengkihla ni ahnsou me ke pahn kapwurehdo riomw serepein laudo oh me tikitiko. I pahn kupwurehda pwe ira en duwehla noumw serepein, mehnda ma met sohte iang mihmi nan ei inou ong uhk.
\v 62 I pahn onehda sapahl ei inou ong uhk, oh ke pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\v 63 I pahn meliehla sapwung koaros me ke wiadahr, ahpw ke pahn tamatamante oh namenengki sarapeseng.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\c 17
\s1 Karasaras en Ikel oh Tuhkehn Wain
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, ndaiong mehn Israel kan karasaras ehu
\v 3 pwe re en ese dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong irail: Mie lapalahn ikel men me wune lingan oh eh pehnpihr kan inenen lapala. E ahpw pihrlahng pohn nahna kan en Lepanon oh katipwasang kadoken tuhke sidar pwoat,
\v 4 ih eri pihrkilahng rahntuhkeo ni sahpw en netinet ehu oh kihdiong nan kahnimw ehu en sounnetinet kan.
\v 5 E ahpw pil ale kisin tuhke pwulopwul kis sang nan wehin Israel oh padokedi nan sahpw pwelmwahu ehu, wasa me pihl kin mie ahnsou koaros pwehn kakairada.
\v 6 Kisin tuhkeo eri keirda oh wiahla tuhke wain losolos ehu. Rah ko uhdalahng rehn ikelo, oh kalowe kan kohdiong pahn pwehl. Tuhkehn waino inenen rarahn oh tehn.
\p 
\v 7 “Pil mie emen lapalahn ikel me eh pehnpihr kan pil lapala oh wune kan mosul mehlel. Eri, kalowen tuhkehn waino ahpw wosalahng reh oh pil rah kan penglahng wasa me ikelo mihmi ie, e koapworopowrki me e pahn kak ale pihl sang rehn ikelo me laudsang pihl me mi nan mwaht me e kekeirda ieo.
\v 8 Ahpw tuhkehn waino poadidier nan mwaht pwelmwahu, oh diren pihl pwe en kak losolos oh wahn oh wiahla tuhke kaselel pwoat.
\p 
\v 9 “Eri ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ahpw keinemwe: Ia duwe, tuhke pwoatet kak mour oh keirda? Keieun ikelo soh pahn usada kalowe kan oh kihsang wah kan, oh katipwasang rah kan oh mweidohng en mengila? E sohte anahne ehu wehi kehlail oh manaman en usadahsang.
\v 10 Ei, e poadidier, ahpw e pahn keirda oh mour? E soh pahn mengila ni ahnsou me kisinieng en palimese pahn lel? E soh pahn mengila wasa me e kekeirda ieo?”
\s1 Karasarso kawehwehda
\p 
\v 11 KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong ie,
\v 12 “Idek rehn aramas kahngohdi pwukat ma re ese wehwehn karasaraso. Ndaiong irail me nanmwarkien Papilonia ketidohr Serusalem oh ketikihsang nanmwarkio oh sapwellime lapalap akan oh ketikilahng Papilonia.\x - \xo 17:12 \xt 2 Nan. 24.15-20; 2 Kron. 36.10-13.\x*
\v 13 E ahpw ketikihla emen peneinei en nanmwarkio, oh wiahiong ih inou lap ehu, oh mahsanihong en kahukihla me e pahn loalopwoat. E ahpw salihedi ekei ohl kesempwal ko
\v 14 oh ketikihsang pwehn kak kerempwahla wehio en dehr uhwong oh re en dadaurete inou lapo.
\v 15 Ahpw nanmwarkien Suda pelianda oh kadarala meninkeder kei Isip pwe re en ale oahs oh karis en sounpei kalaimwun ehu. Ia duwe, e pahn kak pweida? E pahn kak pitsang ire wet? E sohte kak kauwehla inou lapo ahpw sohte ale kalokepe!”
\p 
\v 16 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ahpw mahsanih, “Nin duwen ngehi, Koht ieias, nanmwarki menet pahn sipalla nan Papilonia, pwehki eh kauwehla sapwellime kahula oh inou lapo me e wiahiong nanmwarkien Papilonia, me kasapwiladahng ih nan mwoale.
\v 17 Pil sapwellimen nanmwarkien Isip karis kehlailo sohte kak sewese mahwen ni ahnsou me mehn Papilonia kan pahn wiahda warawar oh mehn poadoandoar kei pwe re en kak kemehla aramas tohto.
\v 18 E kauwehla sapwellime kahula oh inou lapo me e wiadahr. E wiadahr soahng pwukat koaros, oh e sohte pahn pitsang.”
\p 
\v 19 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, eri mahsanih, “Nin duwen ngehi, Koht ieias, I pahn kalokehki eh kauwehla inou lapo me e kahukihla ni mwarei me e pahn dadaurete.
\v 20 I pahn pahkpeseng ei uhk oh kalowehdi loale. I pahn ketikilahng Papilonia oh kaloke wasao, pwehki e soaloalopwoatohng ie.
\v 21 Sapwellime sounpei keieu kehlail kan pahn mehla nan mahwen, oh me mourla kan pahn mwarahkpeseng wasa koaros. Eri, kumwail ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen.”
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Inoun Koapworopwor
\p 
\v 22 Iet me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih:
\q1 “I pahn ale ehu kadoken tuhke sidar
\q2 oh katipwasang apwoat kisin rah pwulopwul;
\q1 I ahpw pahn padokedi pohn nahna ileile ehu,
\q2 
\v 23 pohn nahna keieu ileile en Israel.
\q1 E ahpw pahn kadarala rah kan oh wa
\q2 oh wiahla tuhke sidar kaselel pwoat.
\q1 Soangen menpihr koaros pahn kousoan wasao
\q2 oh kin rukula pahn mweteh.
\q1 
\v 24 Tuhke koaros nan wehio pahn ese
\q2 me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\q1 Ngehi me lupukedi tuhke reirei kan
\q2 oh mweidohng tuhke mwotomwot kan en reireila.
\q1 Ngehi me kamangedi tuhke losolos kan
\q2 oh mweidohng tuhke meng kan en losolosala.
\m Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen. I pahn kapwaiada dahme I mahsaniher me I pahn wia.”
\c 18
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ahpw pil mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Ia kahrepen lepin padahk audapan pwoatet me mehn Israel kan kin ndinda nan wehin Israel?
\q1 ‘Sahm oh ihn akan kangalahr kreip karer,
\q2 ahpw neirail seri kan me karerkihda.’\x - \xo 18:2 \xt Ser. 31.29.\x*
\p 
\v 3 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ahpw mahsanih, “I kahukihla mwarei, Koht ieias, kumwail solahr pahn pwurehng koasoia lepin padahk audapan pwoatet nan Israel.
\v 4 Pwe mour koaros, mouren sahm oh ihn kan, oh pil mouren seri kan, ngehi me sapwellimaniki. Eri, mehmen me kin dipada, iei ih me pahn mehla.
\p 
\v 5 “Eri, ia duwen aramas emen me uhdahn mwahu, pwung oh lelepek.
\v 6 E sohte kin pwongih dikedik en eni kan en mehn Israel, de sohte kin iang tungoale mehn meirong kan sang wasahn kaudok keinepwih kan. E sohte kin kamwahlih en mehn mpe kan ar pwoud, oh e sohte kin wia nsenen pwopwoud ong lih emen me wia eh soumwahu en lih.
\v 7 E sohte kin pitihasang mehkot rehn emen de pirapahsang. E kin kapwurehwei dahme emen kin kihong mehn kadehdepen eh pweipwand; e kin katungoale me duhpeklahr akan, oh kalikawihada me kilisou kan.
\v 8 E sohte kin kihwei mwohni pwe en ale wihni. E kin kahng wiahda me suwed oh kin kihda pwungen kopwung mwahu nan repenpwung koaros.
\v 9 Soangen aramas menet kin peikiong ei kosonned akan oh kin kanahieng kapwaiada ei mahsen kan. Aramas pwung men ih, oh e pahn mourla,” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahsanih met.\x - \xo 18:9 \xt Lip. 18.5.\x*
\p 
\v 10 “Eri, ia duwe, ma aramas menet mie nah pwutak emen me lipirap, sounkam aramas, me kin wiahda soahng kei me eh pahpao soh mwahn kin wia.
\v 11 E kin kang mwengehn meirong sang wasahn kaudok keinepwih kan, oh e kin kamwahlih en mehn mpe kan ar pwoud.
\v 12 E kin pitihasang me semwehmwe kan ar kepwe kan oh kin pirapahsang, e kin koledi dahme emen kihong mehn wia kadehdepen ar pweipwand. E kin kaudokiong dikedik en eni kan, e kin wiahda soahng kanamenek kei,
\v 13 oh kin kihwei mwohni pwe en ale wihn laud. Eri da? Aramas menet pahn mourla? Soh, e sohte pahn mourla. Pwehki eh wiadahr soahng suwed kanamenek pwukat, e uhdahn pahn mehla. Pein ih pahn pwukoahki eh mehla.
\p 
\v 14 “A met, ia duwe, ma aramas suwed menet mie nah pwutak emen? Pwutak menet ahpw kin kilang de ese dihp koaros me eh pahpao kin wiahda, e ahpw sohte kin alasang eh tiahk suwed kan.
\v 15 E sohte kin pwongih dikedik en eni kan en mehn Israel de iang tungoale mehn meirong kan sang ni wasahn kaudok keinepwih kan. E sohte kin kamwahlih en mehn mpe kan ar pwoud,
\v 16 de sakone emen, de pirapahsang en emen eh dipwisou. E kin kapwurehwei dahme emen kin kihong mehn kadehdepen eh pweipwand. E kin katungoale me duhpeklahr akan, oh kalikawihada me kilisou kan.
\v 17 E kin kahng wiahda me suwed, oh e sohte kin kihwei mwohni pwe en ale wihni. E kin kapwaiada ei kosonned akan oh peikiong ei mahsen kan. E sohte pahn mehla pwehki dipen eh pahpa kan, ahpw e uhdahn pahn mourla.
\v 18 Ahpw eh pahpa kin pitihasang aramas oh pirapahsang ar dipwisou oh wia suwediong koaros ahnsou koaros. Eri, eh pahpa mehla pwehki dipe kan me pein ih wiahda.
\p 
\v 19 “Eri, ke ahpw idek, ‘Dahme kahrehda nah pwutako sohte pahn pwukoahki dipen eh pahpao?’ Eri, pasapeng en met, pwehki nah pwutako wiahda dahme pwung oh mwahu. E kapwaiada ei kosonned akan oh idawehnla ni kanahieng, iei me e uhdahn pahn mourkihla.
\v 20 Me kin wiahda dihp, iei ih me pahn mehla. Seri men sohte pahn kin pwukoahki dipen eh pahpa, de pahpa men sohte pahn kin pwukoahki dipen nah seri. Aramas mwahu men pahn ale ketingpen eh wiewia mwahu kan, a aramas suwed men pahn ale kalokepen eh wiewia suwed.\x - \xo 18:20 \xt Deud. 24.16.\x*
\p 
\v 21 “Ma aramas suwed men pahn tokedihsang wiewia suwed oh kapwaiada ei kosonned akan, ma e pahn wiahda dahme pwung oh mwahu, e pahn mourla, e sohte pahn mehla.
\v 22 Dipe kan koaros pahn lapwada, e ahpw pahn mourla pwehki eh wiadahr me pwung.”
\v 23 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie ketin mahsanih, “Kumwail dehr lemeleme me I kin kupwurperenki mehlahn aramas dipan emen; pwe soh; me I kin kupwurperenki mehlelen, aramas dipan emen en koluhla oh wiliakapwasang eh mour suwed pwe en mourla.
\p 
\v 24 “Ahpw ma aramas pwung men pahn tokedihsang eh wiewia mwahu kan oh tapihada wia me suwed, iangahki soahng kanamenek kan me aramas suwed kan kin wia, ia duwe, e kak mourla? Soh; pwe eh wiewia mwahu kan koaros me e wiadahr mahs pahn manoknokla. E uhdahn pahn mehla, pwehki eh soaloalopwoat oh pwehki dipe kan.
\p 
\v 25 “Ahpw kumwail kin nda, ‘Dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, kin ketin wia me sapwung.’ Kumwail mehn Israel kan, kumwail rong ie! Ia duwe, kumwail lemeleme I kin wia me sapwung? Soh! A me kumwail kin wia me sapwung!
\v 26 Ma aramas pwung men pahn tokedihsang eh wiewia mwahu oh tapihada wia me suwed, oh mehla; eri, e mehkihla me suwed me e wiadahro.
\v 27 A ma aramas suwed men pahn tokedihsang eh wiewia suwed oh kin wia dahme mwahu oh pwung, e pahn mourkihla.
\v 28 Pwe e kin dehdehkihla uwen suwed en eh wiewia kan oh kin tokedihsang, iei me e sohte pahn mehkihla, ahpw e pahn mourla.
\v 29 A kumwail mehn Israel kan, kumwail ahpw kin ndinda, ‘Dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, kin ketin wia me sapwung.’ Ia duwe, kumwail lemeleme me I kin wia me sapwung? A me kumwail kin wia, iei me sapwung.
\p 
\v 30 “Eri, iet ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahsanihong kumwail mehn Israel kan, duwen ei pahn kadeikada emenemen kumwail nin duwen eh wiewia kan. Kumwail tokedihsang amwail wiewia suwed kan koaros, oh dehr mweidohng dipamwail kan en kauweikumwailla.
\v 31 Kumwail kesehweisang kumwail dihp koaros me kumwail kin wia, oh kawiliakapwada kapehdamwail oh mohngiongimwail kan. Kumwail mehn Israel kan, dahme kumwail men mehkihla?”
\v 32 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “I sohte kupwurki emen en mehla. Kumwail tokedihsang nan dipamwail kan, kumwail ahpw pahn mourla.”\x - \xo 18:32 \xt Kupw. 1.13.\x*
\c 19
\s1 Koulen Nsensuwed
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie I en koulki koulen nsensuwed pwoatet ong soupeidi riemen en Israel:
\q1 
\v 2 Omw nohno iei laion lih men!
\q2 E apwalihada wah ko nanpwungen laion ohl kommwad ekei.
\q1 
\v 3 E apwalihada wah men oh padahkihong duwen eh pahn rapahki seike;
\q2 e ahpw wiahla sounsaik aramas.
\q1 
\v 4 Wehi kan ahpw rongada duwen laiono
\q2 oh lidipihedi nan pwoahr ehu.
\q1 Re ahpw kihong kehs oh ruwahdekilahng Isip.
\q1 
\v 5 En laiono eh nohno ahpw awiawih lao eh esehda me solahr eh koapworopwor.
\q1 E ahpw pil apwalihada emen wah ko,
\q2 oh wiahla emen laion kommwad.
\q1 
\v 6 Ni laiono eh laudlahr,
\q2 e ahpw kin ieiangseli laion teiko.
\q1 E ahpw pil esehla rapahki seike oh wiahla sounsaik aramas.
\q1 
\v 7 E kin kauwehla kehl kehlail kan, oh kauwehla kisin kahnimw kan.
\q1 Tohn wehio kin masepwehkada
\q2 ahnsou koaros me e kin weriwer.
\q1 
\v 8 Wehi kan eri pokonpene pwe re en mahweniong;
\q2 aramas akan kohdo sang wasa koaros.
\q1 Irail eri pahkpeseng ar uhk kan
\q2 oh kalowehdi nan ar lidip.
\q1 
\v 9 Irail eri kihdiong nan kehl ehu
\q2 oh walahng rehn nanmwarkien Papilonia.
\q1 Irail eri kin sinsile,
\q2 pwe aramas en dehr pwurehng rong ngilen eh weriwer
\q2 pohn dohl kan en Israel.
\b
\q1 
\v 10 Omw nohno rasehng tuhkehn wain pwoat
\q2 me poad limwahn pilitik pwoat.
\q1 Pwehki eh diren pihl,
\q2 tuhkehn waino losolosala oh wahnla.
\q1 
\v 11 Rah kan me inenen kehlail
\q2 oh keirda wiahla sokon en nanmwarki kan.
\q1 Tuhkehn waino ahpw reireila oh leldalahng nan depwek;
\q2 aramas koaros eri kilang duwen losolos oh reirei en tuhkeo.
\q1 
\v 12 Aramas lingeringer kei ahpw usada
\q2 oh kesediong nan pwehl.
\q1 Kisinieng en palimese ahpw kamangala wah kan.
\q1 Rah kan pil tipwasang,
\q2 mengila oh mwasikala.
\q1 
\v 13 Eri, met e poadidier nan sapwtehn,
\q2 nan sahpw madekeng oh sohte pihl.
\q1 
\v 14 Kahlepen tuhkeo eri luluda;
\q2 kisiniei eri kamwasikahla rah oh wah kan.
\q1 Rah ko solahr pahn pwurehng kehlailda,
\q2 solahr pahn wia sokon en nanmwarki.
\p Met iei koulen nsensuwed pwoat; me aramas akan kin kalap koulki.
\c 20
\s1 Aramas Kahngohdiong Kupwur en KAUN-O
\p 
\v 1 Ni rahn kaeisek en kelimaun sounpwong en keisuhn sounpar en at kalipilipala. Ekei kaunen mehn Israel ko ahpw patohdo rehi pwe re en ale kaweid duwen kupwur en KAUN-O, re ahpw mwohndi mwohi.
\v 2 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie,
\v 3 “Kowe, nein aramas, lokaiaiong aramas pwukat oh ndaiong irail dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Kumwail seu kodohn rapahki kupwurei? I kahukihla nin duwen ngehi, Koht ieias, I sohte pahn mweidohng kumwail en kalelapak rehi mehkot. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\p 
\v 4 “Kowe, nein aramas, ke onopadahr ke en kadeikirailda? Eri, wenla mwowe. Katamankin irail duwen tiahk saut kan me ar pahpa ko wiadahr.
\v 5 Ndaiong irail dahme I mahmahsanih. Ni ei pilada Israel, I wiahiong irail inou ehu. I kasalehiong irail pein ngehi nan Isip oh mahsanihong irail: Ngehi me KAUN-O, amwail Koht.\x - \xo 20:5 \xt Eks. 6.2-8.\x*
\v 6 Iei ih ahnsowo me I inoukihong irail me I pahn wairailsang nan Isip oh kahluwairaillahng nan sahpw me I piladahr ong irail, sahpw kaselel oh pwelmwahu, sahpw me keieu kaselel nanpwungen sahpw akan.
\v 7 I mahsanihong irail re en kesehla dikedik en eni kan me re kin poakohng oh re en dehr kasaminehkinirailla koht likamw akan en Isip, pwehki ngehi me KAUN-O, ar Koht.
\v 8 Ahpw re kahngohdiong ie oh sohte men rong ei mahsen. Re sohte kesehla nair dikedik en eni saut kan de kesehla koht en Isip ko. I onopadahr I en mweidohng pwe re en kehn engin ei engieng nan Isip.
\v 9 Ahpw I sohte kapwaiada pwe I dehr kasohwauwihala mwarei, pwehki ei pakairkidahr mwohn aramas akan me mehn Israel kan kin koukousoan rehrail me I pahn kahluwa irail sang nan Isip.
\p 
\v 10 “Eri, I kahluwa irail sang nan Isip kolahng nan sapwtehno.
\v 11 I ketikihong irail ei koasoandi oh padahkihong irail ei kosonned kan, me kin kihong mour ong mehmen me pahn peikiong.\x - \xo 20:11 \xt Lip. 18.5.\x*
\v 12 I kilelehdi koasoandi kan en rahnen Sapad pwehn wia kilel en inou nanpwungen ngehi oh irail, pwe en katamankin irail me ngehi, KAUN-O, me kasarawihirailla.\x - \xo 20:12 \xt Eks. 31.13-17.\x*
\v 13 Ahpw re pil kahngohdiong ie nan sapwtehno. Re kauwehla ei kosonned kan oh soikala ei koasoandi kan, me kin kihong mour ong mehmen me pahn peikiong. Re kasaminehla douluhl rahnen Sapad. I onopadahr I en mweidohng pwe re en kehn engin ei engieng nan sapwtehno oh I en kamwomwirailla.
\v 14 Ahpw I sohte kapwaiada, pwehki met pahn kasohwauwihala mwarei rehn wehi kan me kilangehr duwen ei kahluwa Israel sang nan Isip.
\v 15 Ngehi eri wiahda inou ehu nan sapwtehno me I sohte pahn kahluwairaillahng nan sahpwo me I ketikihongirailehr, sahpw kaselel oh pwelmwahuo, sahpw me keieu kaselel nanpwungen sahpw akan.\x - \xo 20:15 \xt Nemp. 14.26-35.\x*
\v 16 I wiahda inowo pwehki ar soikala ei koasoandi kan, kauwehla ei kosonned kan, oh kasaminehla rahnen Sapad—re pilada re en pwongih dikedik en eni kan.
\p 
\v 17 “Ahpw I poakeirailla. I koasoanehdi I en dehr kemeirailla nan sapwtehno.
\v 18 I kehkehlingkihong me pwulopwul ko: Kumwail dehr kapwaiada kosonned kan me amwail pahpa kahlap ako wiadahr; kumwail dehr idawehn arail tiahk de kasaminehkinkumwailla neirail dikedik en eni kan.
\v 19 Ngehi me KAUN-O, amwail Koht. Kumwail kapwaiada ei kosonned oh koasoandi kan.
\v 20 Wiahkihla rahnen Sapad rahn sarawi ehu, pwe en wia kilel en inou me kitail wiadahr, oh pahn katamankin kumwail me ngehi, KAUN-O, amwail Koht.
\p 
\v 21 “Ahpw diho pil kahngohdiong ie. Re kauwehla ei kosonned oh sohte kapwaiada ei koasoandi kan, me kin kihong mour ong mehmen me pahn peikiong. Re kasaminehla rahnen Sapad. I onopadahr I en mweidohng pwe re en kehn engin ei engieng nan sapwtehno oh kemeirailla koaros.
\v 22 Ahpw I sohte kapwaiada, pwehki met pahn kasohwauwihala mwarei rehn wehi kan me kilang duwen ei kahluwa mehn Israel kan sang nan Isip.
\v 23 Ngehi eri pil wiahda ehu inou nan sapwtehno. I inoukihda me I pahn kamwarakirailpeseng wasa koaros nan sampah.\x - \xo 20:23 \xt Lip. 26.33.\x*
\v 24 I wiadahr met pwehki ar soikala ei koasoandi kan, kauwehla ei kosonned kan, kasaminehla rahnen Sapad, oh pwongih soangen dikedik en enikohte me ar pahpa kahlap ako kin papah.
\p 
\v 25 “Ngehi eri ketikihong irail kosonned kan me sohte mwahu oh koasoandi me sohte pahn kihong aramas mour.
\v 26 I mweidohng re en kasaminehkinirailla pein ar meirong kan, oh mweidohng re en meirongkihla neirail pwutak mesenih kan. Met pwe I en kaloke irail oh kasalehiong irail me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 27 “Eri met, kowe, nein aramas, ndaiong mehn Israel kan dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong irail. Ih ehu ahl met me ar pahpa ko kasohwauwihkiniehla sang ni ar soaloalopwoat.
\v 28 I ketikiniraildohng nan sahpw me I inoukihda me I pahn ketikihong irail. Ni ar kilangada dohl ile kan oh tuhke losolos kan, re ahpw wiahda ar meirong kan wasa pwuko koaros. Re kahngiangihkiniehda ar meirong isihs kan oh wain me re meirongkihla.
\v 29 I ahpw keinemwe rehrail: Wasa dah kei me ile me kumwail kohkolahng ie? Eri, re ahpw kahdanekihla wasa pwuko ‘Wasa Ileile ko’\f l \fr 20:29 \fk WASA ILEILE KO: \ft Wasahn kaudok en me rotorot akan me mehn Ipru kan keinepwihsang re en doadoahngki. Mahsen en Ipru kawehwehdi lepin mahsen wet “Wasa Ile” kereniong duwehte sisen lepin mahsen me wehwehki “me kumwail kohkolahng ie.”\f* lel rahnwet.
\v 30 Eri, ndaiong mehn Israel kan dahme I mahmahsanih: Ia kahrepen amwail pahn pil wiahda soangen dihpohte me samamwail ko wiadahr oh idihdawehnte ar dikedik en eni kan?
\v 31 Pil leledo rahnwet kumwail kin meirongki soangen mehn meirongkohte oh kasaminehkinkumwailla soangen dikedik en enikohte sang ni amwail kin isikala noumwail seri kan wiahki mehn meirong. Oh mwuri, kumwail mehn Israel kan ahpw pil kin kohdo oh rapahki kupwurei! Nin duwen ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalap, Koht ieias, I sohte pahn mweidohng kumwail en kalelapak rehi mehkot.
\v 32 Kumwail koasoanedier nan kapehdamwail me kumwail pahn duwehte wehi teikan, duwehte aramas me kin kousoan nan wehi teikan oh pwongih tuhke kan oh takai kan. Ahpw met sohte kak wiawi.
\s1 Koht kin ketin Kaloke oh Kupwurmahk
\p 
\v 33 “I kahukihla ni mwarei, ngehi KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, Koht ieias, I kehkehlingkihong kumwail me nan ei engieng I pahn kakaunkin kumwail limei me kehlail kat, iangahki ei manaman unsek.
\v 34 I pahn kasalehiong kumwail ei manaman oh ei engieng ni ei pahn kapokoneikumwailpene oh kapwureikumwaildohsang nan wehi kan wasa me kumwail kamwarakpesengehr ie.
\v 35 I pahn ketikinkumwaildohng nan ‘Sapwtehn en Wehi kan,’ oh I ahpw pahn kadeingkumwailda wasao mwohn masamwail kan.
\v 36 Eri, I pahn kadeingkumwailda met duwehte ei kadeikada samamwail ko ni Sapwtehn Sainai,” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahsanih met.
\p 
\v 37 “I pahn sapwellimanikihla manaman pohmwail oh kupwurehda pwe kumwail en peikiong ei inowo.
\v 38 I pahn ketikihsang nanpwungamwail irail ko me kahngohdi oh dipan. I pahn ketikinirailsang nan sahpw akan me re wie koukousoan ie met, ahpw I sohte pahn mweidohng re en pwuralahng nan wehin Israel. Kumwail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\p 
\v 39 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih, “Eri met, kumwail mehn Israel kan koaros, kumwail kohwei oh papah noumwail dikedik en eni kan. Ahpw I kehkehlingkihong kumwail me mwurin met kumwail uhdahn pahn peikiong ie oh tokedihsang kasohwauwih mwarei sarawi ni amwail kin wia meirong ong noumwail dikedik en eni kan.
\v 40 Kumwail mehn Israel koaros pahn kaudokiong ie nan sahpwo, pohn ei nahna sarawio,\f m \fr 20:40 \fk NAHNA SARAWIO: \ft Nahna Saion, dohl me mi nan Serusalem me wia ekis kisehn wasa me Tehnpas Sarawio oh tehnpesen nanmwarki mi ie.\f* oh pohn nahna ileo en Israel. I pahn kupwurperenkin kumwail oh kasik kumwail en wadohng ie amwail meirong kan, amwail meirong keieu kaselel kan, oh amwail meirong sarawi kan.
\p 
\v 41 Mwurin ei pahn kapwureikumwaildo sang nan wehi kan wasa me kumwail kamwaraklahng ie oh kapokoneikumwailpene, I pahn kupwurperenki amwail meirong isihs kan, oh wehi kan pahn kilang me I me sarawi.
\v 42 Ni ei pahn kapwureikumwaildohng nan Israel, sahpw me I inoukihda me I pahn ketikihong amwail pahpa kahlap ako, eri, kumwail pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\v 43 Kumwail eri pahn tamanda soahng suwed koaros me kumwail wiadahr oh duwen amwail pein kasamineikumwailla. Kumwail pahn pein suwedkinkumwailla pwehki soahng suwed kan me kumwail wiadahr.
\v 44 Ni ei pahn mwekid pwehn doarehla wauwi, kumwail mehn Israel kan pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, pwehki ei sohte kin kalokei kumwail nin duwen me konehng amwail wiewia saut kan.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\s1 Kisiniei ni Palieir
\p 
\v 45 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 46 “Kowe, nein aramas, kilenglahng palieir. Lokaiaiong palieir oh wia kokohp me uhwong nanwel en palieir.
\v 47 Ndaiong nanwel en palieir en rong dahme KAUN-O, ketin mahmahsanih: Kilang! I saundahr kisiniei ehu, oh e pahn kamwasikahla omw tuhke koaros, me meng de mour. Sohte mehkot me pahn kak kakunla. E pahn lulsang ni palieir kolahng paliepeng, oh aramas koaros pahn kehn engin karakar en kisinieio.
\v 48 Irail koaros ahpw pahn kilang me ngehi, KAUN-O, me isikada oh sohte emen pahn kak kakunla.”
\p 
\v 49 I ahpw soikala, patohwan, “Maing KAUN, Wasa Lapalahpie, komwi dehr mahsanihong ie I en wia met! Aramas koaros kaulimkilahr me ei kokohp kan me apwal en wehwehki.”
\c 21
\s1 Sapwellimen KAUN-O Kedlahs
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla Serusalem. Keriahla wasa kan me aramas akan kin wia ie ar kaudok. Kehkehlingkihong wehin Israel
\v 3 dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, ketin mahmahsanih: Iei ngehi me omw imwintihti. I pahn usada nei kedlahs oh kemeikumwailla, kumwail koaros me suwed oh mwahu.
\v 4 I pahn doadoahngki nei kedlahs ong koaros sang ni paliepeng lel palieir.
\v 5 Eri, aramas koaros ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, usadahr nei kedlahs oh sohte pahn kapwurehiong nan dewe.
\p 
\v 6 “Kowe, nein aramas, makiaki duwehte ma omw mohngiong tihwohkilahr omw pwunod. Makiaki ni omw pahtou wasa me aramas koaros kak kilang uhk.
\v 7 Ma re idek dahme ke wiewiahki men, ndaiong irail me pwehki rohng kan me pahn kohdo. Ni rohng ko eh pahn leledo, ar mohngiong pahn direkihla masepwehk, pehrail kan pahn mwoatoredi, nan kapehdirail pahn tikitikla, oh nehrail kan pahn rerrer. Ahnsowo leledohr; e miher wasaht.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\p 
\v 8 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie,
\v 9 “Kowe, nein aramas, wia kokohp. Ndaiong aramas kan dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, ketin mahmahsanih:
\q1 Kedlahs pwoat, kedlahs pwoat adahdadahr oh melenglenglahr.
\q1 
\v 10 E adahdadahr pwehn kamaramas,
\q2 melenglenglahr pwehn piripir duwehte lioal.
\q1 Sohte peren pahn kak mie,
\q2 pwehki nei aramas akan pohnsehselahr kehkehlik oh kalokolok koaros.
\q1 
\v 11 Kedlahso melenglenglahr,
\q2 pwehn onopadahng doadoahk.
\q1 E adahdadahr oh melenglenglahr,
\q2 pwehn pwilidiong nan pehn sounkam aramas emen.
\q1 
\v 12 Mwahiei, kowe, nein aramas;
\q2 kedlahs wet pahn doadoahkohng nei aramas akan
\q2 oh ong kaunen Israel kan.
\q1 Re pahn kamakamala
\q2 iangahki nei aramas koaros.
\q1 Pakepakere nan mwaremwaromw ni seukoapworopwor!
\q1 
\v 13 I wie songosong nei aramas akan,
\q2 oh ma re sohte men wiliakapwala,
\q2 soahng pwukat koaros pahn lelohng irail.
\p 
\v 14 Eri, kowe, nein aramas, wia kokohp. Lopwor pehmwen, oh kedlahso ahpw pahn kamaramas sohte kommoal. Iei kedlahs pwoat mehn kamaramas, kedlahs pwoat me kin kamasakada aramas oh kemeirailla.
\v 15 E kin kahrehda nei aramas akan ar kin nan kapehd tikitikla oh dipekelekel. I pahn kamasangki ar kahnimwo kedlahs pwoat me kin piripir duwehte lioal oh kin onopadahr en kamaramas.
\v 16 Palla ni palimeing oh maun, kowe, kedlahs keng! Palla wasa koaros me ke pahn pirekekla ie.
\v 17 I pahn pil lopwor pehi kat, oh ei engieng ahpw pahn meleileidi. Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen.”
\s1 Sapwellimen Nanmwarkien Papilonia Kedlahs
\p 
\v 18 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 19 “Kowe, nein aramas, elehda ahl riepwoat me nanmwarkien Papilonia pahn kak keid ie ketiki sapwellime kedlahso. Ahl riepwoat en pahn tepida sang nan wehi teieu. Wiahda ehu kilel wasa me ahl ako pahn kasangpeseng ie.
\v 20 Kilelo pahn kasalehda elen nanmwarkio me kolahng Rappa, kahnimw en mehn Ammon kan, oh ahl teio kolahng Suda, oh ong Serusalem, kahnimw me kehl kelailo.
\v 21 Nanmwarkien Papilonia pahn uh limwahn kilelo ni wetpeseng en ahlo. Pwehn kadoaropwe wasa me e pahn ketila ie, e pahn itik arep ko; ale kaweid sang rehn sapwellime dikedik en eni kan; e ahpw kasawih ehn mahn emen me meirongalahr.
\v 22 Eri met! Lime palimaun kolokol arep me kileldi ‘Serusalem’! E padahkihong en ketila oh wiahda lepin tuhkehn kauwehla ewen kehlo, en wia weriwer en mahwen, en kihdiong lepin tuhken kauwehla kehlo ni ewen kehlo, wasahn poadoandoar, oh en wiahda warawar akan.
\v 23 Mehn Serusalem kan sohte pahn kamehlele met pwehki inou lapo me re wiadahr. Ahpw kokohp wet pahn katamankin irail diparail kan oh kehkehlingkihong irail me re pahn lohdi.
\v 24 Ih met me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Dipamwail kan sansaladahr. Aramas koaros eseier duwen amwail sapwung kan. Kumwail kasalehda dipamwail kan sang ni amwail mwekid koaros. Kumwail pakadeikadahr, oh I pahn pangkumwaillahng rehn amwail imwintihti kan.
\p 
\v 25 “Kowe, kaunen Israel, aramas suwed, rahn omw lokolok leledohr.
\v 26 Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen. Kihsang sapwellimomwi nihn oh lisoarop en nanmwarki. Soahng koaros solahr pahn duweduwehte. Kasapwilada me semwehmwe kan pwe re en ahnekihla manaman! Kasapwiledi me kakaun akan!
\v 27 Kauwehla, kauwehla! Ei, I pahn wiahkihla kahnimwo mohn kahnimw ehu. Ahpw met sohte pahn wiawi lao mehmeno pahn kohdo me I piladahr en kaloke kahnimwo. Ong ih me I pahn ketikihong kahnimwo.
\s1 Kedlahs Pwoat oh mehn Ammon kan
\p 
\v 28 “Kowe, nein aramas, wia kokohp. Kalohkihda dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong mehn Ammon kan, me kapakapailoke mehn Israel kan. Padahkihong irail:
\q1 ‘Kedlahs pwoat onopadahr en kamwomwala wasa;
\q2 E melenglenglahr pwehn kamaramas, piripir duwehte lioal.\x - \xo 21:28 \xt Ser. 49.1-6; Esek. 25.1-7; Eimw. 1.3-15; Sep. 2.8-11.\x*
\m 
\v 29 Kaudiahl kan me ke kilikilang sohte mehlel, oh kokohp kan me ke wiewia me likamw. Ke me suwed oh dipan, oh omw rahn pahn leledohr, rahnen omw lokolok. Kedlahso pahn lel ni tepinwaramwail kan.
\p 
\v 30 “‘Kapwurehiong kedlahso nan dewe! I pahn kadeik uhk wasa me ke kepikipikda ie, nan sahpw me ke ipwidi ie.
\v 31 Ke pahn kehn engin ei engieng ni ei pahn sapwadehng uhk duwehte kisiniei. Oh I pahn panguhkalahng rehn aramas lemei kan, me kin saman en kamwomwala wasa.
\v 32 Kisiniei pahn kamwomwuhkala. Ntahmw pahn keredi nan pein sapwomw, oh sohte emen pahn pwurehng tamanuhkada.’” KAUN-O, me mahmahsen.
\c 22
\s1 Sapwung kan en Serusalem
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, ke onopadahr pwe ke en kadeikada kahnimwo me direkilahr sounkam aramas? Kasalehiong ni sansal soahng saut koaros me e wiadahr.
\v 3 Ndaiong kahnimwo dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Pwehki omw kemelahr pein noumw aramas tohto oh kasaminehkinuhkalahr omw kin pwongih dikedik en eni kan, me kahrehda omw ahnsou leledohr.
\v 4 Ke dipikidahr kamaramas pwuko oh saminkilahr dikedik en eni kan me ke wiadahr; eri, omw ahnsou leledohr, omw ahnsou imwiseklahr! Ih kahrepen ei mweidohng wehi kan en kouruhrkin uhk oh sahpw koaros en kepitkin uhk.
\v 5 Sahpw keren oh doh kan koaros kin kepitkin uhk pwehki omw kin sapeikiong kosonned akan.
\v 6 Kaunen Israel koaros kin koapworopworki ar kehlail oh kin kamaramas.
\v 7 Sohte emen nan kahnimwo kin wauneki seme oh ine. Ke kin pitih mehn liki kan oh kahpwalihala liohdi oh me sepwoupwou kan. \x - \xo 22:7 \xt Eks. 20.12; Deud. 5.16; b Eks. 22.21-22; Deud. 24.17.\x*
\v 8 Ke sohte kin wauneki wasa sarawi kan, oh sohte kapwaiada rahnen Sapad.\x - \xo 22:8 \xt Lip. 19.30; 26.2.\x*
\v 9 Ekei noumw aramas akan kin karaun likamw ong ekei pwe re en kamakamala. Ekei irail kin kang mwenge me kin meirongalahng dikedik en eni kan. Ekei kin wiewia dipen nenek ahnsou koaros.
\v 10 Ekei kin wendiong rehn en ar pahpa kan ar pwoud kan. Ekei kin idingki lih akan en wia nsenen pwopwoud ni ar wiewia ar soumwahu en lih.\x - \xo 22:10 \xt Lip. 18.7-20.\x*
\v 11 Ekei wiewia dipen kamwahl, oh ekei kin pwangih en neirail pwutak kan ar pwoud de pwangih serepein kan me ar pahpa de nohno tehmen.
\v 12 Ekei noumw aramas akan kin kamaramas pwe re en ale pweine. Ekei kin kihong wihn pohn mwohni me ienge mehn Israel men kin pekihsang, oh kin kepwehpwehkihla. Re manokeielahr.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.\x - \xo 22:12 \xt Eks. 23.8; Deud. 16.19; Eks. 22.25; Lip. 25.36-37; Deud. 23.19.\x*
\p 
\v 13 “I pahn ketikihdiong kumwutiet pohn sounpirap oh sounkam aramas akan.
\v 14 Ke lemeleme me pahn mie kehl en nan kapehdomw de kehlail en kak pwekada pehmw kan ni ei pahn kaimwisakala ei kalokeiuk? Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen, oh I kin kapwaiada ei mahsen.
\v 15 I pahn kamwarakpeseng noumw aramas akan nan wehi oh sahpw koaros oh pahn katokihedi omw wiewia suwed kan.
\v 16 Eri, wehi teikan pahn kasohwauwihiukala, ahpw ke pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Uhmw Mwehl
\p 
\v 17 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 18 “Kowe, nein aramas, sohte katepen mehn Israel kan ong ie. Re rasehng mete mer—koper, dihn, mete, oh leht—me kin luhwehdi ahnsou me silper kin kamwakel nan kisiniei.
\v 19 Eri met, ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong irail me sohte kateparail rasehng mepwukat. I pahn ketikinirailpene koaros nan Serusalem
\v 20 duwehte takai me silper, koper, mete, leht, oh dihn kin mi loale eh kin lekdekiong nan uhmw mwehl. Ei engieng pahn kapeirailpeseng duwehte kisiniei eh kin kapeipeseng takai me mete kan kin mi loale.
\v 21 Ei, I pahn kapokoneirailpene nan Serusalem, saunda kisiniei pahrail, oh kapeikinirailpeseng ei engieng.
\v 22 Re pahn peipeseng nan Serusalem duwehte silper eh kin peipeseng nan uhmw mwehl, eri, re ahpw pahn esehla me re kekehn engieng en KAUN-O.”
\s1 Dipen Kaunen Israel kan
\p 
\v 23 KAUN-O eri pil pwurehng mahsanihong ie,
\v 24 “Kowe, nein aramas, ndaiong mehn Israel kan me sapwarailo sahpw dipan ehu, ihme I pahn kalokehki nan ei engieng.
\v 25 Kaun akan rasehng laion kan me wie ngiringir pohn mahn akan me re kemelahr. Re kin kemehla aramas akan, kihsang mwohni oh dipwisou koaros me re kak ale, oh ar kamaramas kin kahrehda liohdi eh tohtohla.
\v 26 Samworo kan kauwelahr ei kosonned oh sohte wauneki me sarawi kan. Re sohte kin katohrepeseng dahme sarawi oh sohte sarawi. Re sohte kin padahkihong aramas akan wekpeseng en me mwakelekel oh sohte mwakelekel, oh re sohte kin kapwaiada rahnen Sapad. Eri, wahn mepwukat iei duwen mehn Israel ar sohte waunekin ie.\x - \xo 22:26 \xt Lip. 10.10.\x*
\v 27 Lapalap akan en nan koperment rasehng kidi en wel me tetehrpeseng seikarail kan. Re kin kamaramas pwe re en kepwehpwehkihla.
\v 28 Soukohp kan ekihla dihp pwukat, rasehng aramas eh kin litoapwehki litoapw pwetepwet kehl kan. Re kin kilang kaudiahl me sohte mehlel oh wia keseu likamw ong ahnsou kohkohdo kan. Re kin nda me re wiewia mahsen en KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ahpw ngehi, KAUN-O, sohte mwahn mahseniong irail.
\v 29 Me kepwehpwe kan kin pirap oh mwersuwed. Re kin wiakauwe me semwehmwe kan oh kahpwalihala mehn liki kan.
\v 30 I rapahki emen me kak kauwada ehu kehl, me kak uh wasa me kehl kan pwupwudi ie oh doarehla sahpwo ni ahnsou me ei engieng nektehn kamwomwala, ahpw sohte emen me I kak diar.
\v 31 Eri, I pahn sapwadohng irail ei engieng, oh kamwomwirailla rasehng kisiniei pwehki ar wiewia kan.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\c 23
\s1 Pirien en Serepein Dipan ako
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, mahs mie serepein riemen me pirien.
\v 3 Ni ara pwulopwul, wie koukousoan nan Isip, ira ahpw kauwehla ara meipwon oh wiahla lihen netiki paliwere riemen.
\v 4 Me laudo adaneki Oh-olah\f n \fr 23:4 \fk OH-OLAH: \ft Ahd wet ni mahsen en Ipru wehwehki “eh wasahn kousoan.”\f* (iei ih me Sameria), oh me tikitiko adaneki Oh-olipah\f o \fr 23:4 \fk OH-OLIPAH: \ft Ahd wet ni mahsen en Ipru wehwehki “ei wasahn kousoan mi loale.”\f* (iei ih me Serusalem). I ahpw pwoudikihda ira koaros, oh ira wiahiong ie seri kei.
\v 5 Mehndahte ei pwoudiki, Oh-olah wiewiahte lihen netiki paliwere men oh kin diren ineng suwed ong eh kerir kan sang Asiria.
\v 6 Iei irail sounpei kei me mi nan likou pohn ntahnmwel, soupeidi oh kaunen sounpei lapalap akan; irail koaros sounpei pwulopwul masamwahu kei.
\v 7 Iei ih lih tiahk suwed men ong lapalap akan en Asiria, oh eh ineng suwed kahrehiong eh kasaminehkihla pein ih ni eh kin pwongih dikedik en eni kan en Asiria.
\v 8 E ahpw usehla wiewia tiahk en netiki paliwere me e tikikihda nan Isip, wasa me e kauwehla ie eh meipwon. Sangete ni eh kisin serepein, ohl akan kin wendi reh oh wiahki ih lihen netiki paliwere men.
\v 9 I ahpw pangalahng rehn eh mwohnlimpoak kan, iei mehn Asiria kan, me e kin poakohng mehlel.
\v 10 Irail eri kapwuhrasang eh likou kan, adihasang nah pwutak oh serepein kan, oh kemehkihla liho kedlahs pwoat. Lih akan wasa koaros ahpw kin koasoakoasoiaseli duwen paisuwedlahn liho.
\p 
\v 11 “Mehndahte rie serepein Oh-olipah eh kilangehr duwen met, ahpw eh tiahk suwed pil uklahsang me rie Oh-ohla wiadahr.
\v 12 E pil iang diren ineng suwed ong soupeidi oh lapalap akan en Asiria—sounpei kan me mi nan likou melengileng—oh kaunen sounpei kan, irail koaros pil pwulopwul oh masamwahu.
\v 13 I kilang duwen eh mour suwed douluhl, me keriemeno pil inenen suwed duwehte me keieuo.
\p 
\v 14-15 “En Oh-olipah eh mour dipan ahpw ukuhkla mwowe. E ahpw mwahukihda sansal ekei en kaun lapalap akan en Papilonia me mahlenda nin dihdo oh litoapw weitahta poh marahra, me pirapir likou nan likoparail kan oh lisoarop kaselel pohn moangarail kan.
\v 16 Ni eh kilangada sansal ko, e ahpw ineng suwedkihda oh kadarala meninkeder kei rehrail nan Papilonia.
\v 17 Mehn Papilonia ko ahpw kohdo pwe re en wiahiong nsenen pwopwoud. Re ahpw wiahiong nsenen pwopwoud oh kasaminehkihla douluhl me kahrehda e uhd kailongkinirailla.
\v 18 E kasalehda eh suwed mwohn aramas akan oh mweidohng aramas koaros en kilang duwen eh tiahk suwed. I pil kalahdekihla duwehte ei kalahdekihla rie me laudo.
\v 19 Eh tiahk suwed uklahsang mahs, wiewia tiahk me e kin wia ni eh pwulopwulo, tiahk en netiki paliwere nan Isip.
\v 20 E inenen ineng suwedih ohl akan me sengeu duwehte ahs de oahs wol kan.”
\v 21 (Oh-olipah, ke men pwurehng nan omw mour suwed en mahs, me ke dipikidahr ni omw kisin serepein nan Isip, wasa me ohl akan kin mwadomwadonge omw dihdi kan oh kauwehla omw meipwon.)
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Kadeik ong Serepein Tikitiko
\p 
\v 22 “Eri met, Oh-olipah, iet me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong uhk. Ke pwangahkidahr omw kerir ko, ahpw I pahn kupwurehda pwe re en lingeringerda pahmw oh kohdo kapiluhkpene.
\v 23 I pahn ketikihdo mehn Papilonia oh Kaldea kan, ohl akan sang Pekod, Soha, oh Koa, oh mehn Asiria koaros. I pahn kapokonepene soupeidi oh lapalap masamwahu pwulopwul ko, lapalap kesempwal akan oh kaunen sounpei kan.
\v 24 Re pahn mahweniong uhk sang ni paliepeng. Re pahn wa kohdo lapalahn karis ehu me iangahki werennansapw en mahwen oh kuruma tohto. Re pahn perehrehki mehn sansar oh lisoarop mete, re pahn kapiluhkpene. I pahn panguhkala rehrail, re ahpw pahn kadeikuhkada ni pein ar kosonned kan.
\v 25 Pwehki ei engieng pahmw, I pahn mweidala pwe re en kalokeiuk nan ar engieng. Re pahn lupukasang tumwomwen oh salengomw kan oh kemehla noumw seri kan. Ei, re pahn adihasang uhk noumw pwutak oh serepein kan oh isikirailla ni ar momourte.
\v 26 Re pahn tehrasang omw likou kan oh kihsang omw mehn kapwat akan.
\v 27 I pahn katokihedi omw ineng suwed oh tiahk suwed kan me ke wiewia sang ni omw mihmi nan Isip. Ke solahr pahn idawehn dikedik en eni kan de medemedewe duwen Isip.”
\p 
\v 28 Ih met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih: “I pahn panguhkala rehn aramas akan me ke kailongki oh sautiki.
\v 29 Oh pwehki ar kailongkin uhk, re pahn adihasang uhk mehkoaros me ke koadoahkihada oh keseiukala nan omw kilisou, kanamenekpomw ahpw pahn sansalada duwehte lihen netiki paliwere men. Omw ineng suwed oh tiahk en netiki paliweromw
\v 30 me kahredohr mepwukat pohmw. Ke wialahr lihen netiki paliwere men ong wehi kan, oh kasaminehkinuhkalahr dikedik en eni kan.
\v 31 Ke alasang tiahk en riomwo, iei me kahrehda I pahn ketikihong uhk soangen dahl en lokolokohte pwe ke en nim.”
\p 
\v 32 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih,
\q1 “Ke pahn iang nim dahl me riomwo nimalahr;
\q2 dahl laud oh loal.
\q1 Aramas koaros pahn mwamwahlikin uhk oh kepitkin uhk;
\q2 dahlo me dir mehlel.
\q1 
\v 33 E pahn kahrehda omw sakaukihla oh paisuwedkihla,
\q2 iei dahl en misik oh paisuwed,
\q2 dahl me iei limen riomw serepein Sameria.
\q1 
\v 34 Ke pahn nim lao nek, oh pil rukoahla,
\q2 oh dipere kan pahn
\q2 kauwehla nan mwaremwaromw.
\m Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\p 
\v 35 Eri, iei met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: “Pwehki omw manokeiehla oh sohpeisang ie, ke pahn ale kalokepen omw ineng suwed oh tiahk en netiki paliweromw.”
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Kadeik ong Pirien Riemeno
\p 
\v 36 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, ke onopadahr ke en kadeik Oh-olah oh Ohl-olipah? Padokehng ira soahng saut kan me ira wiadahr.
\v 37 Ira wiadahr dipen kamwahl oh kamaramas—kamwahl ong dikedik en eni kan oh kamalahn seri kan me ira wiahiong ie. Ira meirongkihla nei pwutak kan ong neira dikedik en eni kan.
\v 38 Oh kaidehn met kante me ira wiadahr. Ira kasaminehla Tehnpasei Sarawio oh kauwehla rahnen Sapad, me I koasoanedier.
\v 39 Ni rahnohte me ira meirongkihla nei pwutak ko ong dikedik en eni ko, ira ahpw kohdo nan Tehnpasei Sarawio oh kasaminehla!
\p 
\v 40 “Ira kin pwurupwurehng ahnsou koaros kadakadarala meninkeder kan pwe re en lukehdo ohl akan sang wasa doh, oh ohl ako ahpw kin pwarodo. Perien riemeno ahpw kin duhduhla oh kapwatada.
\v 41 Ira eri kin mwohndiong nan ara sehr mwuterek, oh kihdiong pohn tehpel mwohra soahng kaselel kan, me iangahki warpwohmwahu oh lehn olip me I ketikihong ira.
\v 42 Ngilen peren ahpw kin peipeido, pwihn en ohl ehu wisikdohsang nan sapwtehn. Re kihong liwou ni pehn lih ako, oh nihn lingan pohn moangara ko.
\v 43 I ahpw pein mengimengloalki me re wiewiahki lihen netiki paliwere, lih emen me solahr angihki eh kamwahl.
\v 44 Re kin pwurupwurala rehn lihen netiki paliwarara kan pak tohto. Re kin pwuralahng rehn Oh-olah oh Oh-olipah, lih tiahk suwed ko.
\v 45 Aramas pwung kan pahn kadeikirahda ni dipen kamwahl oh kamaramas, pwehki ara kin wiewia dipen kamwahl oh pehra kan direkilahr nta.”
\p 
\v 46 Ih met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih: “Ekerodo pokon lap ehu pwe re en kamasakirahda oh pirapa ira.
\v 47 Pokon lapo en katehkin ira takai oh mahwenkihong ira kedlahs, kemehla neira seri kan, oh isikada imwara kan.
\v 48 I pahn katokihedi tiahk suwed wasa koaros nan sahpwo, pwehn wia karasaras ehu ong lih koaros pwe re en dehr wia dipen kamwahl duwehte me ira wiadahr.
\v 49 Oh kumwa pirienen—I pahn kalokehkin kumwa amwa tiahk suwed oh amwa dipen pwongih dikedik en eni kan. Eri, kumwa ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie.”
\c 24
\s1 Einpwoat Mer
\p 
\v 1 Ni rahn kaeisek en kaeisek en sounpwong en sounpar kaduwau en at kalipilipala, KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, ntingihedi depehn sounpwong rahnwet, pwehki iei rahnwet me nanmwarkien Papilonia tapihada kapilpene Serusalem.\x - \xo 24:2 \xt 2 Nan. 25.1; Ser. 52.4.\x*
\v 3 Padahkihong nei aramas kahngohdi kan karasaras pwoatet me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanihong irail:
\q1 Kihdiong einpwoato pohn kisinieio
\q2 oh audehkihla pihl.
\q1 
\v 4 Kihdiong loale uduk me keieu kaselel—
\q2 uduk en peh kan, oh neh kan—
\q2 pil audehkihla tih me kin keieu iou kan.
\q1 
\v 5 Doadoahngki uduk en sihpw me keieu kaselel;
\q2 saunehng eihn einpwoato.
\q1 Pihlo en pwoail;
\q2 pwoailihada tih kan oh uduk kan.”
\p 
\v 6 Ih met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: “Meid suwediong kahnimw en kamaramaso! E rasehng einpwoat mer ehu me sohte mwahn kin kamwakelda. Kisin sansar en uduk kan kin kohkohsang, oh sohte ehu kin luhwehdi loale.
\v 7 Kamaramas wiewiawi nan kahnimwo, ahpw nta kan sohte wudekdiong nan pwehl wasa me pwelpar kak karirihala; e wudekdiong pohn paip kalaimwun ehu me mi pohn pwehl.
\v 8 I mweidohng ntao en mihmi wasao, wasa me sohte pahn rirla, wasa me e pahn sansal ie oh ale dupukpe.”
\p 
\v 9 Ih met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: “Meid suwediong kahnimw en kamaramaso! Pein ngehi me pahn saunehng eihn einpwoato.
\v 10 Kumwail wahdo pil ekei tuwi! Kumwail irip kisinieien! Pwoailihada uduken! Pwoailih suhpwen lao ngalangalada! Isikala tih kan!
\v 11 Met kihdiong tehn einpwoat prons en pohn mwoalus kan oh mweidohng en weitahtahla. Einpwoat en ahpw pahn pwurehng mwakelekellahng kaudok mwurin mer kan eh pahn kohsang,
\v 12 mehnda ma mer koaros sohte pahn sohrala nan kisinieio.
\v 13 Serusalem, omw wiewia suwed kan kasamineiukalahr. Mehndahte ei kin nannantihong en kamwakeleiukada, ahpw ke kin samisaminte. Ke sohte pahn pwurehng mwakelekella lao ke pehm engin ei engieng unsek.
\v 14 Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen. E lelehr ahnsoun ei mwekid. I sohte pahn meliehla dipomw kan de poakeiukala de kupwurkalahngan ong uhk. Ke pahn ale kalokepen omw wiewia kan.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\s1 Mehlahn en Soukohpo eh Pwoud
\p 
\v 15 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 16 “Kowe, nein aramas, ahnsou tehkis I pahn kihsang aramaso me ke keieu poakohng. Ke sohte pahn kaulim de sengiseng de kakerehdi pilen mesomw.
\v 17 Kaleke e de mie ngilen omw sengiseng. Kaleke ke sehkasang pitenmoangomw de sohte suht alialuseli pwehn wia kilel en nsensuwed. Kaleke ke perehla mesomw de kang kisin mwenge me sounmwahiei kan kin kang.”
\p 
\v 18 Nimenseng en rahno I koasoiong aramas ako. Nin soutiko ei pwoudo kapilsalehdala, oh mahndahn rahno I ahpw wia dahme kohieng ie I en wia.
\v 19 Aramas ako eri kalelapak rehi, “Dahme komw wiewiahki soangen mwekid wet?”
\p 
\v 20 Ngehi eri patohwanohng irail, “KAUN-O ketin mahseniong ie
\v 21 I en patohwanohng kumwail mehn Israel kan mahsen wet: Kumwail kin pohnmwahsohki kehlail en Tehnpas Sarawio. Kumwail kin men pwarek oh kilang, ahpw KAUN-O pahn ketin mweidohng en saminla. Oh kisehn amwail peneinei me pwulopwul kan me luhwehdi nan Serusalem pahn mehla nan mahwen.
\v 22 Kumwail ahpw pahn wia dahme I wiahiero. Kumwail sohte pahn perehla masamwail kan de tungoale kisin tungoal me sounmwahiei kan kin tungoale.
\v 23 Kumwail sohte pahn sehkasang pitenmoangamwail de sohte suht alialuseli de mwahiei de sengiseng. Kumwail pahn luhluwetala pwehki dipamwail kan, oh kumwail pahn ingihngitingki amwail medek nanpwungamwail.
\v 24 I ahpw pahn wiahla kilel ehu ong kumwail; kumwail pahn wia mehkoaros me I wiahier. KAUN-O ketin mahsanih me ahnsou me mepwukat pahn pweida, eri, kumwail pahn esehla me iei ih KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie.”
\p 
\v 25 KAUN-O eri mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, I pahn adihasang irail Tehnpas Sarawi kehlailo me re kin pohnmwahsohki oh perenki, me re kin mwahuki pwarek oh kilang. Oh I pahn pil adihasang neirail pwutak oh serepein kan.
\v 26 Ni rahn me I pahn kapwaiada met, mehmen me pahn pitsang paisuwedo pahn kohdo oh pakairkihong uhk duwen mepwukat.
\v 27 Ni rahnohte ke pahn pwurehng lokaiahda, oh ke pahn iang koasoi. Ih duwen met omw pahn wia kilel ehu ong aramas akan, oh re pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\c 25
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Ammon
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,\x - \xo 25:1 \xt Ser. 49.1-6; Esek. 21.28-32; Eimw. 1.13-15; Sep. 2.8-11.\x*
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla sapwen Ammon.
\v 3 Ndaiong irail en rong dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Kumwail perenkihda amwail kilang ei Tehnpas Sarawio eh saminla, amwail kilang wehin Israel eh ohlahr, amwail kilang mehn Suda ar kalipilipala.
\v 4 Pwehki amwail peren, I pahn mweidohng kadaudok kan sang ni palimesehn sapwtehno en kaloweikumwaildi. Re pahn kauwada imwarail impwal kan nan sapwamwail oh kousoanla ie. Re pahn kang wahnsahpw oh milik me uhdahn pahn kanamwail.
\v 5 I pahn wiahkihla kahnimw Rappa wasahn kousoan en kamel kan, oh sapwen Ammon pahn wiahla wasahn kousoan en sihpw kan, pwe kumwail en ese me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 6 “Ih met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Kumwail lopwolopw oh lusuluski amwail peren. Kumwail kailongkihla wehin Israel.
\v 7 Pwehki amwail kailongki, I pahn pangkumwaillahng rehn wehi teikan me pahn pirapai kumwail oh kulihasang amwail dipwisou kan. I pahn kamwomwkumwailla douluhl me kahrehda kumwail sohla pahn wia ehu wehi de sohla pahn sapwamwail. Kumwail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Mohap
\p 
\v 8 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Pwehki Mohap eh nda me Suda duwehte wehi teikan,\x - \xo 25:8 \xt Ais. 15.1—16.14; 25.10-12; Ser. 48.1-47; Eimw. 2.2-3; Sep. 2.8-11.\x*
\v 9 I pahn mweidohng mahwen en wiawihong kahnimw kan me wia poadoarepen irepen Mohap, iangahki kahnimw me keieu kaselel kan— Ped Sesimod, Paal Meon, oh Kiriadaim.
\v 10 I pahn mweidohng kadaudok kan en palimesehn sapwtehno en kalowehdi Mohap, iangahki Ammon, pwe Mohap en sohla wia wehi ehu.
\v 11 I pahn kaloke Mohap, oh re pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Edom
\p 
\v 12 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie mahsanih, “Mehn Edom kan ikihong Suda ni mwekid suwed, oh mwekid en ikih wet me kahredohr dihp lapalap ehu pohn Edom.\x - \xo 25:12 \xt Ais. 34.5-17; 63.1-6; Ser. 49.7-22; Esek. 35.1-15; Eimw. 1.11-12; Op. 1-14; Mal. 1.2-5.\x*
\v 13 Eri, met I kalohkidahr me I pahn kaloke Edom oh kemehla aramas oh mahn koaros wasao. I pahn wiahkihla sapwtehn, sangete ni kahnimw Teman kolahng ni kahnimw Dedan, oh aramas akan pahn mehla nan mahwen.
\v 14 Nei aramas Israel pahn wilianiehdi oh ikihong Edom, oh re pahn kahrehiong Edom en kehn engin ei engieng. Edom eri pahn esehla dahkot ei engieng.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Pilisdia
\p 
\v 15 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie mahsanih, “Mehn Pilisdia kan wia mwekid suwed en ikihong aramas akan me re kin imwintihtihong sangete mahs, oh kamwomwirailla nan ar kailok.\x - \xo 25:15 \xt Ais. 14.29-31; Ser. 47.1-7; Soel 3.4-8; Eimw. 1.6-8; Sep. 2.4-7; Sek. 9.5-7.\x*
\v 16 Eri, I kalohkidahr me I pahn mahweniong Pilisdia oh koakoahirailla. I pahn kamwomwala aramas koaros me luhwehdi oh koukousoan wasao pohn patapat en Pilisdia.
\v 17 I pahn kalokei irail mwuledek oh ikihiong irail mehkoaros. Re pahn kehn engin ei engieng. Irail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\c 26
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Dair
\p 
\v 1 Ni rahn keieu en... sounpwong en sounpar kaeisek ehu en at kalipilipala, KAUN-O ketin mahseniong ie.\x - \xo 26:1 \xt Ais. 23.1-18; Soel 3.4-8; Eimw. 1.9-10; Sek. 9. 1-4; Mad. 11.21-22; Luk 10.13-14.\x*
\v 2 E mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, iet dahme mehn kahnimw Dair wie pereperenki. Re weriwer, ndinda, ‘Serusalem ohlahr! Eh kehlail en pesines sohralahr! E solahr pahn uhwong kitail!”
\p 
\v 3 “Eri met, iet dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Ngehi me omw imwintihti, kowe kahnimw Dair. I pahn ketikihdo wehi tohto pwehn mahweniong uhk, oh re pahn kohdo rasehng iloak en madau.
\v 4 Re pahn kamwomwala omw kelen kahnimw oh karangkehdi omw wasahn iroir kan. I ahpw pahn koakoahla pwelpar koaros oh paip kalaimwun ehu me pahn luhwehdi.
\v 5 Sounlaid kan ahpw pahn kin palang ar uhk kan powe, wasa me e pahn uhdahsang ie nan madau. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen. Wehi kan pahn kulihasang dipwisou kan en Dair,
\v 6 oh kemehkihla nair kedlahs kan irail kan me koukousoan nan eh kisin kahnimw kan nan werengen sahpwo. Dair eri pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\p 
\v 7 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “I pahn ketikihdo nanmwarki me keieu lapalap—Nepukadnesar, nanmwarkien Papilonia— pwehn mahweniong Dair. E pahn ketido sang ni paliepeng, iangahki lapalahn karis ehu, oahs, werennansapw en mahwen, oh sounpei en dak oahs.
\v 8 Irail kan me koukousoan nan kisin kahnimw kan nanwerengen sahpwo pahn mehla nan mahweno. Imwintihtio pahn kauwada wasahn poadoandoar, warawar, oh wiahda ehu kehl kehlail mehn pere irail sang uhk.
\v 9 Re pahn sukeki omw kehl kan mehn sukpeseng kehl oh karangkehkihdi omw wasahn iroir kan mehn suk mete.
\v 10 Pwelpar en neirail oahs kan pahn koadupwalihiukedi. Katairong en neirail oahs kan me tangatangahki kuruma kan oh werennansapw en mahwen kan pahn itikada omw kehl kan ni ar pahn tangolong nan ewen kehl kan en kahnimw ohlao.
\v 11 Neirail sounpei en dak oahs kan pahn tang nan omw ahl akan, kemekemehkihla noumw aramas akan kedlahs. Omw uhr kehlail kan pahn pwupwudi nanpwel.
\v 12 Omw imwintihti kan pahn simwihasang omw kepwe kan oh dipwisoun pesines kan. Re pahn karangkehdi omw kehl kan oh kauwehla imwomw ihmw kaselel kan. Re pahn ale takai, tuhke oh kihd en mohn ihmw kan koaros oh keselahng nansed.
\v 13 I pahn katokihedi ngilen amwail koul kan, oh katokihedi ngilen noumwail arp kan.\x - \xo 26:13 \xt Kaud. 18.22.\x*
\v 14 I pahn luhwehkihdi paip kalaimwun ehu wasa me sounlaid kan kak en palangada ie arail uhk kan. Kahnimwo sohte pahn onohnda sapahl. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\p 
\v 15 Iet mahsen me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, pahn mahsanihong kahnimw Dair: “Ni omw pahn lohdi, aramas akan me koukousoan ni oaroahr kan pahn masakada weriwer en irail kan me wie kamakamala.
\v 16 Nanmwarki koaros en wehi kan me waranki sohp tohto pahn ketidi sang nan mwoalarail. Re pahn pwuhrsang nan sapwellimarail likou reirei oh likou deiad akan oh ketidi wie rerrer nanpwel. Re pahn inenen masakada duwen imwilahn amwail mour me kahrehda re sohla pahn kak tokedihsang ar wie rerrer.\x - \xo 26:16 \xt Kaud. 18.9-10.\x*
\v 17 Re pahn wia koulen kedepwidepw wet ong kumwail:
\q1 Kahnimw ndando mwomwlahr!
\q1 Were sohp kan sohrasangehr nan madau.
\q1 Tohn kahnimw wet me kaunda nan madau
\q1 Oh kin kamasakada koaros me koukousoan ni oaroahr kan.
\q1 
\v 18 Eri, ni rahn me e pwupwudio,
\q1 Kisin deke kan itikekda,
\q1 Oh towe kan pwuriamweikihla soangen mwomwla wet.”
\p 
\v 19 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie ahpw mahsanih: “I pahn wiahkinuhkala sapwtehn ehu duwehte mohn kahnimw kan me sohte aramas kin kousoan ie. I pahn koaduhpwalkinuhkedi pilen nan madau.
\v 20 I pahn kadaruhkalahng rehn me melahr akan pwe ke en iang mihmi rehn aramas en kawa ko. I pahn kupwurehda pwe ke en mihmi pahn pwehl nanpwungen mohn kahnimw poatopoat kan, ieiang me melahr akan. Ni imwilahn met ke sohte pahn pwurehng wiahla kahnimw en me momour kan.
\v 21 I pahn wiahkinuhkala wasahn karasepe kamasepwehk, oh met iei pahn imwilahn omw mour. Mweinele aramas akan pahn rapahkin uhk, ahpw re sohte pahn diar uhk.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.\x - \xo 26:21 \xt Kaud. 18.21.\x*
\c 27
\s1 Koulen Kedepwidepw ong Dair
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, koulkihong Dair apwoat koulen kedepwidepwen,
\v 3 kahnimwo me mihte ni irepen sehdo wiewia pesines ong aramas akan me koukousoan ni oaroahr akan. Ndaiong dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih:
\q1 “Dair, ke suweiki omw inenen kaselel.
\q1 
\v 4 Iei deumw nansed.
\q1 Me wieiukada kan wieiukada rasehng sohp kaselel pwoat;
\q1 
\v 5 Re doadoahngki tuhke pir sang nin Nahna Ermon mehn wiahda dinapw
\q1 Oh tuhke sidar sang Lepanon mehn wia kehu.
\q1 
\v 6 Re ale tuhke ohk sang Pasan mehn wia padil;
\q1 Re wiahkihda omw taht tuhke pain sang Saiprus
\q1 Oh kapwatki aipori.
\q1 
\v 7 Omw serek kan wiawihkihda likou linen,
\q1 Linen deiad sang Isip,
\q1 Me aramas kak kilang sang wasa doh.
\q1 Omw darpwolin kan wiawihkihda likou keieu kaselel,
\q1 Poh ntahn mwel me kohsang ni kisin deke kan en Saiprus.
\q1 
\v 8 Noumw sounpadil kan sang kahnimw kan en Saidon oh Arpad.
\q1 Pein noumw ohl koahiek kan me sehla.
\q1 
\v 9 Kahpinte kan en sohpo
\q1 Iei ohl koahiek kei sang Piplos.
\q1 Sehla kan sang pohn sohp akan koaros nan madau
\q1 Wia pesines nan omw wasahn netinet kan.
\p 
\v 10 “Sounpei kan sang Persia, Lidia, oh Lipia kin uhpah noumw karis. Re kin tenekihda neirail mehn sansar oh ar lisoarop en sounpei kan ni omw wasahn sounpei kan. Iei irail me kalowehdiong uhk omw lingan.
\v 11 Sounpei kan sang Arpad me kin sinsile omw kehl kan, oh ohl akan sang Kamad me kin sinsile omw imwen iroir kan. Re tenekihda neirail mehn sansar kan ni omw dihd kan. Iei irail me kahrehiong omw lingan.
\p 
\v 12 “Ke netikihla omw dipwisou kan ong Spein oh alehki silper, mete, dihn, oh leht.
\v 13 Ke pesines kihong Krihs, Tupal, oh Mesek omw dipwisou kan oh wiliankihda lidu oh dipwisou prons kan.
\v 14 Ke netikihla omw dipwisou kan mehn pwainda oahs en doadoahk, oahs en mahwen, oh kou sang Ped Dokarma.
\v 15 Mehn Rohdes kawiliali ar dipwisou rehmw; aramas en ni oaroahr tohto kihong uhk aipori oh eponi mehn kawiliankihda omw dipwisou kan.
\v 16 Mehn Siria pwainda omw dipwisou kan oh wahnsahpw tohto. Re kihong uhk emerald, likou poh ntahn mwel, likou deiad, linen kaselel, rahr, oh rupi kan pweinen omw dipwisou kan.
\v 17 Suda oh Israel pwainkihda omw dipwisou kan wihd, sukehn loangalap, lehn olip, oh mehn doal mwenge kan.
\v 18-19 Mehn Damaskus pwainda omw dipwisou kan oh wahnsahpw akan, re pwainki wain sang Elpon oh likou wunen sihpw sang Sahar. Re wiliankihda omw dipwisou kan mete kehlail oh mehn doal mwenge.
\v 20 Mehn Dedan kawiliankihda omw dipwisou kan pilangkes mehn mwohd pohn oahs.
\v 21 Mehn Arepia kan oh kaun akan en wehin Kedar pwainkihda omw dipwisou kan sihpw, sihmpwul oh kuht.
\v 22 Sounnetinet kan en Sipa oh Raama kawiliankihda omw dipwisou kan kisin takai kesempwal, kohl, oh mehn doal mwenge keieu kaselel.
\v 23 Kahnimw kan en Aran, Kanne, oh Eden, sounnetinet kan sang Sipa, kahnimw kan en Ahsur oh Kilmad—irail koaros kin kawiliali rehmw.
\v 24 Re netikihong uhk likou kaselel, likou poh ntahn mwel, oh likou deiad, lohs poh mwangerenger lingan akan, oh sahl ahlap oh ahtikitik me wiawihda kaselel.
\v 25 Omw dipwisou kan kin wisik pohn polohn sohp me kin wa dipwisou laud kan.\x - \xo 27:25 \xt Kaud. 18.11-19.\x*
\q1 “Ke rasehng sohp pwoat nan madau
\q1 Me toutoukihla dipwisou tohto.
\q1 
\v 26 Ni ahnsou me noumw sounpadil kan seikinuhkalahng nan madau,
\q1 Kisinieng en palimese ehu ahpw kauweiukala wasa me dohsang sahpw.
\q1 
\v 27 Omw dipwisoun netinet kaselel kan,
\q1 Noumw sehla koaros,
\q1 Noumw kahpinte kan oh noumw sounnetinet kan,
\q1 Sounpei koaros me mi pohn sohpo—
\q1 Koaros, kihrla nan madau
\q1 Ni ahnsou me weromw sohpo ohla.
\q1 
\v 28 Ngilen sehla kan ar weriwer
\q1 Peipeilahng ni oaroahro.
\b
\q1 
\v 29 “Sohp koaros solahr towe,
\q1 Oh sehla koaros samwalahr nansapw.
\q1 
\v 30 Irail koaros mwahmwahieikin uhk kowahlap,
\q1 Re kesedahng pehs pohn moangarail oh tapwutapwur nan pehs.
\q1 
\v 31 Re sehkasang pitenmoangarail kan pwehki kowe
\q1 Oh pwuhriong nan likoun nsensuwed.
\q1 Mohngiongirail kan tihwohla kowahlap ni ar wie sengiseng.
\q1 
\v 32 Re wia koulen kedepwidepw pwoat ong uhk:
\q1 ‘Ihs me kak kapahrekiong Dair,
\q1 Dair me ahnsou wet nennenlahr nan madau?
\q1 
\v 33 Ni ahnsou me omw dipwisoun netila kan kin wisiklahng nan wehi kan,
\q1 Ke kin kaitarala anahn en wehi koaros.
\q1 Nanmwarki kan kin kepwehpwehkihla
\q1 Omw dipwisou kan.
\q1 
\v 34 Eri, met ke ohlahr nan madau;
\q1 Ke kihrlahr nan kepin madau.
\q1 Omw dipwisou oh koaros me doadoahkohng uhk
\q1 Iang uhk sohrala nan madau.’
\p 
\v 35 “Aramas koaros me kin kousoan ni oaroahro pwuriamweikihla paisuwed me lelohng uhk. Ar nanmwarki kan pil masepwehkada, oh ar masepwehk sansal ni silengirail kan.
\v 36 Ke sohralahr, sohralahr kohkohlahte, oh sounnetinet kan wasa koaros nin sampah masepwehkada, re salohkihda pwe re de iang ale paisuwed me lelohng uhk.”
\c 28
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Nanmwarkien Dair
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, ndaiong kaun en Dair dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong: Ni omwi aklapalapalahr, komw kupwukupwure me komwi koht emen. Komw mahsanih me komw duwehte koht emen me ket nan mwoale, sehd ahpw kapilpene. Ele komw pahn kupwukupwure me komwi koht emen, ahpw soh, komwi aramas emen me pahn mehla, me sohte pahn mour poatopoat.
\v 3 Komw kupwukupwure me komwi kupwurokong sang Danel,\f p \fr 28:3 \fk DANEL: \ft Daniel (tehk 14.14).\f* me sohte mehkot rir kak rirsang komwi.
\p 
\v 4 Omwi kupwurokong oh koahiek kahrehiong omwi kepwehpehkihla kohl oh silper.
\v 5 Komwi wiadahr pesines kehlail kei oh usehla ketiketiki omwi wihn sang nan pesines pwuko. Ia uwen omwi pohnmwahsohki omwi reken kepwe!
\p 
\v 6 “Eri met, iet dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Pwehki omwi kupwukupwure me komw kupwurokong duwehte koht emen,
\v 7 I pahn ketikihdo imwintihti lemei kan pwe re en mahweniong komwi. Re pahn kamwomwala soahng kaselel koaros me komwi sapwellimanikier sang ni omwi koahiek oh kupwurokong.
\v 8 Re pahn kemeikomwihla oh keseikomwilahng nansed.
\v 9 Ni ar pahn kohdo pwe re en kemeikomwihla, ia duwe, komwi pahn kupwukupwurehte me komwi koht emen? Ni omwi pahn ket mwohn irail kan me pahn kemeikomwihla, komwi pahn duwehla aramas emen me pahn mehla, kaidehn emen me pahn rasehng Koht me pahn mour poatopoat.
\v 10 Komwi pahn sipalla duwehte kidi men nan pehn mehn liki kan me sohte ar koht. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me wiadahr koasoandi wet.”
\s1 Pwupwulahn Nanmwarkien Dair
\p 
\v 11 KAUN-O pwurehng mahsanihong ie,
\v 12 “Kowe, nein aramas, mwahieiki imwilahn mour me awiawih nanmwarkien Dair. Ndaiong dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: Komwi wiahier mehn karasepe kaselel ehu mahs. Ia uwen omwi kupwurokong oh silang mwahu!
\v 13 Komwi kin ketiket nan Ihden, sapwellimen Koht mwetuwel, oh kin kapwatki soangen kapwat kaselel koaros: rupi, diamon, topas, peril, karnelian, oh sasper; sapair, emerald, oh karned kan. Komwi pil sapwellimaniki kapwat kohl. Mehn kapwat pwukat wiawidahng komwi ni rahn me komwi kapikipikda.
\v 14 I ketikihdi tohnleng kamasepwehk men wasao pwehn sinsilei komwi. Komwi kousoan pohn ei nahna sarawio oh kin ketiketseli nanpwungen kisin takai kesempwal lingan akan.
\v 15 Komwi kin wiewia mwahu sang ni rahn me komwi kepikipikdao lao komwi tepida wia me suwed.
\v 16 Komwi kin kedirepwkihla omwi netinet kan, oh met kahrehiong komwi en wiahda dihp oh kamaramas. Eri, ihme kahrehda ei kasareikomwihsang ni ei nahna sarawio, oh tohnleng me sinsilei komwio ahpw pwakihkomwihsang nanpwungen kisin takai kesempwal lingan akan.
\v 17 Komwi kin pohnmwahsohki omwi silang mwahu, oh omwi ndand me kahrehiong omwi wia mwekid en aramas pweipwei men. Pwehki met me kahrehda ei kesehkinkomwihdi nanpwel oh keseikomwihla pwehn wia mehn karasepe ehu ong nanmwarki teikan.
\v 18 Omwi doadoahk en netinet me inenen suwed me kahrehda omwi wasahn kaudok kan saminla. Ihme kahrehda I isingkihdi kahnimwo nanpwel. Koaros me kilang komwi met, kilang duwen omwi wialahr pehs.
\v 19 Komwi sohralahr, sohralahr kohkohlahte, oh wehi koaros me wehwehkinkomwihla masepwehkada, salohda pwe imwilahn ar mour de duwehte komwi.”
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Saidon
\p 
\v 20 KAUN-O mahsanihong ie,\x - \xo 28:20 \xt Soel 3.4-8; Sek. 9.1-2; Mad. 11.21-22; Luk 10.13-14.\x*
\v 21 “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla kahnimw Saidon.
\v 22 Ndaiong tohn wasao dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih duwen irail: Ngehi me omw imwintihti, Saidon; aramas akan pahn kapinga ie pwehki dahme I wiahiong uhk. Re pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, I pahn kasalehda duwen ei sarawi ni ei pahn kaloke irail kan me koukousoan rehmw.
\v 23 I pahn kadarodo soumwahu pohmw oh kupwurehda pwe nta en pwilipwil pohn omw ahl akan. Mahwen pahn lelohng uhk pali koaros, oh noumw aramas akan pahn mehla. Ke ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\s1 Israel pahn ale Kupwuramwahu
\p 
\v 24 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie, “Sohte ehu wehi nanpwungen wehi kan me kapilpene Israel me mwamwahlikihla Israel pahn pwurehng duwehte tuhke tekatek pwehn kamedekehla Israel. Ihme re pahn esehkihla me ngehi KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie.”
\p 
\v 25 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih, “I pahn kapwurehdo mehn Israel kan sang nan wehi kan me I kamwarakiraillahng ie, oh wehi koaros ahpw pahn esehla me I me sarawi. Mehn Israel kan pahn kousoanla nan pein sapwarail, sahpw me I ketikihong ei ladu Seikop.
\v 26 Re pahn kousoan wasao ni onepek mwahu. Re pahn kauwada ihmw kan oh padokedi mwetuwel en wain. I pahn kaloke mehn mparail kan me kin mwamwahlikin irail, oh Israel pahn onepek mwahu. Irail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, arail Koht.”
\c 29
\s1 Kokohp me Uhwong Isip
\p 
\v 1 Ni rahn kaeisek riau en kaeisek en sounpwong en sounpar kaeisek en at kalipilipala, KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,\x - \xo 29:1 \xt Ais. 19.1-25; Ser. 46.2-26.\x*
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla nanmwarkien Isip. Ndaiong duwen ih oh wehin Isip eh pahn ale lokolok.
\v 3 Ndaiong me iet dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong nanmwarkien Isip: Ngehi me omwi imwintihti, kowe kieil kamasepwehk, me wonohn nan pillap. Komwi mahsanih me sapwellimomwi Pillap Nail oh komwi me wiahda.
\v 4 I pahn ketikihong kehs ni doauosomwien oh kupwurehda pwe kisin mwahmw akan en nan sapwellimomwi pillapo en pasehng ni kilimwen. I ahpw pahn apihkomwihdahsang nan Nail, iangahki mwahmw kan me pasehng ni kilimwen.
\v 5 I pahn keseikomwihla iangahki mwahmw kan koaros nan sapwtehn. Kahlepomwi pahn pwupwudiong nanpwel oh wonohn powe sohte seridi. I pahn ketikihong menpihr kan oh mahn akan pwe re en kangala.
\v 6 Eri, mehn Isip koaros ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\p KAUN-O eri mahsanih, “Mehn Israel kan kin koapworopworki kumwail mehn Isip kan amwail sawas, ahpw kumwail sohte mwahusang kisin rahntuhke luwet pwoat.\x - \xo 29:6 \xt Ais. 36.6.\x*
\v 7 Ni ar idengek rehmwail, kumwail tupwedi, oh diperemwail kan doakoahdi pahn pehrail kan oh kauwehla tihnsewarail kan.
\v 8 Eri met, ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanihong kumwail me I pahn kupwurehda pwe aramas akan en mahwenkihong kumwail neirail kedlahs akan, oh re pahn kemehla noumwail aramas oh mahn akan.
\v 9 Isip pahn wiahla sapwtehn ehu. Eri, kumwail ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\p “Pwehki omw nda me Nail iei ahmw oh kowe me wiahda,
\v 10 ihme kahrehda ei wia omw imwintihti oh imwintihtien omw Pillap Nail. I pahn wiahkihla Isip sapwtehn ehu, sang ni kahnimw Mikdol ni paliepeng kolahng ni kahnimw Aswan ni palieir, lao lellahng ni irepen Sudan.
\v 11 Sohte aramas de mahn pahn kotehla. Sohte mehkot pahn kousoan wasao erein sounpar pahisek.
\v 12 I pahn wiahkihla Isip sahpw me keieu tehn nan sampah pwon. Erein sounpar pahisek kahnimw kan en Isip pahn wonohn wiewia mohn kahnimw, mohn kahnimw me suwedsang kahnimw teikan. I pahn kupwurehda pwe mehn Isip kan en duwehla aramas akan me kin sopohsang nan mahwen. Re pahn sopolahng nan wehi koaros oh kousoanla nanpwungen aramas teikan.”
\p 
\v 13 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Mwurin sounpar pahisek I pahn kapwurehdo mehn Isip kan sang nan wehi kan me I kamwarakiraillahng ie,
\v 14 oh I pahn mweidohng irail en kousoan ni palieir en Isip, ni uhdahn wasa re tepin kousoan ie. Re ahpw pahn wia wehi luwet ehu wasao,
\v 15 wehi me keieu luwet sang koaros, oh sohte pahn pwurehng kaunda ehu wehi tohrohr. I pahn kupwurehda pwehn sohla me kesempwalkin irail me kahrehda re sohla pahn kak kihdi wehi ehu pahn ar manaman.
\v 16 Israel sohla pahn pwurehng koapworopworki arail sawas. En Isip imwila suwed pahn katamanohng Israel duwen sapwung en ar koapworopworkinirailla. Israel ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie.”
\s1 Nanmwarki Nepukadnesar Pahn Kalowehdi Isip
\p 
\v 17 Ni rahn keieu en sounpwong keieu en kerieisek isuhn sounpar en at kalipilipala, KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 18 “Kowe, nein aramas, Nepukadnesar, nanmwarkien Papilonia mahweniongehr Dair. E ketin koasoanehdi sapwellime sounpei kan en wahda wisik toutou kan me kahrehda moangarail kan madkihda oh pwopworail kan ohkihla, ahpw nanmwarkio de sapwellime karis sohte mwahn paieki mehkot sang ar doadoahk laudo.
\v 19 Eri, iet me ngehi KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih: I pahn ketikihong Nanmwarki Nepukadnesar wehin Isip. E pahn kulihasang dipwisou kan oh kauwehla oh ketikihsang kepwe kesempwal koaros pwehn pwainkihla en sapwellime karis kan ar doadoahk.
\v 20 I pahn ketikihong Isip pwehn wia pweinen sapwellime doadoahk, pwehki sapwellime karis wie doadoahkohng ie. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\p 
\v 21 “Ni met eh pahn pweida, I pahn kupwurehda pwe mehn Israel kan en kehlail oh mweidohng, kowe, Esekiel, en koasoi wasa me aramas koaros kak rong uhk, pwe re en ese me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\c 30
\s1 KAUN-O Pahn ketin Kaloke Isip
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O pwurehng mahseniong ie.
\v 2 E mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, wiahda kokohp oh kalohkihda dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih. Ke pahn ngihl laudikihda koasoi pwukat:
\q1 Rahn kamasepwehk kowahlap ehu kohkohdo!
\q1 
\v 3 Rahno kerendohr, ni rahn me KAUN-O pahn ketin mwekid,
\q1 Rahnen depwek mosul oh apwal ong wehi kan.
\q1 
\v 4 Mie mahwen pahn wiawi nan Isip
\q1 Oh paisuwed laud nan Sudan.
\q1 Me tohto nan Isip pahn kamakamala;
\q1 Dipwisoun wehio pahn kulsang
\q1 Oh wehio pahn ohla douluhl.
\p 
\v 5 “Mahweno pahn pil kemehla sounpei kan me pweipweido sang Sudan, Lipia, Lidia, Arepia, Kup, oh pil sang rehn nei aramas akan.”
\p 
\v 6 KAUN-O ketin mahsanih, “Sounpoadoarepen Isip koaros pahn mehla nan mahwen, sang Mikdol ni paliepeng lel Aswan ni palieir. Nein Isip karis en sounpei aklapalapo pahn mwomwla. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\v 7 Sahpwo pahn wiahla sapwtehn me keieu laud nan sampah pwon, oh eh kahnimw kan pahn wiahla mohn kahnimw douluhl.
\v 8 Ni ei isikada Isip oh poadoarepe kan mehla, eri, re ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 9 “Ni rahno eh pahn leledo oh Isip mwomwla, I pahn kadarodo meninkeder kei me pahn dake sohp kei pwehn kamwakidada mehn Sudan kan, oh re pahn masepwehkada. Rahno samwodohr!”
\p 
\v 10 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “I pahn doadoahngki Nepukadnesar, nanmwarkien Papilonia pwehn katokihedi en Isip eh reken kepwe.
\v 11 Ih oh sapwellime sounpei lemei kan pahn ketido pwehn kauwehla wehio. Re pahn mahwenkihong Isip kedlahs, oh sahpwo pahn direkihla paliwar mehla.
\v 12 I pahn kamadahda Nail oh ketikihdi Isip pahn manaman en aramas suwed kan. Mehn liki kan pahn kauwehla sahpwo pwon. Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen.”
\p 
\v 13 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “I pahn kamwomwala dikedik en eni kan oh koht likamw akan nan Mempis. Sohte emen pahn kaunda Isip, oh I pahn kamasakada aramas koaros.
\v 14 I pahn wiahkihla palieir en Isip sapwtehn oh isikala kahnimw Soan ni paliepeng. I pahn kaloke poahsoan kaunen kahnimw Dihpes.
\v 15 I pahn mweidohng kahnimw Pelusium, en Isip wasahn poadoandoar kehlail, en kehn engin ei engieng. I pahn kamwomwala en Dihpes eh reken kepwe.
\v 16 I pahn isikada Isip, oh Pelusium pahn weirek kowahlap. Kehl kan en Dihpes pahn rengkidi, oh kahnimwo pahn duhla.
\v 17 Mwahnakapw akan en kahnimw kan en Iliopolis oh Pupastis pahn mehla nan mahwen, oh aramas teikan pahn selidi oh wisiksang.
\v 18 Rotorot pahn kipehdi Dapanihs ni ei pahn kauwehla manaman en Isip oh katokihedi ar kehlail me re kin pohnmwahsohki. Pelien depwek pali pahn kipehdi Isip, oh tohn eh kahnimwo pahn selidi oh wisiksang.
\v 19 Ni ei pahn kaloke Isip ni duwe met, re pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\s1 Manaman en Nanmwarkien Isip Ohla
\p 
\v 20 Ni rahn keisuh en keieun sounpwong en kaeisek ehun sounpar en at kalipilipala, KAUN-O ketin mahseniong ie.
\v 21 E mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, I kauwelahr nin limen nanmwarkien Isip. Sohte emen me kidimpene ohla wet de kihong lipwene pwe en kak mwahula oh kehlailda oh kak pwurehng kolada kedlahs.
\v 22 Eri met, iet dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih: Ngehi me imwintihti en nanmwarkien Isip. I pahn kauwehla nin lime pali koaros—pali mwahuo oh pali me ohlahro—oh kedlahs ahpw pahn pwupwudihsang nin limeo.
\v 23 I pahn kamwarakpeseng mehn Isip kan wasa koaros nin sampah.
\v 24 Mwuhr I ahpw pahn kakehlahda nin limen nanmwarkien Papilonia oh ketikihong nei kedlahs nin lime. Ahpw I pahn kauwehla nin limen nanmwarkien Isip, oh e pahn weiweirek oh sipalla mwohn mesen sapwellime imwintihti.
\v 25 Ei, I pahn kaluwetehla nanmwarkien Isip oh kakehlahda nanmwarkien Papilonia. Ni ei pahn ketikihong nei kedlahs oh e pahn kauwalahng Isip, aramas koaros pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\v 26 I pahn kamwarakpeseng mehn Isip kan wasa koaros nin sampah. Irail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\c 31
\s1 Isip Karasarasohng Tuhke Sidar pwoat
\p 
\v 1 Ni rahn keieu en kesiluh en sounpwong en sounpar kaeisek ehu en at kalipilipala, KAUN-O ketin mahseniong ie.
\v 2 E mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, ndaiong nanmwarkien Isip oh sapwellime aramas koaros:
\q1 Ia uwen omwi manaman!
\q1 Dahme I pahn kak karasahiong komwi?
\q1 
\v 3 Komwi rasehng tuhke sidar pwoat nan Lepanon,
\q1 Me teh lingan oh rarahn,
\q1 Tuhke pwoat me inenen reirei leldalahng pahn depwek.
\q1 
\v 4 Mie pihl mehn kakairada,
\q1 Oh pillap pahn pwehl mehn kalamwurih.
\q1 Pihl pwukat kin kalamwurih wasa me tuhkeo kekeirda ie
\q1 Oh kadarpeseng piletik ong tuhke koaros en nanwelo.
\q1 
\v 5 E keirda oh reireisang tuhke teikan,
\q1 Oh rah kan losolosala oh reireila,
\q1 Pwehki eh kelemwur mwahu.
\q1 
\v 6 Soangen menpihr koaros kin wiahda pasarail nin rah kan;
\q1 Mahn lawalo kan kin neitik pahn mweteh;
\q1 Wehi kan en sampah kin kommoaldi pahn mweteh.
\q1 
\v 7 Ia uwen lingan en tuhkeo—
\q1 Me ile, inenen rah reirei.
\q1 Kalowe kan leldilahng wasa loal ni piletik pwilipwil kan.
\q1 
\v 8 Sohte sidar pwoat me mi nan sapwellimen Koht mwetuwel me kak pahrekiong.
\q1 Sohte tuhke pir pwoat me rah kan duwehte met,
\q1 Oh sohte tuhke dupwopw pwoat me rarahn duwehte.
\q1 Sohte tuhke pwoat me mi nan sapwellimen Koht mwetuwel me lingan duwehte.\x - \xo 31:8 \xt Sen. 2.9.\x*
\q1 
\v 9 Ngehi me wiahda pwe en lingan, oh rarahn.
\q1 Tuhke koaros nan Ihden nan sapwellimen Koht mwetuwelo kin peiriniong.
\p 
\v 10 “Eri met, ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, pahn mahsanihong uhk dahme pahn wiawihong tuhke pwoato me keirda lao leldalahng pahn depwek. Ni eh reireila e aklapalapala;
\v 11 ihme I soikikihla oh mweidohng kaunen liki men en ahnekihla. E pahn wiahiong tuhkeo dahme konehng eh suwed kan.
\v 12 Mehn liki lemei kan pahn pelehdi oh kesehla. Rah kan oh rah ohla kan pahn pwupwudiong pohn nahna koaros oh wahu koaros nan sahpwo. Wehi koaros me koukousoan pahn mweteh pahn mweselsang.
\v 13 Menpihr kan pahn pihrdo oh sok pohn tuhke pwupwudio, oh mahn lawalo kan pahn alu pohn rah kan.
\v 14 Eri, sang met kohla, sohte tuhke pwoat pahn pwurehng reireila de leldalahng pahn depwek, mehnda ma e kelemwur mwahu. Irail koaros koasoandiongehr en mehla duwehte aramas, koasoandiongehr en patehng irail kan me kohdilahr nan wasahn me melahr akan.”
\p 
\v 15 Iet dahme KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih: “Ni rahn me tuhkeo pahn kohdihla nan wasahn me melahr akan, I pahn kupwurehda pwe pihl en pahn pwehl kan en kaduhala pwehn wia kilel en nsensuwed. I pahn katokihedi pwilipwil en pillap akan oh sohla mweidohng piletik tohto en pwiliwei. Pwehki tuhkeo eh melahr, I pahn ketikihdo rotorot pohn Nahnahn Lepanon kan oh kupwurehda pwe tuhke koaros nanwelo en mengidi.
\v 16 Ni ei pahn kadardilahng nan wasahn me melahr akan, ngilen eh pahn pwupwudi pahn itikada wehi kan. Tuhke koaros nan Ihden, tuhke pilipil koaros, tuhke kelemwur mwahu nan Lepanon me kohdilahr pahn sampah pahn perenkihda eh pwupwudi.
\v 17 Re pahn iang ih kohdihla nan wasahn me melahr akan pwe re en patehng me pwupwudier kan. Oh koaros me kin kousoan pahn mweteh pahn mwarahkpeseng nan wehi kan.
\p 
\v 18 “Tuhkeo iei nanmwarkien Isip oh sapwellime aramas koaros. Pil sohte tuhke nan Ihden me ile oh lingan duwehte. Ahpw met, e duwehte tuhke kan nan Ihden, e pahn kohdihla nan wasahn me melahr akan oh patehng me sohte ar koht kan oh irail kan me melahr nan mahwen. Ngehi me mahsen,” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie me mahsanih met.
\c 32
\s1 Nanmwarkien Isip Karasarasohng Kieil men
\p 
\v 1 Ni rahn keieu en kaeisek riau en sounpwong en kaeisek riau en sounpar en at kalipilipala, KAUN-O ketin mahseniong ie.
\v 2 E mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, wiahiong nanmwarkien Isip kehkehlik kehlail ehu. Kihong mahsen wet me sang rehi: Omwi mwekid kan duwehte mwekid en laion men nanpwungen wehi kan, ahpw soh, pwe komw duwehte kieil men me kin likelikemisik kohwei nan pillap akan. Komw kin kakiriedihkihda pihlo nehmw oh kasaminehkihla pillap akan.
\v 3 Ni ahnsou me wehi tohto kin pokonpene, I pahn saingkomwihdi nan ei uhk oh mweidohng re en apihadahng uhko pohn oaroahr.
\v 4 I pahn keseikomwilahng nanpwel oh ketikihdo menpihr koaros oh mahn koaros en sampah pwe re en kangkomwihla.
\v 5 I pahn kadirehkihla nahna oh wahu kan kahlepomw me matalahr.
\v 6 I pahn wudekihla ntahmw lao e wudeklahng pohn nahna kan oh audehla piletik kan.
\v 7 Ni ei pahn kauweikomwihla, pahnlahng pahn rotala oh perehla usu kan. Ketipin pahn rirla pahn depwek, oh maram sohla pahn marain.\x - \xo 32:7 \xt Ais. 13.10; Mad. 24.29; Mk. 13.24-25; Luk 21.25; Kaud. 6.12-13; 8.12.\x*
\v 8 I pahn kakunla marain koaros nanleng oh kipehkihdi sampah rotorot mosul. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\p 
\v 9 “Wehi tohto pahn pwunodada ni ei pahn kalohkihda rohng en omwi mwomwlahr ong sahpw akan me komwi sohte mwahn kin mwahngih.
\v 10 Dahme I pahn wiahiong uhk pahn kapwuriamweiong wehi tohto. Ni ei pahn palkihwei nei kedlahs, nanmwarki kan pahn rerrerki ar masepwehk. Ni rahnen omwi pahn pwupwudio, irail koaros pahn rerrerki ar masepwehk pwehki keper ong ar mour.”
\p 
\v 11 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanihong nanmwarkien Isip, “Komwi pahn uh mwohn sapwellimen nanmwarkien Papilonia kedlahs.
\v 12 I pahn mweidohng sounpei kan sang nan wehi lemei kan re en usada neirail kedlahs oh kemehla sapwellimomwi aramas koaros. Sapwellimomwi aramas koaros oh mehkoaros me komwi kin pohnmwahsohki pahn mwomwla.
\v 13 I pahn kemehla sapwellimomwi kou kan nan peden pihl koaros. E solahr pahn mie aramas de kou me pahn kakiriedihada pihl kan.
\v 14 I pahn mweidohng omwi pihl kan en nennenla oh mwakelekella, oh omwi pillap akan en pwilipwiliwei ni meleilei. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\v 15 Ni ei pahn wiahkihla Isip sapwtehn ehu oh kamwomwala me mour koaros wasao, re pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O.
\v 16 Kehkehlik kehlail wet pahn wiahla koulen kedepwidepw pwoat. Lihen wehi kan pahn koulki ni ar pahn mwahieiki Isip oh towe kan. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\s1 Wasahn me Melahr akan
\p 
\v 17 Ni rahn kaeisek limau en keieun sounpwong en kaeisek riaun sounpar en at kalipilipala, KAUN-O ketin mahseniong ie.
\v 18 E mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, mwahieiki aramas ngeder en Isip. Kadariraildilahng nan wasahn me melahr akan iangahki wehi kehlail teikan.
\v 19 Ndaiong irail:
\q1 “Ia duwe, kumwail lemeleme me kumwail lingan sang meteikan?
\q1 Kumwail pahn kohdilahng nan wasahn me melahr akan
\q2 oh wonohn wasao nanpwungen irail kan me sohte wauneki Koht.
\p 
\v 20 “Mehn Isip kan pahn iang irail kan me kamakamalahr nan mahwen pwupwudi. Kedlahs pwoat onopadahr pwehn kemeirailla koaros.
\v 21 Me keieu ndand nan mahwen kan oh irail kan me kin uhpalihki mehn Isip nan mahwen pahn kasamwoh mehn Isip kan nan wasahn me melahr akan. Re pahn weriwer, ndinda: ‘Irail kan me sohte wauneki Koht me kamakamalahr nan mahwen kohdidohr oh wonohn wasaht!’
\p 
\v 22 “Asiria mihmi wasao, iangahki sousoun nah sounpei kan me kapilpene. Irail koaros kamakamala nan mahwen,
\v 23 oh ar sousou kan me mi wasa keieu loal nan wasahn me melahr akan. Nah sounpei kan pwupwudi nan mahwen, oh ar sousou kan kapilpene eh sousou. Mahs re kamasakada sapwen me momour kan.
\p 
\v 24 “Elam mihmi wasao, iangahki sousoun nah sounpei kan me kapilpene. Irail koaros kamakamala nan mahwen, oh re sohte sirkumsais kohdihla nan wasahn me melahr akan. Ni ar momour re kamasakada wasa, ahpw met re melahr wonohn oh sarohdier.
\v 25 Elam wonohn nanpwungen irail kan me kamakamalahr nan mahwen, oh sousoun nah sounpei kan kapilpene. Irail koaros sohte sirkumsais, irail koaros kamakamala nan mahwen. Ni ar momour re kamasakada wasa, ahpw met re melahr wonohn oh sarohdier, re iang ale pwais en irail kan me kamakamalahr nan mahwen.
\p 
\v 26 “Mesek oh Tupal mihmi wasao, iangahki sousoun neira sounpei kan me kapilirapene. Irail koaros sohte sirkumsais, koaros kamakamala nan mahwen, ahpw mahs re kamasakada me momour kan.
\v 27 Sohte wahu kohieng irail ni ar seridi duwehte me kin wiawihong me ndand en kawa ko, me kohdilahng nan wasahn me melahr akan wa neirail tehtehn mahwen kan, neirail kedlahs kan koasoansoandi pahn moangarail oh neirail mehn sansar pohn paliwararail kan. Mahs sounpei ndand pwukat ahneki manaman me itarohng kamasakada me momour kan.
\p 
\v 28 “Iei duwen mehn Isip kan ar pahn wonohn nanpwungen me sohte sirkumsais kan me kamakamala nan mahwen.
\p 
\v 29 “Edom mihmi wasao iangahki eh nanmwarki kan oh kaun akan. Iei irail sounpei kehlail kei, ahpw met re wonohnehr nan wasahn me melahr akan, iang me sohte sirkumsais kan me kamakamalahr nan mahwen.
\p 
\v 30 “Soupeidi koaros en paliepeng mihmi wasao, oh pil mehn Saidon. Mahs ar manaman kipehkihdi wasa masepwehk, ahpw met re sarohdier kohdilahr iang irail kan me kamakamalahr nan mahwen oh seridier, sohte sirkumsais. Re iang ale saroh me irail kan me kohdilahr nan wasahn me melahr akan aleier.
\p 
\v 31 “Peudiahlpen irail pwukat koaros me kamakamalahr nan mahwen pahn kansenamwahu ong nanmwarkien Isip oh sapwellime karis,” KAUN-O me mahsanih met.
\p 
\v 32 “I kupwuredahr nanmwarkien Isip en kamasakada me momour kan, ahpw ih oh sapwellime karis pahn kamakamala oh kommoaldi iang irail kan me sohte sirkumsais me kamakamalahr nan mahwen.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\c 33
\s1 Koht ketin Idihada Esekiel en Wiahla Silepe men
\r (Esekiel 3.16-21)
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, padahkihong tohn omw wehi dahme kin wiawi ni ei kin kadarowohng sahpw ehu mahwen. Tohn sahpwo kin pilada emen rehrail pwe en kin wia silepe.
\v 3 Eri, ni ahnsou me silepeo kin kilang imwintihti kan ar kin kohkodohng sahpwo, e kin peuk koronihda pwe en kehsehki aramas koaros.
\v 4 Ma emen pahn rong, ahpw sohte men tehk, imwintihti kan pahn kohdo oh kemehla; eri, pein ih me pahn pwukoakihdi eh mehla.
\v 5 Pein ih me pwukoahki irair wet, pwehki eh sohte men tehk pakairpen koronihdao. Ma e kanahieng tehkada pakairo, e kakete pitla.
\v 6 Ahpw ma silepeo, ni eh kilangada imwintihti kan ar samwodohr, e ahpw sohte peuk koronihdao oh pakairkihong aramas akan, imwintihti ko pahn kohdo kemehla aramas dipan pwuko. Eri, I uhdahn pahn kapwukoahnki silepeo en aramas ako ar mehla.
\p 
\v 7 “Kowe, nein aramas, met I pahn wiahkinuhkala silepen wehin Israel pwon. Ke pahn padahkihong irail pakair wet me I kihong uhk.
\v 8 Ma I mahsanih me aramas suwed men pahn mehla, ke ahpw sohte padahkihong en wekidala eh mour pwe en kak doarehla eh mour, e uhdahn pahn mehla nan dipe kan; eri, I pahn kapwukoahnkin uhk eh mehla.
\v 9 A ma ke pahn padahkihong aramas suwed men en tokedihsang dipe kan, e ahpw sohte tokedihsang, e pahn mehla nan dipe kan; eri, ke pahn mourla.”
\s1 Emenemen en Pein Pwukoahki Dipe kan
\r (Esekiel 3.16-21)
\p 
\v 10 KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, katamanki mehn Israel ko dahme re kin ndindao: ‘Se toutoukilahr dipat akan oh sapwung kan me se wiadahr; se inenen ohkilahr. Ia duwen at kak mourla?’
\v 11 Padahkihong irail ni mwarei, pwe ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalap, Koht ieias, I sohte kin kupwurperenki mehlahn aramas dipan. Ahpw en wiliakapwasang eh suwed pwe en mour. Mehn Israel kan, kumwail tokedihsang amwail wiewia suwed kan. Dahme kumwail men mehkihla?
\p 
\v 12 “Eri met, kowe, nein aramas, padahkihong mehn Israel kan me ni ahnsou me aramas mwahu men kin wiahda dihp, e wiewia mwahu kan sohte pahn kamourala. A ma aramas suwed men pahn tokedihsang wia me suwed, e sohte pahn ale lokolok; oh ma aramas mwahu men pahn tapihada wia me suwed, e sohte pahn mourla.
\v 13 Ma I inoukihong mour ong aramas mwahu men, e ahpw medemedewe me eh wiewia mwahu kan itarehr, oh ahpw tapihada wiahda dihp, I sohte pahn tamataman eh wiewia mwahu kan. E pahn mehla pwehki dipe kan.
\v 14 Ma I padahkihong aramas suwed men me e pahn mehla, e ahpw tokedihang dipe kan oh wia dahme pwung oh mwahu—
\v 15 ni karasepe, ma e kapwurehla soahng ehu me e kihsang aramas mehn wia kadehdepen pweipwand de kapwurehla dipwisou me e pirapahda—ma e pahn tokedihsang wiewia dihp oh idawehn kosonned akan me kin kihong mour, e sohte pahn mehla, ahpw e pahn mourla.
\v 16 I uhdahn pahn mahkikihong dipe kan. E pahn mourla pwehki eh wiadahr dahme mwahu oh pwung.
\p 
\v 17 “Eri, tohn omw wehi kin ndinda me I kin wia me sapwung! Ahpw soh! Pwe arail wiewia kan me sapwung.
\v 18 Ma aramas pwung men pahn tokedihsang wia me mwahu oh tapihada wia me suwed, e uhdahn pahn mehkihla.
\v 19 Oh ma me dipan emen pahn tokedihsang wia me suwed, e ahpw kin wia me mwahu oh pwung, e pahn mourkihla.
\v 20 Ahpw kumwail mehn Israel kan, kumwail kin ndinda me I kin wia me sapwung. Eri, I pahn kadeingkumwailda nin duwen amwail wiewia kan.”
\s1 Rongen Serusalem eh Ohla
\p 
\v 21 Ni rahn kalimau en kaeisek en sounpwong en sounpar kaeisek riau en at kalipilipala, ohl emen me pitdohsang Serusalem ahpw patohdo oh padahkihong ie duwen kahnimwo eh ohlahr.\x - \xo 33:21 \xt 2 Nan. 25.3-10; Ser. 39.2-8; 52.4-14.\x*
\v 22 Nin soutik, mwohn ohlo eh pwarodo, I pehmada duwen manaman en KAUN-O eh ketin kipeiehdi unsek. Ni ahnsou me ohlo leledo ninmenseng, KAUN-O ahpw ketin kasapahldohng ie manaman en kak lokaia.
\s1 Dipen Aramas akan
\p 
\v 23 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie,
\v 24 “Kowe, nein aramas, ke en ese me aramas akan me kin koukousoan nan mohn kahnimw kan en wehin Israel kin ndinda, ‘Eipraam ih ohl tehmen, ahpw sahpwet pwon kohieng. A kitail me tohto; eri, met kitail pahn sapwenikihla sahpwet.’
\p 
\v 25 “Padahkihong irail dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih: Kumwail kin kang uduk iangahki nta. Kumwail kin kaudokiong dikedik en eni kan. Kumwail kin kemehla aramas. Ia duwe, kumwail lemeleme me kumwail pahn sapwenikihla sahpwo?
\v 26 Kumwail kin koapworopworki noumwail kedlahs kan. Amwail wiewia kan me inenen kasaut. Kumwail koaros kin kamwahl. Ia duwe, kumwail lemeleme me kumwail pahn sapwenikhla sahpwo?
\p 
\v 27 “Padahkihong irail ni mwarei me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa lapalahpie, Koht ieias, me mahsanih me aramas akan me kin kousoan nan mohn kahnimw kan pahn kamakamala. Oh irail kan me kin mihmi nansapw pahn wiahla kenen mahn lawalo kan. Oh irail kan me kin rukuruk pohn nahna kan oh nan pwoaren paip kan pahn soumwahuda oh mehla.
\v 28 I pahn wiahkihla sahpwo sapwtehn ehu. Oh manaman me re kin koapworopworki oh pohnmwahsohki pahn imwisekla. Nahnahn Israel kan pahn wiewella, me kahrehda sohte me pahn kin kak kotehla.
\v 29 Eri, ni ei kin kaloke aramas akan pwehki diparail kan, oh kin kawekiong sahpwo ni sapwtehn, iei ih ahnsou me re pahn dehdehkihla me iei ngehi, KAUN-O.”
\s1 Wahn Mahsen en Soukohpo
\p 
\v 30 KAUN-O eri ketin mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, ke en ese me aramas akan wie koasoakoasoia duwen kowe ni ar kin pokonpene limwahn kelen kahnimw kan oh ni wenihmwen imwarail kan. Re kin ndapene nanpwungarail, ‘Kitail kolahng rong dahme KAUN-O ketin mahsanih met.’ \fig |alt="HK-15A Aramas akan ni imwarail kan" src="" size="col" ref="ESEKIEL 33:30"\fig*
\v 31 Nei aramas akan kin pokonpene pwe re en rong dahme ke pahn ndahng irail, re ahpw sohte kin kapwaiada. Pwe re me liksansalamwahu oh kin usehlahte ar tiahk en mehwo kan.
\v 32 Re kin wiahkin uhk sounkamweit men me kin wiewia koulen limpoak de kesekesengki arp. Re kin rong omw lokaia kan, re ahpw sohte kin kapwaiada.
\v 33 Ahpw ni ahnsou me omw kokohp kan koaros pahn pweida—me iei eh uhdahn pahn pweida—iei ahnsou me aramas pwukat pahn dehdehkihla me soukohp emen koukousoan rehrail.”
\c 34
\s1 Silepe kan en Israel
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla kaun akan en Israel. Kohpada oh ndaiong irail dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih: Meid suwediong kumwail, kumwail silepe kan en Israel! Kumwail kin apwahpwalih pein kumwail, ahpw sohte kin apwalih sihpw kan.
\v 3 Kumwail kin nimasang pilen dihdi en sihpw pwukat, kumwail kin likawihada likou me wiawihsang ni wunen pelin sihpwo, kumwail kin kemehla oh kangala sihpw me keieu kaselel kan. Kumwail ahpw sohte mwahn kin apwalih sihpw kan.
\v 4 Kumwail sohte kin apwalih me luwet kan, kamwahwihala me soumwahu kan, kidimpene ohlahn me kin lipwalipwada kan, kasapahldo me kin kohkohseli mwahl akan, de rapahki me salongala kan. Ahpw kumwail kin wiakauwe irail.
\v 5 Pwehki sihpw kan eh sohte sileparail, re mwarahkpeseng wasa kan, kahrehda mahn lawalo kan kemeirailla oh kangirailla.\x - \xo 34:5 \xt Nemp. 27.17; 1 Nan. 22.17; Mad. 9.36; Mk. 6.34.\x*
\v 6 Eri, nei sihpw kan ahpw kohkohseli mwahl pohn dohl oh pohn nahna kan. Re mwarahkseli wasa koaros nin sampah, oh sohte me apwalih irail de song en rapahkin irail.
\p 
\v 7 “Eri, kumwail silepe kan, kumwail rong dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, mahsanihong kumwail.
\v 8 Ni mwarei, Koht ieias, kumwail rong ie. Nei sihpw kan lohdiongehr pahn mahn lawalo kan me kemeiraillahr oh kangiraillahr, pwehki eh sohte sileparail. Pwehki nei silepe ko ar sohte song en rapahki sihpw ko. Pwehki ar kin apwahpwalihte pein irail oh sohte nsenohki sihpw ko.
\v 9 Eri, kumwail silepe kan, kumwail rong ie.
\v 10 Kumwail en ese me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, I uhwongkumwailehr oh wialahr amwail imwintihti. I pahn adihasang kumwail nei sihpw kan oh solahr mwahn pahn wiahkin kumwail sileparail, pwe kumwail kin apwahpwalihte pein kumwail. I pahn kapitasang kumwail nei sihpw kan, pwe kumwail dehr kin wiahkin irail kanamwail kisin mwenge.”
\s1 Silepe Mwahu
\p 
\v 11 “Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanihong kumwail me pein ngehi pahn rapahki nei sihpw kan oh apwalih irail,
\v 12 nin duwen silepe men eh kin apwalih nah sihpw kan me salongpesengehr ahpw pwurehng kohpene. I pahn pwurehng kasapahliraildo sang wasa koaros me re mwarahkpeseng nin sampah ni rahnen nsensuwed, rahnen paisuwedo.
\v 13 I pahn kahreiraildo sang nan wehin liki kan, kapokoneirailpene oh kasapahldohng irail nan uhdakarail. I pahn kin kamwenge irail pohn nahnahn Israel kan, ni keilen piletik kan, oh wasa koaros me aramas kin kousoan ie.
\v 14 I pahn kin mweidohng pwe re en kin mwengemwengeseli nan mohsen nahna kan oh nan wahu kan, oh pil nan dihpw kapw en wehin Israel.
\v 15 Pein ngehi me pahn wia silepen nei pelin sihpw, oh I pahn kin rapahkihong irail wasahn ar kommoal. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\p 
\v 16 “I pahn kin rapahki me salongalahr akan, kapwurehdo me kin kohkohseli mwahl akan, kidimpene ohlahn me lipwalipwada kan, kamwahwihala me soumwahu kan, oh apwahpwalih me kehlail oh mworourou kan, pwehki ngehi silepe men me kin wia me pwung.
\p 
\v 17 “Eri met, ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, padahkihong kumwail nei pelin sihpw me I pahn kadeikada emenemen kumwail oh katohrepeseng me mwahu kan sang me suwed kan, sihpw kan sang kuht kan.
\v 18 Ekei kumwail sohte itarki kang dihpw me keieu mwahu kan; kumwail kin tiakedi me kumwail sohte kin kang kan. Kumwail kin nim pihl mwakelekel oh kakiriedihada pihl me kumwail sohte kin nim.
\v 19 Eri, nei sihpw teikan ahpw kin kangkang dihpw me kumwail tiakpeseng oh nim pihl me kumwail kakiriedihada.
\p 
\v 20 “Eri met, ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, padahkihong kumwail me I pahn wia kadeikpen kumwail sihpw me kehlail kan oh sihpw me luwet akan.
\v 21 Pwe kumwail kin sikensang oh kodomasang me luwet akan nan pelin sihpwo.
\v 22 Ahpw I pahn doarehla nei pelin sihpwo oh I sohte pahn mweidohng en pwurehng lokolok pahmwail. I pahn wia kopwung ong emenemen nei sihpw oh I pahn katohrehsang me mwahu kan sang rehn me suwed kan.
\v 23 I pahn kihong irail emen nanmwarkien me duwehte ei ladu Depit pwe en wiahla sileparail tehmen, oh en kin apwahpwalih irail.\x - \xo 34:23 \xt Kaud. 7.17.\x*
\v 24 Ngehi, KAUN-O, me pahn kin wia arail Koht, oh emen nanmwarki me duwehte ei ladu Depit pahn kin kakaun irail. Ngehi me mahsaniher met.\x - \xo 34:24 \xt Esek. 37.24.\x*
\v 25 I pahn wiahda inou ehu ong irail me pahn keleirailpene. I pahn koakoahsang mahn keper koaros nan sahpwet, pwe nei sihpw kan en kak silasil mwahu koukousoan nan mohs akan oh meir mwahu nanwel en tuhke kan.
\p 
\v 26 I pahn kupwuramwahwih irail oh mweidohng re en kin kousoan kapil ei dohl sarawi.\f q \fr 34:26 \fk DOHL SARAWI: \ft Tehk 20.40.\f* I pahn kin kupwuramwahwihkin irail keteu ni ahnsou me re pahn anahne.
\v 27 Tuhke kan pahn kin wa, oh mwetuwel kan pahn pweida mwahu; eri, aramas koaros pahn kin silasil mwahu kousoan nan uhdahn sapwarail kan. Ni ei pahn kasaledekihala nei aramas akan sang rehn me kin kaliduwihirail, ni ei pahn kamweidpeseng seliparail kan, iei ahnsou me re pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.
\v 28 Wehi rotorot kan solahr pahn kohdo oh kulihasang ar dipwisou kan, mahn lawalo kan solahr pahn kemeirailla oh kangirailla. Re pahn kousoan ni meleilei oh silasil mwahu, oh sohte masak mehkot.
\v 29 I pahn kihong irail sahpw pwelmwahu oh kaimwisekala lehk nan sahpwo. Wehi teikan solahr pahn mwamwahlkin irail.
\v 30 Aramas koaros pahn esehla me I kin doandoare Israel oh me tohn Israel iei nei aramas. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Laplahpie, me mahmahsen.
\v 31 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih, “Eri, kumwail nei pelin sihpw me I kin kamwenge, kumwail nei aramas, oh ngehi me amwail Koht.”
\c 35
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Kalokolok ong Edom
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,\x - \xo 35:1 \xt Ais. 34.5-17; 63.1-6; Ser. 49.7-22; Esek. 25.12-14; Eimw. 1.11-12; Op. 1-14; Mal. 1.2-5.\x*
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla sapwen Edom.
\v 3 Ndaiong aramas akan dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, ketin mahmahsanih:
\q1 “Nahna kan en Edom, ngehi me amwail imwintihti!
\q1 I pahn wiahkinuhkala sapwtehn ehu.
\q1 
\v 4 I pahn wiahkihla omw kahnimw kan mohn kahnimw kei
\q1 Oh wiahkihla sapwomwen sapwtehn ehu;
\q1 Eri, ke ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi iei KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 5 “Ke wia en Israel eh imwintihti poatopoat oh kemehla nah aramas akan ni ahnsoun eh paisuwed, ni ahnsoun eh lokolongki dipe kan.
\v 6 Eri met, I kahukihla nin duwen ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, Koht ieias—mehla iei imwilahmw, oh ke sohte kak pitsang. Ke dipkidahr dipen kamaramas, oh kamaramas me pahn idawehn uhk.
\v 7 I pahn wiahkihla sahpw nahnahn Edom sapwtehn ehu oh kemehla aramas koaros me pahn seiloakla ie.
\v 8 I pahn kadirehkihla nahna kan paliweren me melahr akan, oh paliweren irail kan me kamakamalahr nan mahwen pahn kadirehla pohn dohl kan oh nan wahu kan.
\v 9 I pahn wiahkinuhkala sapwtehn ehu kohkohlahte, oh sohte me pahn pwurehng kousoan nan omw kahnimw kan. Eri, ke ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi iei KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 10 “Ke kahski me dene wehi riau, Suda oh Israel, iangahki sapwara kan, iei uhdahn sapwomw oh ke pahn kolokol ira, mehnda ma ngehi, KAUN-O, me wia ar Koht.
\v 11 Eri met, I kahukihla nin duwen ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, Koht ieias, me I pahn dupukohng uhk omw lingeringer, omw peirin, oh omw kailongki nei aramas akan. Re pahn ese me I kalokalokehkin uhk dahme ke wiahiongirailehr.
\v 12 Ke ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, karongeier duwen omw kahski ni mwamwahl me nahna kan en Israel wialahr sapwtehn oh e kohienguhker pwe ke en kangala.
\v 13 I karongeier duwen omw lokaia mwamwahl oh suwei me ke lahlahwehkin ie.”
\p 
\v 14 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, eri mahsanih, “I pahn wiahkinuhkala sapwtehn douluhl ehu me kahrehda sampah pwon pahn perenkihda omw pwupwudi,
\v 15 duwehte omw perenkihda mwomwlahn Israel, me uhdahn nin limei. Nahna kan en Seir, ei, sahpw koaros en Edom, pahn wiahla sapwtehn. Eri, aramas koaros ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi iei KAUN-O.”
\c 36
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Kupwuramwahu ong Israel
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, lokaiaiong nahna kan en Israel oh padahkihong irail en rong mahsen me ngehi,
\v 2 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, pahn ketikihong irail: Imwintihti kan en Israel perendahr oh kahski, ‘Met dohl en kawa ko wialahr sapwatail!’
\p 
\v 3 “Eri, wia kokohp oh kalohkihda dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih. Ni ahnsou me wehi keren kan kalowehdi oh kulihasang audepen nahna kan en Israel, aramas koaros kouruhrki Israel.
\v 4 Eri met, rong dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanihong kumwail nahna kan oh dohl akan, ong kumwail piletik kan oh wahu kan, ong kumwail wasa kan me ohlahr, oh kumwail kahnimw kan me audepe kan kulsangehr oh wia mwahllahr pahn wehi kan me kapilkumwailpene.
\p 
\v 5 “Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsaniher ni karakar en ei engieng ong wehi kan me kapilkumwailpene, ahpw mehlel ong Edom. Ni peren oh mwamwahl re kalowehdi nin limeio oh sapwenikihla.
\p 
\v 6 “Eri, wia kokohp ong Israel; padahkihong nahna kan, dohl akan, piletik kan, oh wahu kan dahme ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahmahsanih nan ei engiengdahr kowahlap pwehki kapailok oh saroh me re alehsang wehi teikan.
\v 7 Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, inoukidahr ni kehlail me wehi kan me kapilpene Israel pahn sarohdi.
\v 8 A tuhke kan pohn nahna kan en Israel pahn pwurehng losolosala oh wa ong kumwail, nei aramas akan. Kumwail kereniongehr pwurodohng nan uhdakamwail.
\v 9 I uhpalihkin kumwail, oh I pahn tehk ni keneinei pwe sapwamwailo en pwurehng deideida oh wahnsahpw en poadidi loale.
\v 10 I pahn kahngedereikumwailla. Kumwail pahn kousoanla nan kahnimw kan oh onehda sapahl mehkoaros me ohlahr.
\v 11 I pahn kupwurehda pwe aramas oh kou kan en tohtohla. Kumwail pahn tohtohla sang mahs, oh neitik seri tohto. I pahn mweidohng kumwail en kousoan wasao duwehte amwail kousoanehr ie mahs, oh I pahn kapaikumwailda laud sang mahs. Eri, kumwail ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi iei KAUN-O.
\v 12 I pahn kapwureikumwaildo, nei aramas akan, pwe kumwail en pwurehng kousoan nan sapwamwailo. E pahn wia uhdahn sapwamwail, oh I sohte pahn pwurehng mweidohng noumwail seri kan en duhpekla.
\p 
\v 13 “Ngehi, KAUN-O, mahsanih: Mehlel me aramas akan kin kahdaneki sahpwo sapwen kang aramas, oh re kin nda me e pirapahsang nein wehio seri kan.
\v 14 Ahpw sang met kohla e solahr pahn wia sapwen kang aramas ehu me kin pirapahsang noumwail seri kan. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\v 15 Sahpwo solahr pahn rong wehi kan ar pahn kouruhrki de kilang aramas akan ar pahn kepitki. Sahpwo solahr pahn pirapahsang nein wehio seri kan. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\s1 En Israel Mour Kapw
\p 
\v 16 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 17 “Kowe, nein aramas, ni ahnsou me mehn Israel kan koukousoan nan sapwarailo, re kasaminehkihla mwomwen ar mour oh wiewia kan. I wiahki ar wiewia mehkot me samin ong kaudok duwehte lih emen me kin wia eh soumwahu en lih.\f r \fr 36:17 \fk MEHKOT ME SAMIN...SOUMWAHU EN LIH: \ft Met sang nan Kosonned en Moses me lih emen me wia eh soummwahu wia mehkot samin ong kaudok (tehk Lip. 15.19).\f*
\p 
\v 18 I mweidohng re en kehn engin ei engieng pwehki kamaramas akan me re wiadahr nan sahpwo oh dikedik en eni kan me re kasaminehkihla.
\v 19 I kadeikirailda pwehki mwomwen ar mour oh mwekid, oh kamwarakirailpeseng nan wehin liki kan.
\v 20 Wasa koaros me re kohla ie, re kasohwauwihala mwarei sarawi, pwehki aramas akan pahn nda, ‘Sapwellimen KAUN-O aramas pwukat, ahpw re uhdahn pahn kohkohsang nan sapwelime wehi.’
\v 21 Met kapwunodeiehda, pwehki mehn Israel ko ar kasohwauwihala mwarei sarawi, wasa koaros me re kin kohla ie.
\p 
\v 22 “Eri met, ke pahn padahkihong mehn Israel kan mahsen wet me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, pahn ketikihong irail: ‘Dahme I pahn wiahet kaidehkin pwehki kumwail mehn Israel kan, ahpw pwehki mwarei sarawi, me kumwail kasaminelahr nan wehi koaros me kumwail koasoanla ie.
\v 23 Ni ei pahn kalinganahla mwarei sarawi mwohn wehi kan—mwar me kumwail kasaminelahr—iei ahnsou me re pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen. I pahn doadoahngkin kumwail pwe I en kasalehiong wehi kan duwen ei sarawi.
\v 24 I pahn kahreikumwaildo sang nan wehi koaros, oh sahpw koaros, kahreikumwaildohng nan uhdakamwail.
\v 25 I pahn usupihkin kumwail pihl mwakelekel oh kamwakeleikumwailda sang nan tiahk en pwongih dikedik en eni kan oh sang soahng teikan me kumwail saminkilahr.
\v 26 I pahn kihong kumwail mohngiong kapw ehu oh ngehn kapw ehu. I pahn ketikihsang rehmwail mohngiong keptakai oh ketikihong kumwail mohngiong peik.\x - \xo 36:26 \xt Esek. 11.19-20.\x*
\v 27 I pahn audehkin kumwail ngeniet, oh mwasahn pwe kumwail en kin idawehn ei kosonned akan oh kapwaiada mahsen koaros me I ketikihongkumwailehr.
\v 28 Kumwail eri pahn kousoanla nan sahpw me I ketikihongehr amwail pahpa kahlap ako. Kumwail pahn wiahla nei aramas, oh ngehi amwail Koht.
\v 29 I pahn doarehsang kumwail mehkoaros me pahn kasamineikumwailla. I pahn koasoanehdi pwe wahn pilawa kan en ngederla, pwe lehk lapalap en dehr pwurehng lelohng kumwail.
\v 30 I pahn katohtowehla wahn amwail tuhke kan oh audepen sapwamwail kan, pwe lehk en dehr pwurehng wiawi oh kanamenekeikumwailla nanpwungen wehi kan.
\v 31 Kumwail pahn tamanda amwail tiahk suwed kan oh sapwung kan; ihme kumwail ahpw pahn pein namenengkihla oh koluhkihla mehlel dipamwail kan oh amwail sapwung kan.
\v 32 Mehn Israel kan, I men kumwail en ese oh dehdehki me kaidehkin kumwail me I wiewiahki soahng pwukat koaros. A I men kumwail en pehmada kanamenek oh kasuwedpen amwail wiewia kan. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\p 
\v 33 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih, “Ni ei pahn kamwakeleikumwailda sang nan dipamwail kan koaros, I pahn pwurehng mweidohng kumwail en kousoanla nan amwail kahnimw kan oh kauwada sapahl ihmw me ohlahr akan.
\v 34 Aramas koaros me kin epwehnki keid nan sapwamwail kan kilangehr uwen eh dipwidipwlahr oh wiewellahr; ahpw I pahn koasoanehdi pwe kumwail en pwurehng koadoahkihada.
\v 35 Aramas koaros pahn koasoia duwen sahpwet, me wie sapwtehnla mahso, oh met e duwelahr mwetuwel en Ihden, oh duwen kahnimw ko me ohlahr, me pirapalahr, oh solahr towe, eri met, re ahpw onohnsapahldahr oh aramas akan kousoanlahr loale.
\v 36 Eri, wehi kan me luhwehdi me mi limwahmwail pahn esehki me ngehi, KAUN-O, me onehda sapahl kahnimw me ohlahr akan oh pwurehng padokedi mwaht akan me wialahr sapwtehn. Ngehi, KAUN-O, me inoukidahr me I pahn wia met; eri I pahn kapwaiada.”
\p 
\v 37 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin mahsanih, “I pahn pwurehng mweidohng mehn Israel kan en peksawas rehi. I pahn mweidohng re en ngederla, rasehng pelin sihpw ehu.
\v 38 Eri, ni ahnsowo aramas pahn kadirehla kahnimw kan me ahnsou wet ohlahr, duwehte Serusalem eh diren sihpw mahso, mehn wia meirong ni rahn sarawi lapalap akan. Irail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.”
\c 37
\s1 Wahun Tihn Aramas Madekeng
\p 
\v 1 Eri, I ahpw pehmada manaman en nin limen KAUN-O rehi, oh ngene ahpw kipeiehdi oh pwilikiniehdi nan wahu ehu me inenen diren tihn aramas.
\v 2 Ih eri kahreieseli nan wahwo, wasa me I kak kilang ie tihn aramas tohtohie me inenen madekeng.
\v 3 Ih eri mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, ke lemeleme me tihn aramas pwukat kak pwurehng mourda?”
\p Ngehi eri sapeng, patohwan, “Maing KAUN, Wasa Lapalahpie, komwihte me mwahngih.”
\p 
\v 4 E ahpw mahsanih, “Wia kokohp ong tih pwukat. Ndaiong tih madekeng pwukat re en rong mahsen en KAUN-O.
\v 5 Ndaiong irail me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanihong irail, ‘I pahn kihong kumwail engin mour pwe kumwail en esingekda oh pwurehng mourda.
\v 6 I pahn kihong kumwail selin mour oh uduk, oh kidimkinkumwailpene kihl. I pahn kihong kumwail engin mour pwe kumwail en kak pwurehng esingekda oh mourda. Kumwail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.”
\p 
\v 7 Ngehi eri kohpada duwen mahsen me I aleier. Eri, nindokon ei lokolokaia, I rongada ngihl ehu, ngilen tih kan me mwamwahnd, re tapihadahr ospene.
\v 8 Ni ei mwasamwasahn oh kilikilang, selin mour oh uduk pa pwarapwarada pohn tih ko, a mwuhr, kilirail pil sansalda. Ahpw sohte engin mour ni paliwar ako.
\p 
\v 9 Koht eri mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, kohpada ong kisiniengo. Kohpada oh ndaiong me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin koasoanedier pwe en kohdo sang ni pali pahieun sampah, oh kihong esingek rehn paliwar mehla pwukat pwe en komourirailda sapahl.”
\p 
\v 10 Ngehi eri kohpada duwen mahsen me I aleier. Engin mour eri pedolong nan paliwar pwukat, irail eri mourda oh kesihnenda. Uwen tohtohn aramas me mi wasao rasehng karis en sounpei ehu.\x - \xo 37:10 \xt Kaud. 11.11.\x*
\p 
\v 11 Koht eri mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, ke en ese me aramas en Israel kan rasehng tih pwukat. Re kin nda me re madekenglahr lel tih, solahr ar koapworopwor oh aramas lekdekla kei me sohte ar mour.
\v 12 Eri, kohpada ong aramas en Israel kan oh ndaiong irail me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, I pahn kasarapeseng ar sousou kan, oh komourirailda oh kasapahliraillahng nan wehin Israel.
\v 13 Eri, ni ahnsou me I pahn kasarapeseng sousou kan wasa nei aramas akan wonohn ie, oh komourirailda, re pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O.
\v 14 I pahn kihong irail engin silangi, komourirailda sapahl oh mweidohng irail en kin koukousoan nan uhdakarail. Irail eri pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O. I inoukidahr me I pahn wia met, oh I pahn kapwaiada. Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen.”
\s1 Suda oh Israel wiahla Wehi Teieu
\p 
\v 15 KAUN-O ahpw pil pwurehng mahsanihong ie,
\v 16 “Kowe, nein aramas, ale ehu kisin lepin dinapw oh ntingihedi powe, ‘Wehin Suda.’ Mwuhr, ke ahpw pil ale ekis lepin dinapw tohrohr oh ntingihedi powe, ‘Wehin Israel.’
\v 17 Ke ahpw kolpene kisin lepin dinapw riakiso pwe ira en duwehla kisin lepin dinapw tehkis.
\v 18 Tohn omw wehi pahn peki rehmw ke en kawehwehiong irail irair wet.
\v 19 Ke pahn padahkihong irail me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, I pahn ale kisin lepin dinapw me wehwehki Israel, oh kapatahiong kisin lepin dinapw me wehwehki Suda. Eri, sang ni kisin lepin dinapw riapali wet, I pahn wiahkihla lepin dinapwtepali oh I pahn kolada nan pehiet.
\p 
\v 20 “Kolada kisin lepin dinapw riapali me ke ntingih powe, oh kasalehiong aramas akan.
\v 21 Ke ahpw ndaiong irail me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, I pahn ale mehn Israel kan sang nan wehi kan me re kousoanla ie, oh kapokoneirailpene oh kasapahliraildohng nan uhdakarail.
\v 22 I pahn wiahkinirailla wehi teieu nan sapwarailo pohn nahna kan en Israel. Re pahn ahneki nanmwarki tehmen me pahn kaunirailda, oh re solahr pahn wia wehi riau.
\v 23 Re solahr pahn kasaminehkinirailla dikedik en eni kasaut kan de kauwehkinirailla dihp. I pahn doareirailsang nan soangen dihp koaros oh sang arail sapeik. I pahn kamwakeleirailda oh irail pahn wiahla nei aramas, oh ngehi, I pahn wiahla ar Koht.
\v 24 Emen nanmwarki me duwehte ei ladu Depit pahn wiahla ar nanmwarki. Irail koaros pahn kin ehupene pahn kaun tehmen, oh re pahn kin loalopwoat peikiong ei kosonned akan.\x - \xo 37:24 \xt Esek. 34.24.\x*
\v 25 Re pahn kin kousoan nan sahpw me I kihong ei ladu Seikop, wasa me ar pahpa kahlap ako kousoanehr ie. Irail pahn kin kousoan wasao, oh neirail seri kan oh kadaudokarail kan koaros kohkohlahte. Emen nanmwarki me duwehte ei ladu Depit pahn kin kakaun irail kohkohlahte.
\v 26 I pahn wiahda inou ehu ong irail me pahn wia poahsoan en arail mour meleilei kohkohlahte. I pahn kangedereirailla oh koasoanehdi Tehnpesei Sarawio pwe en uh kohkohlahte nan sapwarail.
\v 27 I pahn kin ket wasao rehrail oh wia ar Koht, a irail pahn kin wia nei aramas.\x - \xo 37:27 \xt 2 Kor. 6.16; Kaud. 21.3.\x*
\v 28 Ni ei pahn koasoanehdi Tehnpesei Sarawio wasao pwe I en ieiang irail kohkohlahte, iei ahnsou me wehi kan pahn esehla me ngehi, iei KAUN-O, me piladahr Israel pwe en wiahla nei aramas.”
\c 38
\s1 Kok iei Sapwellimen Koht Tehte
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O ketin mahsanihong ie,
\v 2 “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla Kok, kaun lapalap en Mesek oh Tupal nan sapwen Makok. Keriahla\x - \xo 38:2 \xt Kaud. 20.8.\x*
\v 3 oh ndaiong me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me wia eh imwintihti.
\v 4 I pahn kasohpaido, ketikihong kehs ni ewe, oh ruwahdekihla ih oh nah sounpei kan. Nah karis, iangahki nair oahs oh soundak oahs kan, me inenen ngeder, oh sounpei koaros wa nair mehn sansar oh tehtehn peiki kedlahs.
\v 5 Aramas akan sang Persia, Sudan, oh Lipia iang ih, oh koaros wisik mehn sansar oh lisoarop en mahwen.
\v 6 Sounpei koaros sang sapwen Komer oh Ped Dokarma ni paliepeng iang ih, oh pil sounpei sang wehi teikan.
\v 7 Padahkihong en onopada oh ruwese nah sounpei kan.
\v 8 Mwurin sounpar tohto I pahn koasoanediong ih en mahweniong sahpw ehu me towe kan kapwurupwurdohsang nan wehi tohto oh koukousoan ie ni ar sohte perki mahwen. E pahn mahweniong nahna kan en Israel, me tehnlahr oh solahr towe ahnsou reirei, ahpw met aramas akan koukousoan ie ni onepek mwahu.
\v 9 Ih oh nah karis oh wehi tohto me iang ih pahn mahweniong rasehng melimel oh pwaindi sahpwo duwehte pelien depwek pali.”
\p 
\v 10 Ih met me KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanihong Kok: “Ni ahnsowo eh pahn leledo, ke pahn tapihada wie lamalamki koasoandi suwed.
\v 11 Ke pahn koasoanehdi ke en mahweniong sahpw ehu me sohte sawasepe, me towe kan meleilei oh onepek mwahu ie nan kahnimw kan me sohte kehl oh poadoarepe.
\v 12 Ke pahn kulih oh adihasang en aramas akan ar dipwisou kan, aramas akan me kin koukousoan nan kahnimw kan me mahs wia mohn kahnimw kei. Re kapokonpene sang nan wehi kan, oh met re naineki pelinmen oh sapwasapw oh mihmi nanwerengen sahpw koaros en sampah.
\v 13 Mehn Sipa oh Dedan oh sounnetinet kan sang Spein pahn idek rehmw, ‘Ke kapokonepenehr noumw karis oh mahweniong pwe ke en adihasang oh kulihasang ar dipwisou kan? Ke lemeleme ke en kihsang nair silper oh kohl, pelinmen oh sahpw, oh wa dipwisou kan kohkohwei?’”
\p 
\v 14 Eri, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ketin kadariehdo pwe I en padahkihong Kok dahme e mahmahsanihong: “Eri, nindokon nei aramas Israel eh onepek mwahu, ke pahn tapihada mwekid sang
\v 15 nan omw wasa ni paliepeng, kahre lapalahn karis kehlail en sounpei sang wehi tohto, oh irail koaros pahn dak oahs.
\v 16 Ke pahn mahweniong nei aramas Israel rasehng melimel ehu me mwekimwekid pohn sahpw. Ni ahnsowo eh pahn leledo, I pahn kadaruhkala pwe ke en mahweniong nin limeio pwehn kasalehiong wehi kan ihs ngehi, en kasalehda ei sarawi sang ni dahme I kin ketikihong kumwail en wia.
\v 17 Iei kowe me I mahmahsanih duwe kawao, ni ei mahsanihong ei ladu, soukohp kan en Israel pwe re en padahkihong nei aramas akan, me ni rahn akan me pahn kohdo I pahn ketikihdo mehmen pwehn mahweniong Israel.” KAUN-O, wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Kalokolok ong Kok
\p 
\v 18 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Ni rahn me Kok pahn mahweniong Israel, I pahn engiengda kowahlap.
\v 19 I kalohkihda ni karakar en ei engieng me ni rahno e pahn mie rerrer en sahpw nan wehin Israel.
\v 20 Mwahmw oh menpihr koaros, mahn tikitik oh laud koaros, oh aramas koaros me mi nin sampah pahn rerrerki ar masak ie. Nahna kan pahn pwupwudi, paip akan pahn mweredi, oh kehl koaros pahn rengkidi.
\v 21 I pahn kamasangkihda Kok soangen apwal tohto. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen. Nah sounpei kan pahn uhpene oh peikipene nair kedlahs akan.
\v 22 I pahn kalokehki soumwahu oh keredien nta. Keteu laud oh keteu aihs takai, iangahki kisiniei oh suwepel okohk, pahn mwerediong powe oh pohn nah karis oh pohn wehi tohto me uhpalihki.
\v 23 Ih duwen met ei pahn kasalehiong wehi koaros me I me manaman oh sarawi. Irail pahn esehla me ngehi iei KAUN-O.”
\c 39
\s1 En Kok eh Lohdi
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, keriahla Kok, kaun lapalap en wehin Mesek oh Tupal, oh padahkihong me ngehi me eh imwintihti.
\v 2 I pahn kasohpeilahng ehu wasa kapw oh kahrehiei sang ih ni paliepeng lao e lellahng nin nahna kan en Israel.
\v 3 I ahpw pahn kesehsang nah kesik ketieu ni palimeingi oh nah arep ni palimauni.
\v 4 Kok oh nah karis oh ienge kan pahn pwupwudi mehla pohn nahna kan en Israel, oh I pahn mweidohng kahleparail kan en wiahla kenen menpihr oh mahn lawalo kan.
\v 5 Re pahn pwupwudi mehla nan sahpw patapato. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.
\v 6 I pahn saunda kisiniei ehu nan wehin Makok oh ni oaroahr kan wasa me aramas akan kin koukousoan ie ni meleilei, aramas koaros ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi iei KAUN-O.
\v 7 I pahn kupwurehda pwe nei aramas akan en Israel en esehla mwarei sarawi, oh sohte pwurehng mweidohng mwarei en sohla wauwi. Eri, wehi kan ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi, KAUN-O, me Koht sarawien Israel.”
\p 
\v 8 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Rahn me I mahmahsanih duwe uhdahn pahn leledo.
\v 9 Aramas akan me koukousoan nan kahnimw kan en Israel pahn kohieila rikpene dipwisoun mahwen kan me lekdeklahr pwe re en tuwihki. Re pahn saunkihda kisiniei mehn sansar kan, kesik ketieu kan, arep kan, ketieu kan, oh padda kan, oh ar tuwi pahn itarohng erein sounpar isuh.
\v 10 Re sohte pahn wesei tuwi nan mwaht akan de lupukedi tuhke kan nanwel, pwe re pahn tuwihki dipwisoun mahwen me lekdeklahr akan. Re pahn adihasang oh kulihasang en irail kan dipwisou, irail kan me kulihasangehr oh adihasangehr ar dipwisou mahs.” KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie me mahmahsen.
\s1 Seridien Kok
\p 
\v 11 KAUN-O ketin mahsanih, “Ni ahnsou me mepwukat koaros pahn pweida, I pahn ketikihong Kok wasahn eh seridi nan Israel, ni Wahun Tohnseiloak, palimesehn Sehden Mehla. Kok oh nah karis koaros pahn seridi wasao, oh wahwo pahn adanekihla ‘Wahun Karis en Kok.’
\v 12 Sounpwong isuh uwen reirei en ahnsou me mehn Israel pahn sansarepedi paliweren me melahr akan oh pwurehng kamwakelehda sahpwo.
\v 13 Koaros me koukousoan nan sahpwo pahn sewese sarepiraildi, oh re pahn alehki wahu ni rahnen ei powehdi. Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen.
\v 14 Mwurin sounpwong isuh eh pahn imwisekla, ohl ekei pahn pilipilda pwe re en kohseli nan sahpwo oh sarepedi luhwe kan me mihmihte pohn pwehl, pwe re en kak kamwakelehda sahpwo.
\v 15 Ni ar pahn kohda ni ukada oh ukedi kan en sahpwo, ahnsou koaros re pahn diar tihn aramas, re pahn kin kihong kilel ehu limwah pwe sounweir pwoahr akan en kak kohdo oh sarepedi nan Wahun Karis en Kok.
\v 16 (E pahn mie kisin kahnimw keren kis wasao me pahn adanekihla eden kariso.) Eri, sahpwo pahn pwurehng kamwakelda.”
\p 
\v 17 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, ekerodo menpihr oh mahn koaros pwe re en kohdo sang wasa koaros pwe re en kang meirong me I pahn kaunopadahng irail. Iei lapalahn kamadipw ehu pohn nahna kan en Israel, wasa re kang uduk oh nim nta.\x - \xo 39:17 \xt Kaud. 19.17-18.\x*
\v 18 Re pahn kang paliweren sounpei kan oh nim ntahn kaun akan en sampah, irail koaros pahn kamakamala rasehng sihpw wol de sihmpwul de kuht de kou mworourou.
\v 19 Ni ei pahn kemehla aramas pwukat duwehte meirong kan, menpihr oh mahn akan pahn kangala kirihs uwen me re kak oh nim nta lao re sakaukihla.
\v 20 Re pahn kangasang pohn ei tehpel oahs oh soundakepe oh sounpei kan uwen me re kak. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\s1 Onohnsapahl en Israel
\p 
\v 21 KAUN-O eri mahsanih, “I pahn mweidohng wehi kan en kilang ei lingan oh kasalehiong irail duwen ei doadoahngki ei manaman pwe en kapwaiada ei koasoandi pwung kan.
\v 22 Eri, sang met kohla mehn Israel kan pahn esehla me ngehi iei KAUN-O, arail Koht.
\v 23 Oh wehi kan pahn ese me mehn Israel kan kalipilipala pwehki dihp me re wiahiong ie. I keseirailla oh mweidala pwe ar imwintihti kan en kaloweiraildi oh kemeirailla nan mahwen.
\v 24 I ketikihong irail dahme konehng ar saminla oh ar suwed, I ahpw keseirailla.”
\p 
\v 25 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Ahpw met I pahn kupwurkalahngan ong kadaudok en Seikop kan, mehn Israel kan, oh I pahn pwurehng kapaiairailda. I pahn sinsile mwahu mwarei sarawi.
\v 26 Ni ar pahn pwurehng kousoanla nan uhdakarailo ni onepek mwahu, ni sohte emen pahn kamasak irail, re pahn kak manokehla kanamenek me re aleier pwehki ar pengiehla.
\v 27 Pwehn kasalehiong wehi tohto me I me sarawi, I pahn kapwurehdo nei aramas akan sang nan sahpw koaros me ar imwintihti kan koukousoan ie.
\v 28 Eri, nei aramas akan ahpw pahn esehla me ngehi iei KAUN-O, arail Koht. Re pahn ese met, pwehki ei kadarirailla nan seliparail oh met I kapokoneirailpene oh kapwureiraildo nan uhdakarail, sohte emen I kesehla.
\v 29 I pahn kamwerehdi ngeni pohn aramas akan en Israel oh I sohte pahn pwurehng sohpeisang irail. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\c 40
\s1 Esekiel Wisiklahng Serusalem
\p 
\v 1 Ni rahn kaeisek en parakapw, me iei karieisek limaun sounpar mwurin at kalipilipala oh kaeisek pahieun sounpar mwurin Serusalem eh lohdi. Ni rahno I pehmada manaman en KAUN-O eh ket wasao, e ahpw ketikiniehla sang wasao.
\v 2 Nan kaudiahlo Koht ketikiniehla nan wehin Israel oh ketikiniehdi pohn nahna ile ehu. I ahpw kilangada ihmw kei mwohi me likamwete kahnimw ehu.\x - \xo 40:2 \xt Kaud. 21.10.\x*
\v 3 E ahpw ketikiniehla pwe I en karanih, I ahpw kilangada ohl emen me lingaling duwehte prons. E wie kolokol mehn sosohng linen ehu oh mehn sosohng kisin tuhke oh wie kesikesihnen limwahn ewen kehlo.\x - \xo 40:3 \xt Kaud. 11.1; 21.15.\x*
\p 
\v 4 E ahpw patohwanohng ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, rong oh kanahieng mehkoaros me I pahn kasalehiong uhk, pwehki ire wet me ke wisingkidohng wasaht. Ke pahn padahkihong aramas en Israel kan mehkoaros me ke pahn kilang.”
\s1 Ewen Kelen Palimese
\p 
\v 5 Dahme I kilang iei Tehnpas Sarawio, oh mie dihd ehu me kapilpene. Ohlo eri ale nah mehn sosohng kisin tuhkeo, me piht 10 reirei, oh sohngedi dihdo. Dihdo piht 10 ile oh 10 mosul.\x - \xo 40:5 \xt 1 Nan. 6.1-38; 2 Kron. 3.1-9.\x*
\v 6 E ahpw kohla ni ewen kehlo me sallahng palimese. E doudahla pohn kehndake ko, oh sohng pohn wasahn pedolongo; e piht 10 loal.
\v 7 Palihlahsang mie ahl ehu kolongala, me perehn silasil siluh mie me mi pali koaros. Ehuehu pere ko keimw pahieu, piht 10 pali koaros, oh dihd ko me irepeseng pere ko piht 8 mosul. Palio perehn silasil ko mie ahl pwoat kohlongala me piht 10 reirei oh kohlongalahng wenihmwen pere ehu me sallahng Tehnpas Sarawio.
\v 8-9 E ahpw sohngedi pere wet oh diarada me piht 14 loal. E patehngete imwin ewen kehlo me keieu kerendohng Tehnpas Sarawio, oh ni imwi lepio dihdo piht 4 mosul.
\v 10 (Perehn silasil pwukat ni pali koaros en wasahn alulongalao soangen weteieu, oh dihd ko me irepeseng soangen mosul teieu.)
\p 
\v 11 Mwuhr, ohlo ahpw uhd sohng uwen tehlap en wasahn aluwo ni ewen kehlo, oh tehlap en wenihmwo piht 16, koaros patpene wenihmwo oh ewen kehlo piht 22.
\v 12 Mwohn ehuehu perehn silasil ko mie dihd karakarahk ehu me inses 20 ile oh inses 20 mosul. (Pere ko piht 10 keimw pahieu.)
\v 13 Ih eri pil sohng uwen dohpeseng en dihdo sang apali dihdo en ehu pere ko kolang ni apali en ehu dihd en pere ko me kotehla wasahn aluwo, oh e piht 42.
\v 14 Pere me mi keieu lepio pedoilahng nan kehl ehu. E ahpw sohngedi pereo oh diarada me piht 34 tehlap.
\v 15 Uwen reirei en ewen kehlo sang ni maslikin kehlo kolahng apali en pere keieu mi mwurio piht 84.
\v 16 Mie kisin wenihmwtok kei ni maslikin dihdo me mi ni pere koaros oh pil mie me mi ni dihd nanpwungen pere ko. Mie mwomwen tuhke pahm kei me perperda ni masloalen dihdo me sohpeilahng wasahn aluwo.
\s1 Kehl en Liki
\p 
\v 17 Ohlo eri kahreiehla ni wasahn aluwo kolahng nan kehlo. Mie pere silihsek me wiawihda patehngete dihd en maslikio, oh mwohn pere ko tatki takai,
\v 18 ih takai ko me tete nan kehlo pwon. Kehl en masliki wet karakarahk sang kehl en masloaleo.
\p 
\v 19 Mie ewen kehl ni kehl ileo me pedolongalahng nan kehl en masloaleo. Ohlo eri sohngedi uwen dohpeseng en nanpwungen ewen kehl riauo, oh e piht 168.
\s1 Ewen Kehl en Paliepeng
\p 
\v 20 Ohlo eri sohngedi ewen kehl me mi paliepeng me pedoilahng kehl en maslikio.
\v 21 Perehn silasil siluhwo me mi apali apali en wasahn aluwo, dihdo ko me irepeseng pere ko, oh perehn pedolongalao soangen wehteieu duwehte ewen kehl en palimeseo. Kapatpene uwen reirei mihmi ni piht 84 oh tehlap piht 42.
\v 22 Perehn pedolongalao, wenihmwtok ko, oh tuhke pahm me perperda ko duwehte me mi ni ewen kehl en palimeseo. Wasao mie lohn kehndake isuh mehn doudalahng ni ewen kehlo, oh perehn pedolongalao mi lepio sallahng ni kehl en likio.
\v 23 Sang ni kehl en likio ni ewen kehl en paliepeng pil mi ehu ewen kehl me kohlongalahng nan kehl en masloaleo, pil duwehte palimeseo. Ohlo sohngedi uwen dohpeseng en nanpwungen ewen kehl riau wet, oh e piht 168 dohpeseng.
\s1 Ewen Kehl en Palieir
\p 
\v 24 Mwuhr, ohlo kahreielahng palieir, oh se kilangada pil ehu ewen kehl. Ih eri sohngedi masloalen dihdo oh perehn pedolongalao, oh re pil duwehte mehteiko.
\v 25 Mie wenihmwtok ni pere ko en ewen kehl wet me pil duwehte mehteiko. Uwen reirei en ewen kehlo piht 84 oh tehlap piht 42.
\v 26 Lohn kehndake isuh me doudalahng, oh perehn pedolongalao pil mi lepio sallahng kehl en maslikio. Mie tuhke pahm kei me perperda ni masloalen dihdo me sohpeiong wasahn aluwo.
\v 27 Pil wasaht, mie ewen kehl ehu me kohlongalahng nan kehl en masloaleo. Ohlo eri sohngedi uwen dohpeseng en ewen kehl riau wet, oh e piht 168 dohpeseng.
\s1 Kehl en Masloaleo: Ewen Kehl en Palieir
\p 
\v 28 Ohlo eri kahreielahng ni ewen kehl en palieir kolahng kehl en masloaleo. Ih eri sohngedi ewen kehlo, oh e duwehte uwen sosohng en ewen kehl teiko en dihd en maslikio.
\v 29-30 Eh perehn silasil ko, eh perehn pedolongalao, oh eh dihd en loaleo duwehte uwen sosohng en ewen kehl teiko. Pil mie wenihmwtok ni pere ko ni ewen kehl wet. Uwen kapatpenehn reirei mihmi ni piht 84 oh tehlap piht 42.
\v 31 Perehn pedolongalao sallahng kehl en masliki teio, oh tuhke pahm perperda ni dihd ko ni wasahn pedolongalao. Lohn kehndake waluh me doudalahng ni ewen kehl wet.
\s1 Kehl en Masloaleo: Ewen Kehl en Palimese
\p 
\v 32 Ohlo kahreielahng ni ewen kehl en palimese kolahng nan kehl en masloaleo. Ih eri sohngedi ewen kehlo, oh uwen sosohngpe duwehte mehteiko.
\v 33 Eh perehn silasil ko, perehn pedolongalao, oh dihd en loaleo duwehte uwen sosohngpen ewen kehl teiko. Mie wenihmwtok kei me kapilpene, oh pil wenihmwtok ni perehn pedolongalao. Kapatpenehn uwen reirei mihmi ni piht 84 oh tehlap piht 42.
\v 34 Perehn pedolongalo sallahng kehl en maslikio. Tuhke pahm kei perperda ni dihd ko ni wasahn aluwo. Lohn kehndake waluh me doudalahng ni ewen kehl wet.
\s1 Kehl en Masloale: Ewen Kehl en Paliepeng
\p 
\v 35 Ohlo eri kahreielahng ni ewen kehl en paliepeng. Ih eri sohngedi, oh e duwehte uwen sosohngpen mehteiko.
\v 36 E pil duwehte mehteiko, me mie perehn silasil, kapwat ni dihdo ko, perehn pedolongala, oh wenihmwtok me kapilpene. Kapatpenehn uwen reirei piht 84 oh tehlap piht 42.
\v 37 Perehn pedolongalao sallahng kehl en maslikio. Tuhke pahm pil perperda ni dihd ko ni wasahn aluwo. Lohn kehndake waluh me doudalahng ni ewen kehl wet.
\s1 Ihmw kan Limwahn Ewen Kehl en Paliepeng
\p 
\v 38 Nan kehl en maslikio mie pere laud ehu me patehngete ewen kehl en masloaleo ni paliepeng. E pedolongalahng nan perehn pedolongo me sallahng kehl en maslikio, oh ih wasao me re kin widen ie mahn en meirong kan me kin pwonte meirongala.
\v 39 Nan perehn pedolong wet mie tehpel pahieu mi loale, riau mi apali, a riau apali. Ih pohn tehpel pwukat me re kin kemehla mahn en meirong kan, mahn en meirong isihs de meirong en dihp de meirong en tomw.
\v 40 Likin pereo pil mie tehpel pahieu me duwehte me mi loale ko, riau mi apali wasahn pedolongalahn ni ewen kehl en paliepeng, a riau apali.
\v 41 Koaros patpene tehpel waluh me mahn en meirong kan kin kamala powe: pahieu mi loaleo oh pahieu mi nan kehl en maslikio.
\v 42 Tehpel pahieu me mi nan pere laudo, me kin doadoahkohng kaunopadahn meirong kan me pahn pwonte isihsla; tehpel pwukat wiawihkihda takai perper. Tehpel pwukat inses 20 ile, oh powe inses 30 keimw pahieu. Dipwisoun kemehla mahn en meirong kan kin nekinek pohn tehpel pwukat.
\v 43 Ni keilen tehpel ko mie keile masliki me inses 3 tehlap kapilpene. Uduk koaros mehn meirong kin kohdiong pohn tehpel pwukat.
\p 
\v 44 Ohlo eri kahreielahng nan kelen masloaleo. Mie pere riau nan kelen masloaleo me wenihmw ko ritidahngete kelen masloaleo, ehu sallahng palieir limwahn ewen kehl en paliepeng oh ehu sallahng paliepeng limwahn ewen kehl en palieir.
\v 45 Ohlo patohwanohng ie me pere me sallahng palieir ong samworo kan me kin papah nan Tehnpas Sarawio,
\v 46 oh pere me sallahng paliepeng ong samworo kan me kin papah ni pei sarawio. Samworo ko koaros kadaudok en Sadok; irail iei kisehn kadaudok en Lipai me kin mweimweiong en pedolong mwohn silangin KAUN-O pwe re en papah.
\s1 Kehl en Masloale oh Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 47 Ohlo eri sohngedi kehl en masloaleo, oh e piht 168 keimw pahieu. Tehnpas Sarawio mi palikapi, oh mwohn Tehnpaso mie pei sarawi ehu.
\v 48 Ih eri kahreielahng wasahn pedolong en Tehnpas Sarawio. Ih eri sohngedi wasahn pedolongo: e piht 9 loal oh piht 24 tehlap, iangahki dihd kan piht 5 mosul pali koaros.
\v 49 Kehndakehn doudalahng ni wasahn pedolong wet, me piht 34 tehlap oh 20 loal. Mie uhr riapwoat, ehu mi apali wasahn pedolongo, a ehu apali.
\c 41
\p 
\v 1 Mwuhr, ohlo kahreielahng nan perehn nanwerengeo, Wasa Sarawio. Ih eri sohngedi wasahn aluhlongalao: e piht 10 loal
\v 2 oh 18 tehlap, iangahki dihd ko me piht 8 mosul pali koaros. Ih eri sohngedi nan pereo: e piht 68 reirei oh 34 tehlap.
\p 
\v 3 Ih eri pedolongala nan pere me keieu mi loaleo. E sohngedi wasahn aluwo kohlongala loale: e piht 3 loal oh 10 tehlap, iangahki dihd ko pali koaros me piht 12 mosul.
\v 4 Ih eri sohngedi pereo, oh e piht 34 keimw pahieu. Pere wet mihte palihlahsang perehn nanwerengeo. Ih eri patohwanohng ie, “Iei ih Wasa Sarawiheo met.”
\s1 Pere ko Wiawihda Patehngete Dihd en Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 5 Ohlo eri sohngedi uwen mosul en dihd en masloalen Tehnpas Sarawio, oh e piht 10 mosul. Patehngete dihd wet, kapilpene Tehnpas Sarawio, mie kisin pere kei me piht 7 tehlap.
\v 6 Pere pwukat poasoake siluh, oh kisin pere silihsek nan ehu poasoake. Likin dihd en Tehnpas Sarawio ehuehu taht menipinip sang taht en pah, pwe pere ko en kak soandi pohn dihdo ni eh sohte anahne katengtengdi.
\v 7 Eri, dihd kan en Tehnpas Sarawio, ni aramas eh pahn kilenglong sang likio, e mwomwen soangen mosul teieu sang pah lel powe. Patehngete ni dihd en maslikin Tehnpas Sarawio, likin pere ko, kehndake tehlap riau wiawihda ie, pwe en kak mengeiong aramas en doudalahng peren nanwerengeo oh pil kohdalahng keieu powe.
\v 8-11 Maslikin dihd en pere ko piht 8 mosul; mie ehu wenihmw me pedolongalahng nan pere ko ni paliepeng en Tehnpas Sarawio, oh ehu pedolongalahng nan pere ko ni palieir. I ahpw kilangada me mie palangk ehu me piht 8 tehlap kapilpene Tehnpas Sarawio; e piht 10 iledahsang pwehl oh pahrekiong poahsoan en pere ko me patehngete dihd en Tehnpas Sarawio. Nanpwungen palangko oh ihmw kan me samworo kan kin doadoahngki mie ehu wasa wehwe me piht 34 tehlap, me mihte ni pengepengen Tehnpas Sarawio.
\s1 Ihmw me mi ni Palikapi
\p 
\v 12 Ni imwi keieu lepio wasa wehwe wet ni palikapi en Tehnpas Sarawio mie ihmw ehu me piht 150 reirei oh 116 tehlap; dihd kan piht 9 mosul kapilpene.
\s1 Kapatpenehn Sosohngpen Ihmw kan en Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 13 Ohlo eri sohngedi likin Tehnpas Sarawio, oh e piht 168 reirei. Oh sang nan tihnsewen Tehnpas Sarawio, kolahng wasa wehweo ni imwi lepio ihmwo kolahng palikapi, uwen reirei pil piht 168.
\v 14 Uwen dohpeseng en mwohn Tehnpas Sarawio, iangahki wasa wehweo ni pali koaros, pil piht 168 reirei.
\v 15 E sohngedi uwen reirei en ihmwo kolahng ni palikapi, iangahki palangk kan pali koaros, oh e pil piht 168 reirei.
\s1 Oaritik en Tehnpas Sarawio
\p Wasahn pedolong nan Tehnpas Sarawio, nan Wasa Sarawio, oh nan Wasa Sarawiheo
\v 16 koaros didki tuhke sang nan tato lel ni wenihmwtok kan. Wenihmwtok pwukat kak perehrehla.
\v 17 Masloalen dihd kan en Tehnpas Sarawio, pohnangin wenihmw kan, mahlen kei me mie me perperda,
\v 18 mahlen en tuhke pahm oh kerup kei. Tuhke pahm kan perperda oh mwuri kerup kan, emente mi mwurin emen, kapilpene nan pereo pwon. Emenemen kerup ko mese me riau:
\v 19 ehu mesen aramas me sohpeiong tuhke pahm ko apali, a ehu mesen laion me sohpeiong ni ehu tuhke pahm apali. E wiewia soahng wet lao kapilpene dihdo,
\v 20 sangete nan tahto kodahng pohnangin wenihmw ko.
\v 21 Uhr en wenihmwen Wasa Sarawio keimw pahieu.
\s1 Pei Sarawi Dinapw
\p Mwohn wasahn pedolong en Wasa Sarawiheo mie mehkot me mwomwen
\v 22 pei sarawi dinapw. E piht 5 ile oh piht 4 tehlap. Nehn pei sarawio, poahsoane, oh pengepenge kan wiawihkihda tuhke. Ohlo ahpw patohwanohng ie, “Ih tehpel wet me kin uh mwohn silangin KAUN-O.”
\s1 Wenihmw kan
\p 
\v 23 Mie ehu wenihmw ni imwi lepio ni wasahn alu kolahng Wasa Sarawio oh pil ehu mi ni imwi lepio ni wasahn alu kolahng Wasa Sarawiheo.
\v 24 Wenihmw riau pwukat wad riau me kin ritpeseng nanwerenge.
\v 25 Mie tuhke pahm oh kerup kei me perperda ni wenihmw kan en Wasa Sarawio, duwehte me mi ni dihd ko. Oh mie dinapw mehn perehla maslikin wenihmwo me kohlong wasahn pedolongo.
\v 26 Ni pengepengen pere wet wenihmwtok kei mie, oh dihd kan kapwatki tuhke pahm.
\c 42
\s1 Ihmw Riau Limwahn Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 1 Ohlo eri kahreielahng nan kelen likio oh kolahng ni ihmw ehu me mi ni paliepeng en Tehnpas Sarawio, me sohte dohsang ihmw me mi ni palikapi ni imwin Tehnpas Sarawio.
\v 2 Ihmw wet piht 168 reirei oh 84 tehlap.
\v 3 Apali sallahng wasa wehweo piht 34 tehlap me mi ni pengepengen Tehnpas Sarawio, oh apali sallahng taht takai en kelen maslikio. E kokouda pohn poahsoan poasoake siluh, poasoakehko mwomwen ireklongala, mehn powe keilongala sang mehn pah.
\v 4 Ni paliepeng en ihmw wet mie wasahn alu me piht 16 tehlap oh piht 168 reirei, iangahki wasahn pedolong mi pali wet.
\v 5 Pere kan me mi pohn poahsoan en powe en ihmw wet me wetikitik sang mehn nanwerenge oh mehn keieu pah pwehki poahsoano eh keilongala.
\v 6 Pere kan me mi pohn poahsoan siluh kan koaros mie palahngk ie oh sohte uhr me utungada duwehte ihmw teikan me mi nan kelen likio.
\v 7-8 Keieu pah maslikin dihd en ihmwo me inenen mosulki piht 84, elep ihmwo sohte wenihmw; oh elep piht 84 pere kei mie. Pil ni poahsoan en keieu powe mie pere kei me irekla idawehnla reirei en ihmwo.
\v 9-10 Pahnangin pere pwukat ni imwilahn palimesehn ihmwo, wasa me dihd en kelen likio tepida ie, mie wenihmw ehu me pedoilahng nan kelen likio.
\p Ni palieir en Tehnpas Sarawio mie pil ehu ihmw me duwehte me sohte dohsang ihmw teio me mi ni imwin palikapi en Tehnpas Sarawio.
\v 11 Mwohn pere ko mie wasahn alu me duwehte me mi ni paliepeng. Sosohngpe pil duwehte, soangen mwohmwohte, oh wasahn pedolongo pil duwehte.
\v 12 Mie wenihmw ehu me mihte pahnangin pere ko ni palieir en ihmwo, ni imwi palimese wasa me dihdo tepida ie.
\p 
\v 13 Ohlo eri patohwanohng ie, “Ihmw riau pwukat koaros me sarawi. Samworo kan me kin pedolong wasa me KAUN-O kin ketiket ie kin tungoale meirong me keieu sarawi kan wasao. Pwehki pere ko ar sarawi, samworo ko kin kihdiong meirong me keieu sarawi ko wasao: meirong en wahnsahpw oh meirong en dihp de meirong en tomw.
\v 14 Ni ahnsou me samworo kan kin pato nan Tehnpas Sarawio oh men patohla nan kelen likio, re pahn pwuhrsang nan likou sarawi kan me re kin mi loale ni ahnsou me re kin papah KAUN-O. Re pahn pwuhriong nan ehu likou torohr mwohn ar pahn patohieila wasa me aramas akan kin pokonpene ie.”
\s1 Sosohngpen nan Kelen Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 15 Ni ohlo eh kaimwisekla eh sosohng nan Tehnpas Sarawio, e ahpw kahreielahng ni ewen kelen palimese oh sohng likin wasao.
\v 16 E ale kisin tuhkehn sosohngo oh sohngedi palimese, oh e piht 840.
\v 17-19 Ih eri pil sohngedi paliepeng, palieir, oh palikapi; pali koaros soangen reirei teieu, piht 840,
\v 20 eri, dihdo me kapilpene keimw pahieu piht 840 pali koaros. Dihdo me kin katohrepeseng mehkan me sarawi oh sohte sarawi.
\c 43
\s1 KAUN-O ketin Sapahldohng nan Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 1 Ohlo eri kahreielahng ni ewen kehl me sallahng palimese,
\v 2 oh wasao I ahpw kilangada marain lingaling en Koht en Israel eh uhdahsang ni palimese. Kapitien Koht peipeido rasehng ngirisek en madau, oh sampah marainkihda marain lingalingo.\x - \xo 43:2 \xt Esek. 10.3-4, 18-19; 11.22-23; Kaud. 1.15.\x*
\v 3 Kaudiahl wet duwehte me I kilangehr ni ahnsou me Koht ketido pwehn kamwomwala Serusalem, oh me I pil kilangehr limwahn Pillap Separ. Ngehi eri poarikihdi meseiet nanpwel.
\v 4 Marain lingalingo ahpw daulihala nan ewen kelen palimese oh ketilong nan Tehnpas Sarawio.
\p 
\v 5 Ngenen KAUN-O ahpw pwekiehda oh waielahng nan kelen masloaleo, wasa me I kilangada Tehnpas Sarawio eh direkihla lingan en KAUN-O.
\v 6 Ohlo eri kesihnenda limwahi wasao, I ahpw rongada KAUN-O eh mahsendohng ie sang nan Tehnpas Sarawio:
\v 7 “Kowe, nein aramas, iet mwoalei en. I pahn ketiket wasaht rehn aramas en Israel kan oh kakaun irail kohkohlahte. Sohte mehn Israel de ar nanmwarki kan pahn pwurehng kasohwauwihala mwarei sarawi ni ar pahn pwongih koht teikan de keilahng limwahn kahlep en ar nanmwarki kan me sipallahr.
\v 8 Nanmwarki kan me kauwada wenihmw oh mesendid kan en tehnpasarailo patehngete wenihmw oh mesendid en Tehnpesei Sarawio, me kahrehda dihd ehu me ireikitpeseng. Re kasohwauwihkihla mwarei sarawi ar wiewia saut kan, oh nan ei engieng I ahpw kamwomwirailla.
\v 9 Eri, met re uhdahn pahn tokedihsang ar pwongpwongih koht teikan oh kamwakidasang kahlep en ar nanmwarki me pwoulahr akan. Ma re pahn wia met, I pahn ieiang irail kohkohlahte.”
\p 
\v 10 KAUN-O eri pil usehla mahsanih, “Kowe, nein aramas, ndaiong mehn Israel kan duwen Tehnpas Sarawio, oh re en padahngki duwen koasoanepe. Kanamenekihirailla pwehki arail wiewia suwed kan.
\v 11 Eri, ma re namenengkihda ar wiewia kan, kawehwehiong irail koasoandien Tehnpas Sarawio: koasoandien wiepe, wenihmwen pedolong oh pedoi kan, mwomwe, koasoandien mehkoaros, oh kosonnedpe kan. Ntingihedi mepwukat koaros ong irail pwe re en kilang duwen koasoandien mehkoaros oh kapwaiada kosonned koaros.
\v 12 Iet kosonned en Tehnpas Sarawio: Wasa koaros me kapilpene Tehnpas Sarawio pohn kumwen nahna sarawio me wahu oh sarawi.”
\s1 Pei Sarawio
\p 
\v 13 Iet sosohngpen pei sarawio, me doadoahngki mehn sosohongohte me sohng Tehnpas Sarawio. Mie kisin warawar kis me inses 20 loal oh inses 20 tehlap kapilpene keilen poahsoan en pei sarawio, oh ni keilen warawaro mie keile masliki me ilehki inses 10.\x - \xo 43:13 \xt Eks. 27.1-2; 2 Kron. 4.1.\x*
\v 14 Wasa keieu karakarahk en pei sarawio, sang pohn poahsoano, piht 4 ile. Pil pohnangin mehteio ni mwomwen kehndake inses 20 keilongala sang ni keile, kapilpene, oh piht 7 ile. Pil pohnangin mwo pil ekis keilongala inses 20 keilongala, kapilpene.
\v 15 Keieu powe, wasa me meirong kan kin isihsla ie, piht 7 ile. Ni keimw pahieuo mie kohd me uhda sikdahsang wasa teikan koaros.
\v 16 Pohn pei sarawio keimw pahieu, piht 20 pali koaros.
\v 17 Ni kehndakehn nanwerengeo pil keimw pahieu, piht 24 pali koaros, mie keile masliki me ilehkihda inses 10. (Kisin warawaro inses 20 tehlap.) Kehndakehn douda pohn pei sarawio mi ni palimese.
\s1 Kasarawihalahn Pei Sarawio
\p 
\v 18 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, ahpw mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, rong dahme I pahn mahsanihong uhk. Ni ahnsou me pei sarawio pahn kokouda, kowe me pahn kasarawihala ni omw pahn isikala meirong powe oh usupihki powe ntahn mahn en meirong ko. \x - \xo 43:18 \xt Eks. 29.35-37; 1 Mak. 4.52-56.\x*
\v 19 Samworo ko me kisehn kadaudok en Lipai me kodoudoudohsang Sadok iei irail kelehpw me pahn kohdo mwohi pwe re en papah ie. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me koasoanehdi met. Ke pahn kihong irail emen kouwol pwulopwul pwe re en wiahkihla mehn meirong en dihp.
\v 20 Ke pahn ale ekei ntah oh iriski ni koden pei sarawio ni keimw pahieuo, ni keilen keimw pahieu en kehndakehn nanwerenge, oh ni keile wasa koaros. Ih duwen met omw pahn kamwakelehda pei sarawio oh kasarawihala.
\v 21 Ke ahpw pahn ale kouwol me wialahr meirong en dihp oh isikala wasa me koasoandiong mwekid wet en wiawi ie likin Tehnpas Sarawi.
\v 22 Mandahn rahno ke pahn ale emen kuht wol me sohte samin oh wiahkihla mehn meirong en dihp. Kamwakelehkihda pei sarawio ntah duwehte me ke wiahiongehr kouwolo.
\v 23 Ni omw pahn kaimwisekala mepwukat, ale emen kouwol pwulopwul oh sihpw wol pwulopwul, ira koaros sohte pahn samin,
\v 24 oh wadohng ie. Samworo ko pahn iriski soahl oh isikala nin duwen meirongohng ie.
\v 25 Rahn koaros erein rahn isuh ke pahn meirongkihla emen kuht, emen kouwol, oh emen sihpw wol nin duwen meirong en dihp. Irail koaros sohte pahn samin.
\v 26 Erein rahn isuh samworo ko pahn kasarawihala pei sarawio oh kaunopadahng doadoahk.
\v 27 Mwurin wihko eh pahn imwisekla, samworo ko pahn tapihada wia meirong isihs oh meirong en kaminimin ong aramas akan pohn pei sarawio. I ahpw pahn kupwurperenkihla kumwail koaros. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\c 44
\s1 Duwen Doadoahngki Ewen Kelen Palimese
\p 
\v 1 Ohlo eri kahreielahng maslikin ewen kelen palimese ni pengepengen Tehnpas Sarawio. Ewen kehlo rit,
\v 2 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie, “Ewen kehl wet sohte pahn ritida. Sohte mweimweiong aramas en doadoahngki, pwehki ngehi, KAUN-O, Koht en Israel, ketilongehr loale. E pahn ritirit ahnsou koaros.
\v 3 Ahpw soupeidi me kakaun wehi, kak patohla mwo pwehn tungoale pilawa sarawi mwohn silangi. E pahn patohlong oh patohiei ni ewen kehl kolahng nan perehn pedoio ni imwi lepeio.”
\s1 Kosonned en Kapedolong nan Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 4 Ohlo eri kahreielahng ni ewen kelen paliepeng mwohn Tehnpas Sarawio. Ni ei kilikilengla, I ahpw kilangada me Tehnpas en KAUN-O direkihla sapwellime marain lingalingo. Ngehi eri poarikihdi meseiet nanpwel,
\v 5 oh KAUN-O ahpw mahsanihong ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, rong kanahieng dahme ke kilang oh rong. I pahn mahsanihong uhk kosonned oh koasoandi kan ong Tehnpas Sarawio. Kilelehdi mwahu ihs aramas me mweimweiong en pedolong oh pedoi sang nan Tehnpas Sarawio, oh ihs me sohte mweimweiong.
\p 
\v 6 “Ndaiong aramas en Israel kahngohdi pwuko me ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, solahr pahn kanengamahiong soahng saut kan me re wiewia.
\v 7 Re kasaminehkilahr Tehnpesei Sarawio ar kin mweidohng mehn liki me sohte sirkumwsais kan, aramas akan me sohte kin peikiong ie, en pedolong nan Tehnpas Sarawio ni ahnsou me wih oh ntahn meirong kan kin meirongala ong ie. Eri, nei aramas akan kauwehkilahr ei inowo soahng saut kan me re wiadahr.
\v 8 Re sohte wia ar doadoahk sarawi kan nan Tehnpesei Sarawio, ahpw re kihong mehn liki kan en wia.
\p 
\v 9 “Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, kalohkidahr me sohte mehn liki men me sohte sirkumsais, sohte emen me sapeikiong ie, pil sohte mehn liki men me koukousoan rehn mehn Israel kan pahn pedolong nan Tehnpesei Sarawio.”
\s1 Mehn Lipai kan Sohte pahn Wia Doadoahk en Samworo
\p 
\v 10 KAUN-O eri mahsanihong ie, “I pahn kaloke mehn Lipai kan me iang luhwen mehn Israel kan keseiehla oh pwongihala dikedik en eni kan.
\v 11 Re kak papah ie nan Tehnpas Sarawio ni ar pahn apwalih ewen kehl kan oh wia doadoahk en Tehnpas Sarawio. Re kak kemehla mahn akan me aramas akan kin patohwanda pwehn wia meirong isihs oh meirong teikan, oh re pahn doadoahk pwe re en papah aramas akan.
\v 12 Ahpw pwehki ar wiewia kaudok en dikedik en eni kan ong aramas en Israel kan oh kahrehiong aramas akan nan dihp, ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, kahukihla ni kehlail me re uhdahn pahn ale lokolok.
\v 13 Re sohte pahn papah ie nin duwen samworo kei de keiong limwahn mehkot me sarawi ong ie de pedolong Wasa Sarawiheo. Met iei kalokolok en soahng saut kan me re wiadahr.
\v 14 I pahn kilelehiong irail en wia doadoahk tikitik kan me pahn wiawi nan Tehnpas Sarawio.”
\s1 Samworo kan
\p 
\v 15 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Samworo pwuko me kisehn kadaudok en Lipai me kodoudoudohsang Sadok, me usehlahte papah ie ni loalopwoat nan Tehnpas Sarawio ni ahnsou me luhwen mehn Israel ko sohpeisang ie. Ihme kahrehda irail me pahn papah ie oh patohdo mwohn silangi pwe re en patohwandahng ie wih oh ntahn meirong kan.
\v 16 Irail kelehpw me pahn pedolong nan Tehnpesei Sarawio, papah pohn ei pei sarawio, oh wia kaudok nan Tehnpas Sarawio.
\v 17 Ni ar pahn pedolong nan ewen kehl me kolahng nan kelen masloalen Tehnpas Sarawio, re pahn pwuhriong nan likou linen. Re sohte pahn likawih likou me wiawihkihda wunen sihpw ni ahnsoun ar doadoahk masloalen kehlo de nan Tehnpas Sarawio.\x - \xo 44:17 \xt Eks. 28.39-43; Lip. 16.4.\x*
\v 18 Pwe pwudowarail en dehr kerada, re pahn mi nan lisoarop linen oh rausis linen, ahpw sohte kateng.
\v 19 Mwohn ar pahn kohla nan kelen maslikio, wasa me aramas kin mie, re pahn kihsang mahs ar likou me re likawih ahnsoun ar daodoahk nan Tehnpas Sarawio oh pwilikihdi nan pere sarawi ko. Re pahn pwuhriong nan ehu likou pwe ar likou sarawi kan dehr kauwehla aramas akan.\f s \fr 44:19 \fk KAUWEHLA ARAMAS AKAN: \ft Mehn mahs ako kin kamehlele me aramas me kaidehn samworo pahn ohla ma re sairada mehkot me sarawi.\f*\x - \xo 44:19 \xt Lip. 16.23.\x*
\p 
\v 20 “Samworo kan sohte pahn koakoahsang pitenmoangarail de mweidohng en reireila. Re pahn mweidohng en reirei mwahute.\x - \xo 44:20 \xt Lip. 21.5.\x*
\v 21 Samworo kan sohte pahn nim wain mwohn ar pahn pedolong nan kelen masloaleo.\x - \xo 44:21 \xt Lip. 10.9.\x*
\v 22 Sohte samworo men pahn pwoudikihda lih me mweisang eh pwoud; e pahn pwoudikihte serepein en Israel me meipwon de liohdi en emen samworo.\x - \xo 44:22 \xt Lip. 21.7,13-14.\x*
\p 
\v 23 “Samworo kan pahn kin padahkihong nei aramas akan wekpeseng en dahme sarawi oh sohte sarawi, oh pil wekpeseng en dahme mwakelekel oh sohte mwakelekel ong kaudok.\x - \xo 44:23 \xt Lip. 10.10.\x*
\v 24 Ni ahnsou me akamai ehu pahn kin pwarada, samworo kan me pahn kapwungala repen pwungo nin duwen ei kosonned kan. Re pahn kin kapwaiada rahn sarawi kan nin duwen ei kosonned oh koasoandi kan, oh re pahn kin kasarawihala rahnen Sapad.
\p 
\v 25 “Samworo men pahn saminla ong kaudok ma eh pahn sairada aramas mehla men, me kaidehk eh nohno de pahpa, de nah seri de rie pwutak de serepein me sohte pwopwoud.\x - \xo 44:25 \xt Lip. 21.1-4.\x*
\v 26 Mwurin eh pahn pwurehng kamwakelda, e pahn awih mwurin rahn isuh,
\v 27 e ahpw pahn kohla masloalen kelen Tehnpas Sarawio wiahda ehu meirong pwehn kamwakelda, pwe en kak pwurehng papah nan Tehnpas Sarawio. Ngehi, KAUN-O, me mahmahsen.
\p 
\v 28 “Samworo kan wia samworo kei nin duwen pwais me I ketikihong Israel me pahn kadakadaur kohdo sang ehu dih lel ehu dih. Re sohte pahn sapweniki sahpw ehu nan Israel; ngehite me wia anahneparail.\x - \xo 44:28 \xt Nemp. 18.20.\x*
\v 29 Meirong en wahnsahpw, meirong en dihp, oh meirong en tomw me re pahn tungoale, oh re pahn ale mehkoaros nan Israel me katohrohrlahr ong ie.\x - \xo 44:29 \xt Nemp. 18.8-19.\x*
\v 30 Samworo kan me pahn ale wahnsahpw me keieu mwahu ni tepin dondoal en wahnsapw oh mehkoaros me pahn meirong ong ie. Ahnsou koaros me aramas pahn umwun pilawa, re pahn kihong samworo kan keieun lopwon nin duwen kisakis ehu, oh ei kupwuramwahu ahpw pahn kohdi pohn imwarail kan.
\v 31 Samworo kan sohte pahn tungoale soangen menpihr de mahn emen me mehkihla soumwahu de emen mahn kemehla.”\x - \xo 44:31 \xt Lip. 22.8.\x*
\c 45
\s1 Sapwellimen Koht Pwais sang ni Sahpwo
\p 
\v 1 Ni ahnsou me sahpwo pahn nehnepeseng ong ehuehu kadaudok, ekis wasa pahn kasarawihla ong KAUN-O. E pahn mwail 10 reirei oh 8 tehlap. Wasao pwon pahn sarawi.
\v 2 Wasakiset pahn mie wasa kis me pahn keimw pahieu ong Tehnpas Sarawio. Piht 840 pali koaros, oh pahn mie wasa kis me tehlapki piht 84 pahn kapilpene.
\v 3 Apalien wasakiset, wasa kis me mwail 10 reirei oh 4 tehlap, pahn sosohngdi; ih wasao me Tehnpas Sarawio pahn kokouda ie, iei wasa me keieu sarawi.
\v 4 Wasakiset pahn wia wasa keieu sarawi nan sahpwo, me pahn katohrohrla ong samworo kan me kin papah KAUN-O nan Tehnpese Sarawio. Imwarail kan pahn kokouda loale iangahki wasa me Tehnpas Sarawio pahn mie.
\v 5 Apali wasao pahn katohrohrla pwehn wia sapwen mehn Lipai kan, me kin doadoahk nan Tehnpas Sarawio. E pahn mie kisin kahnimw kei wasao pwe re en kousoan ie.
\p 
\v 6 Palihlahsang wasa sarawi wet, pil pahn mie ehu wasa, mwail 10 reirei oh 2 tehlap, e pahn katohrohrla pwehn wia kahnimw ehu, wasa me mehn Israel teikan kak kousoan ie.
\s1 Sapwen Soupeidi
\p 
\v 7 Ehu pelien sahpw pil pahn katohrohrla ong soupeidi me kakaun wehio. Sang ni irepen palikapi wasa me sarawio kolahng palikapi ong Sehd Mediderenien; oh sang ni irepen palimese kolahng ni irepen palimesehn sahpwo, pwe en reirei duwehte reirei en wasa kan me kohieng kadaudok en Israel.
\v 8 Wasakiset me soupeidi me kakaun wehio pahn sapweniki nan Israel, pwe en dehr kahpwalih aramas akan, ahpw e pahn mweidohng luhwen sahpwo ong kadaudok kan en Israel.
\s1 Kosonned kan ong Soupeidi
\p 
\v 9 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, eri mahsanih, “Kumwail kaunen Israel kan, kumwail dipadahr ahnsou reirei! Kumwail katokihedi amwail kamaramas oh kahpwalih irail. Kumwail wia dahme pwung oh pahrek. Kumwail solahr pahn koakoahsang nei aramas akan nan sapwarail. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsanihong kumwail met.
\p 
\v 10 “Aramas koaros pahn doadoahngki mehn tenek oh sosohng pwung: \x - \xo 45:10 \xt Lip. 19.36.\x*
\p 
\v 11 “\it Ihpah\it* ong mehn teneki mehkot madekeng pahn duwehte \bk pahd\bk* mehn teneki mehkot me pihl. Mehn sosohng me adaneki omer\f t \fr 45:11 \fk OMER: \ft Mehn sosohng en mehkot madekeng de pihl, me ele ehd limau de kalon 44; eri, ihpah de pahd pahn ele elep en ehd de kalon 4.\f* me wia wiepen mehn sosohng koaros. Mehn kadiarakada sosohng iei me pahn sansal pah:
\pi1 \it Omer\it* 1 = \it Ihpah\it* 10 = \it pahd\it* 10
\p 
\v 12 “Amwail mehn tenek pahn duwe met:
\pi1 \it Kerahs\it* 20 = \it sekel\it* 1 \f u \fr 45:12 \fk SEKEL: \ft Ni mwehin Esekiel mehn sosohng wet mweinele 0.4 onses de onsese 11.4.\f*
\q1 \it Sekel\it* 60 = \it mina\it* 1
\p 
\v 13-15 “Ih duwen met amwail pahn wia amwail mehn meirong kan:
\pi1 Wihd: 1/60 en amwail wahnsahpw
\q1 Parli: 1/60 en amwail wahnsahpw
\q1 Lehn olip: 1/100 en amwail tuhke olip kan
\b
\m (Sosohngki \it pahd:\it* \it pahd\it* 10 = \it omer\it* 1 = \it kor\it* 1.)
\q1 Sihpw: emen sihpw sang sihpw 200 nan pelien sahpw en Israel
\p “Kumwail pahn wahdo meirong en wahnsahpw, mahn me pahn pwonte isihsla, oh mahn en wia meirong en kaminimin, pwe dipamwail en lapwada. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me koasoanehdi met.
\p 
\v 16 “Koaros tohn sahpwo pahn walahng meirong pwukat rehn soupeidi en Israel.
\v 17 Iei en soupeidio pwukoa en kihda mahn akan me pahn pwonte isihsla, meirong en wahnsahpw, oh meirong en wain wiliandi wehin Israel pwon ni ahnsoun Sarawien Maram Pwul kan, rahnen Sapad kan, oh soangen sarawi teikan. Ih me pahn kihda mehn meirong en dihp, meirong en wahnsahpw, meirong me pahn pwonte isihsla, oh meirong en kaminimin, pwehn lapwahda dipen mehn Israel.”
\s1 Sarawi kan
\r (Eksodus 12.1-20; Lipai 23.33-43)
\p 
\v 18 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Ni keieun rahnen sounpwong keieu kumwail pahn meirongkihla emen kouwol me sohte samin oh kamwakelehda Tehnpas Sarawio.
\v 19 Samworo ko pahn patohwanla ekei ntahn meirong en dihp wet oh kihdiong ni mesendid en Tehnpas Sarawio, ni keimw pahieu en pei sarawio, oh ni uhr kan en ewen kehl kan me kolahng masloalen kehlo.
\v 20 Ni rahn keisuhn sounpwong kumwail pahn wia soahngohte wiliandi mehmen me wiahda dihp ni eh sohte nsenki de sohte ese. Ih duwen met amwail pahn kadakadaur sarawien Tehnpas Sarawio.
\p 
\v 21 “Ni rahn kaeisek pahieun sounpwong keieu kumwail pahn tapihada kasarawih Sarawien Pahsohpa. Erein rahn isuh aramas akan pahn tungoale pilawa me sohte doal ihs. \x - \xo 45:21 \xt Eks. 12.1- 20; Nemp. 28.16-25.\x*
\v 22 Ni rahn keieu en sarawio soupeidi me kakaun wehio pahn patohwanda emen kouwol mehn wia meirong en dipe kan oh dipen aramas koaros.
\v 23 Ni ehuehu rahn isuh en sarawio e pahn meirongkihong KAUN-O kouwol isimen oh sihpw wol isimen me sohte samin oh pahn pwonte isihsla. E pahn pil meirongkihla emen kuht wol ni ehuehu rahn nin duwen meirong en dihp.
\v 24 Ong emenemen kouwol oh emenemen sihpw wol me meirongalahr, kumwail pahn iangahki elep en ehd en wahnsahpw oh pahkis siluh en kalon ehu en lehn olip.
\p 
\v 25 “Ong ni Sarawien Impwal kan, me kin tepida ni kaeisek limaun rahnen sounpwong keisuh, soupeidio pahn patohwanda ong ehuehu rahn isuho soangen mehn meirongohte ong meirong en dihp, soangen meirongohte me pahn pwonte isihsla, oh uwen wahnsahpwohte oh uwen lehn olipo.” \x - \xo 45:25 \xt Lip. 23.33-36; Nemp. 29.12-38.\x*
\c 46
\s1 Soupeidi oh Sarawi kan
\p 
\v 1 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Ewen kelen pedolong nan kelen masloaleo pahn ritidi erein rahnen doadoahk weneu, ahpw e pahn ritida ni rahnen Sapad oh ni Sarawien Maram Pwul.
\v 2 Soupeidi me kakaun wehio pahn patohsang ni kelen maslikio patolahng nan perehn pedolongo ni ewen kehlo oh kesihnenda limwahn uhr kan en ewen kehlo nindokon samworo kan ar isihsik eh meirong me kin pwonte isihsla oh patohwanda eh meirong en kaminimin. E pahn wia eh kaudok wasao oh pwureila. Ewen kehlo sohte pahn ritidi lao lel nin soutik.
\v 3 Ni ehuehu rahnen Sapad oh ehuehu Sarawien Maram Pwul aramas koaros pahn pil poaridi oh pwongih KAUN-O mwohn ewen kehlo.
\v 4 Ni rahnen Sapado soupeidio pahn patohwandohng KAUN-O, nin duwen meirong me pahn pwonte isihsla, sihmpwul wenemen oh emen sihpw wol, koaros sohte pahn samin.
\v 5 Ong emen sihpw wol e pahn iangahki elep en ehd en wahnsahpw, oh ong emen sihmpwul e pahn iangahki mehkot me e inengieng patohwanda. Ong elep en ehd en meirong en wahnsahpw ehu e pahn iangahki pahkis siluh en kalon ehu en lehn olip.
\v 6 Ni Sarawien Maram Pwul e pahn meirongkihla emen kouwol pwulopwul, sihmpwul wenemen, oh emen sihpw wol, koaros sohte pahn samin.
\v 7 Ong emenemen kou oh emenemen sihpw wol meirong ko pahn iangahki elep en ehd en wahnsahpw, oh ong emenemen sihmpwul soupeidio pahn patohwanda meirong me e nsenki. Pahkis siluh en kalon ehu en lehn olip pahn meirongala iangahki elep en ehuehu ehd en wahnsahpw.
\v 8 Soupeidio pahn patohieisang nan perehn pedolongo ni ewen kehlo oh patohieila wasa me e patohlong ie.
\p 
\v 9 “Ni ahnsou me aramas akan pahn patohdo pwe re en kaudokiong KAUN-O ni rahn sarawi ehu sohte lipilipil, irail ko me patohlong ni ewen kelen paliepeng pahn patohieila ni ewen kelen palieir ni kaudoko eh pahn imwisekla, oh irail ko me patohlong ni ewen kelen palieir pahn patohieila ni ewen kelen paliepeng. Sohte me kak patohiei wasa me e patohlong ie, e uhdahn pahn patohiei ni ewen kehl me sallehngete me e patohlong loale.
\v 10 Soupeidio pahn patohlong ahnsou me aramas akan kin pedolong oh pedoi ahnsou me re kin pedoi.
\v 11 Ni rahnen kamadipw kan oh rahn sarawi kan meirong en wahnsahpw pahn mihmi ni elep en ehd ong emenemen kouwol de sihpw wol, oh dahme tohn kaudoko insenki kihda pwehn iangahki emenemen sihmpwul. Pahkis siluh en kalon ehu en lehn olip pahn meirongala iangahki elep en ehuehu ehd en wahnsahpw.
\p 
\v 12 “Ni ahnsou me soupeidi me kakaun wehio pahn nsenki patohwanda meirong tohrohr ehu ong KAUN-O, ma meirong me pahn pwonte isihsla de meirong en kaminimin, ewen kelen palimesehn pedolong nan kelen masloaleo pahn ritidahng ih. E pahn patohwanda meirongo duwehte me e kin wia ni rahnen Sapad, oh ewen kehlo pahn ritidi mwurin eh pahn pedoila.”
\s1 Meirong en Rahn Koaros
\p 
\v 13 KAUN-O eri mahsanih, “Nimenseng koaros emen sihmpwul me sounpar ehu me sohte kisin samin kis reh pahn pwonte isihsla nin duwen meirong ong KAUN-O. Meirong wet pahn wiawi rahn koaros.
\v 14 Pil meirong en pilawa paun limau pahn wiawi nimenseng koaros, iangahki pahkis siluh en kalon ehu en lehn olip mehn doaloa pilawao. Kosonned pwukat ong meirong wet ong KAUN-O pahn wiewiawi kohkohlahte.
\v 15 Sihmpwulo, pilawao, oh lehn olipo pahn meirong ong KAUN-O nimenseng koaros kohkohlahte.”
\s1 Soupeidio oh Sahpwo
\p 
\v 16 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih: “Ma soupeidi me kakaun wehio pahn kihla ehu peliensapw ong emen nah pwutak nin duwen kisakis ehu, e pahn wiahla sapwen peneineien pwutako.
\v 17 Ahpw ma soupeidi me kakaun wehio pahn kihla ehu peliensapw ong mehmen me doadoahkohng, sahpwo pahn kapwurupwurdohng soupeidio ni Pahr en Onohnsapahlo.\f v \fr 46:17 \fk PAHR EN ONOHNSAPAHLO: \ft Mwurin sounpar limeisek koaros, mehn Israel koaros anahne en kasaledekihala iangarail mehn Israel men me wiahla ar lidu pwehki ar pweipwandla; re pil anahne kapwurehla rehn aramas emen me uhdahn sapweniki sahpw ehu, de ahneki manaman en sohsohki, sapwen sohso ehu me netilahr pwehn kapwungala pweipwand (tehk Lip. 25.8-55).\f* Sahpwo iei uhdahn sapwe, oh ihete oh nah pwutak kan me kak sapweniki kohkohlahte. \x - \xo 46:17 \xt Lip. 25.10.\x*
\v 18 Soupeidi me kakaun wehio sohte pahn adihasang sapwen aramas akan. Peliensapw ehu me e pahn kihong nah pwutak kan pahn sang nan sahpw me e kileldiong powe, pwe en dehr kahpwalihala emen nei aramas akan ni eh pahn kihsang sapwarail.”
\s1 Wasahn Kuk en Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 19 Ohlo eri kahreielahng ni perehn pedolong ko me sallahng paliepeng limwahn ewen kelen palieir ni pengepengen kelen masloaleo. Met iei en samworo kan pere sarawi kei. Ih eri idilahng wasa kis ni palikapi en pere ko
\v 20 oh patohwan, “Iei wasakiset me samworo kan pahn kin pwoailih ie uduk en meirong en dihp de meirong en kapwungala sapwung, oh umwunda pilawahn meirong kan, pwe mehkot me sarawi en dehr wisikieilahng nan kelen maslikio, wasa me eh kak kauwehla aramas akan.”\f w \fr 46:20 \fk KAUWEHLA ARAMAS: \ft Tehk 44.19.\f*
\p 
\v 21-22 Ih eri kahreielahng nan kelen maslikio oh kasalehiong ie me nan keimw pahieuo mie kehl tikitik ehu, piht 68 reirei oh 48 tehlap.
\v 23 Nan ehuehu kisin kehl ko takai me didih, wasahn kisiniei wiawihda patehng dihdo.
\v 24 Ohlo eri patohwanohng ie, “Ih wasahn kuk kan met, wasa me sounpapah kan en Tehnpas Sarawio pahn kin pwoailihada meirong me aramas akan kin patohwanda.”
\c 47
\s1 Piletik me kin Pwilipwilsang nan Tehnpas Sarawio
\p 
\v 1 Ohlo eri kahreielahng wasahn pedolong en Tehnpas Sarawio. Pihl wie pwilipwilieisang pahn wasahn pedolongo oh pwilipwilahng palimese, wasa me Tehnpas Sarawio sohpeilahng ie. E pwilipwildilahsang wasa kis ni palieir en pahn Tehnpas Sarawio pwilipwildihla ni palieir en pei sarawio.\x - \xo 47:1 \xt Sek. 14.8; Sohn 7.38; Kaud. 22.1.\x*
\v 2 Ohlo eri kahreiesang nan Tehnpas Sarawio keid ni ewen kelen paliepeng oh wetila ni ewen kehl me sallahng palimese. Kisin piletik kis wie pwilipwilsang ni palieir en kehlo.
\v 3 Ohlo eri sohngki nah kisin tuhkeo iaht 560 kohdihla ni palimese oh ndaiong ie I en aluhla nan pihlo. Pihlo kohda lel ni keimw en nei kat.
\v 4 Ih eri pil sohngala iaht 560, oh pihlo kohda lel ni pwikieiet. E pil sohngala iaht 560, oh pihlo kohda lel ni lukopeiet.
\v 5 E pil sohngala iaht 560, oh pihlo inenen loalla I sohla kak kotehla. E inenen loal, aramas pahn papala loale.
\v 6 E ahpw patohwanohng ie, “Kowe, nein aramas, tehk mwahu mepwukat koaros.”
\p Ohlo eri kapwureielahng ni keilen pihlo,
\v 7 oh ni ei lel mwo, I ahpw kilangada me diren tuhke pali koaros ni keilen pihlo.
\v 8 E ahpw patohwanohng ie, “Pihl wet pwilipwilla nan sahpwo kolahng palimese oh kodilahng nan Wahun Sordan oh kolahng Sehden Mehla. Ni eh leldihla nan Sehden Mehla, e kin kahrehda pilen sehdo eh kin sohla soahl.
\v 9 Wasa koaros me pihlo kin pwila ie, e kin mie soangen mahn oh mwahmw koaros. Pihlo pahn kahrehda pilen Sehden Mehla eh mwakelekel, oh wasa koaros me e pahn pwillahng ie, e pahn kahrehda mour.
\v 10 Sang ni Pwarer en Engkedi kolahng Pwarer en Eneklaim, soused kan pahn kin mihmiseli pohn oaroahr kan, oh kin palang ar uhk kan wasao. E pahn mie soangen mwahmw tohto wasao duwehte nan Sehd Mediderenien.
\v 11 Ahpw pihl kan me mi nan lehpwel oh peden pihl akan pohn keilen oaroahro sohte pahn iang mwakelekel. Re pahn mihmi mwo pwehn wia pwarer en soahl.
\v 12 Wasa koaros ni keilen piletiko soangen tuhke koaros pahn keirda ie pwehn kihda mwenge. Tehrail kan sohte pahn mengida, oh wah sohte pahn tokedi. Re pahn kin kapwarehda wah nan sounpwong koaros, pwehki ar kelemwurki piletiko me pwilipwilsang ni Tehnpas Sarawio. Tuhke kan pahn kihda kisin mwenge, oh tehrail kan pahn wia wini ong aramas akan.”\x - \xo 47:12 \xt Kaud. 22.2.\x*
\s1 Irepen Sahpwo
\p 
\v 13 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Iet kan irepen sahpwo ni eh pahn nehnepeseng rehn kadaudok eisek riauo, me kadaudok en Sosep pahn ale wasa riau.\f x \fr 47:13 \fk WASA RIAU: \ft Kadaudok en Manase oh Epraim, nein Sosep pwutak riemeno, emen ale ehu wasa, a emen ale ehu.\f*
\p 
\v 14 I inoukihong amwail pahpa kahlap ako me I pahn ketikihong irail en sapwenikihla sahpwet; eri, met kumwail nehkpeseng ni pahrek nanpwungamwail.
\p 
\v 15 “Irepen paliepeng tang kolahng palimese, sang Sehd Mediderenien kolahng kahnimw Edlon, kolahng Wasahn Kot en Amad, kolahng kahnimw Sedad,
\v 16 kolahng kahnimw kan en Peroda oh Sipraim (wasa pwukat mihte nanpwungen sapwen wehin Damaskus oh wehin Amad), oh kolahng Tikon (me mihte limwahn irepen wehin Auran).
\v 17 Eri, irepen paliepeng tangasang ni palimesehn Mediderenien kolahng kahnimw Enon, me irepen Damaskus oh Amad mi ni paliepengih.
\p 
\v 18 “Irepen palimese tangasang ni palieir sang wasa kis nanpwungen sapwen Damaskus oh Auran, me Pillap Sordan wia irepen sahpw nanpwungen wehin Israel ni palikapi oh Kilead ni palimese, lellahng Damar ni Sehden Mehla.
\p 
\v 19 “Irepen palieir tangasang palieir en palikapi sang Damar kolahng wasahn pihl en Kades Meripa oh mwuhr kolahng paliepeng en palikapi peianla irepen Isip kolahng Sehd Mediderenien.
\p 
\v 20 “Irepen palikapi sang Mediderenien oh tang kolahng paliepeng ong wasa kis ni palikapi en Wasahn Kot en Amad.
\p 
\v 21 “Kumwail nehkpeseng sahpwet nanpwungen kumwail kadaudok kan;
\v 22 kumwail pahn sapwenikihla kohkohlahte. Mehn liki kan me koukousoan rehmwail oh me neirail seri kan ipwidi wasaht pahn pil ale pwaisarail sang ni sahpwo ni amwail pahn nehkpeseng. Kumwail pahn wiahkin irail uhdahn pwilidak en Israel kei oh re pahn iang kadaudok en Israel kan usuhski pwaisarail sang nan sahpwo.
\v 23 Emenemen mehn liki me koukousoan rehmwail pahn ale pweise rehn kadaudok kan me e koukousoan reh. Ngehi, KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, me mahmahsen.”
\c 48
\s1 Nehnepeseng en Sahpwo Nanpwungen Kadaudok ko
\p 
\v 1-7 Irepen paliepeng en sahpwo tangasang palimese sang Sehd Mediderenien kolahng kahnimw Edlon, kolahng Wasahn Kot en Amad, kolahng kahnimw Enon, kolahng irepen sahpw nanpwungen wehin Damaskus oh Amad. Ehuehu kadaudok pahn ale ehu wasa sang ni sahpwo me tangasang ni irepen palimese ni palikapi kolahng Sehd Mediderenien, ni duwen koasoandi wet sang paliepeng kolahng palieir:
\p 
\v 8 Ehu peliensapw kumwail pahn katohrehla mehn wia doadoahk kesempwal. E pahn mwail 10 tehlap sang ni paliepeng kolahng palieir, oh soangen reireiohte sang palimese kolahng palikapi duwehte me kohieng kadaudok kan. Tehnpas Sarawio pahn mi wasakiset.
\p 
\v 9 Nanwerengen wasakiset, wasa kis pahn reireiki mwail 10 oh 8 tehlap pahn kasarawihong KAUN-O.
\v 10 Samworo kan pahn ale ar pwais sang nan wasa sarawi wet. Sang palimese kolahng palikapi ar wasao pahn mwail 10, oh sang paliepeng kolahng palieir mwail 4. Tehnpas en KAUN-O pahn mi nanwerengen wasakiset.
\v 11 Wasa sarawi wet pahn kohieng samworo kan me kadaudok en Sadok. Re papah ie ni loalopwoat oh sohte iang mehn Israel teikan wia me sapwung, duwehte me kadaudok en Lipai teikan wiadahr.
\v 12 Eri, re pahn ale ekis wasa palihlahsang wasa me kohieng mehn Lipai ko, oh wasao me pahn keieu sarawi.
\v 13 Mehn Lipai kan pahn pil ale ekis wasa ni paliepeng en samworo ko. E pahn mwail 10 sang palimese kolahng palikapi, mwail 4 sang paliepeng kolahng palieir.
\v 14 Wasa me kasarawihong KAUN-O iei wasa me keieu kaselel nan sahpwo, oh sohte wasa kis pahn netila de kawilialihda de kohieng emen. E me sarawi oh nin limen KAUN-O.
\p 
\v 15 Wasakis me luhwehdi sang ni peliensapw kesempwalo, mwail 10 reirei oh 2 tehlap, me sohte sarawi, ahpw e pahn wia wasahn doadoahk kesempwal ong aramas koaros. Re kak kousoan wasao oh doadoahngki. Kahnimwo pahn mi nanwerenge,
\v 16 oh e pahn keimw pahieu, iaht 2,520 pali koaros.
\v 17 Pali koaros kapilpene kahnimwo pahn mie wasa saledek kis me iaht 140 kotehla.
\v 18 Sahpw me pahn luhwe mwurin kahnimwo eh kokoudahr wasa me mi palieir en wasa sarawio—mwail 4 reirei oh 2 tehlap ni palimese oh mwail 4 reirei oh 2 tehlap ni palikapi—pahn wia wasahn mwetuwel ong aramas akan me koukousoan nan kahnimwo.
\v 19 Mehmen me koukousoan nan kahnimwo, sohte lipilipil mehnia kadaudok me e kohsang ie, kak wia mwetuwel nan sahpwo.
\p 
\v 20 Eri, kapatpenehn uwen laud en wasa me mi nanwerenge me katohrohrla pahn mwail 10 pali koaros en keimw pahieu, oh e pahn iangahki wasa me kahnimwo mi ie.
\p 
\v 21-22 Kolahng palimese oh kolahng palikapi en wasakiset me Tehnpas Sarawio mi ie, iangahki sapwen samworo kan, sapwen mehn Lipai kan, oh kahnimwo, luhwen sahpwo iei sapwen soupeidi me kakaun wehio. E lellahng palimese ni irepen palimese oh palikapi kolahng Sehd Mediderenien, oh e ididi ni paliepeng wasa me wia sapwen Suda oh ni palieir wasa me wia sapwen Pensamin.
\s1 Sapwen Kadaudok Teikan
\p 
\v 23-27 Palieir en wasa kesempwal wet, ehuehu luhwen kadaudok kan pahn ale ehu peliensapw me tangasang irepen palimese kolahng Sehd Mediderenien, ni duwen koasoandi wet sang paliepeng kolahng palieir:
\p 
\v 28 Ni palieir en wasa me kohieng kadaudok en Kad, irepen sapweo pahn tangasang palieir en palikapi sang Damar kolahng wasahn pihl en Kades, oh kolahng paliepeng en palikapi peianla irepen Isip kolahng Sehd Mediderenien.
\p 
\v 29 KAUN-O, Wasa Lapalahpie, mahsanih, “Ih duwen amwail pahn nehkpeseng sahpwo ong kadaudok kan en Israel pwe re en sapwenikihla.”
\s1 Ewen Kehl kan en Serusalem
\p 
\v 30-34 Ewen kehl eisek riau ong kahnimw en Serusalem. Ehuehu dihd pahieu ko iaht 2,520 oh ewen kehl siluh mie ie, ehuehu adasang rehn kadaudok ko. Ewen kehl me mi ni dihd en paliepeng adasang Reupen, Suda, oh Lipai; me mi ni dihd en palimese ko, adasang Sosep, Pensamin, oh Dan; me mi ni dihd en palieir ko, adasang Simion, Isakar, oh Sepulon; oh me mi ni dihd en palikapi ko adasang Kad, Aser, oh Napdali.\x - \xo 48:30-34 \xt Kaud. 21.12-13.\x*
\v 35 Koaros kapatpene uwen reirei en dihdo ni pali koaros en kahnimw iaht 10,080. Sang met kohla kahnimwo pahn adanekihla “KAUN-O-Ketiket-Wasaht!” 
